  <para style="mt1">JOHANA</para>
  <para style="imt1">Ũhoro wa Ibuku Rĩĩrĩ</para>
  <para style="ip">Ibuku rĩa Johana rĩandĩkirwo nĩguo rĩonanie bata wa andũ gwĩtĩkia Jesũ Kristũ (20:30, 31). Mĩhari ĩrĩa yambĩrĩirie ibuku-inĩ rĩĩrĩ yonanĩtie atĩ Kristũ aarĩ Ngai, na rĩkonania ũhoro wa ngwatanĩro yake ya mwanya na Ngai.</para>
  <para style="ip">Nĩtwĩrutaga maũndũ maingĩ thĩinĩ wa ibuku rĩa Johana ma ũhoro ũkoniĩ ũrĩa Jesũ aaririe na andũ arĩa angĩ. Andũ acio nĩ ta Nikodemo ũrĩa warĩ mũrutani wa kĩrĩra ndini-inĩ ya Ayahudi, na mũtumia Mũsamaria ũrĩa maaririe na Jesũ gĩthima-inĩ kĩa maaĩ na akĩĩrirĩria Jesũ amũhe maaĩ ma muoyo, o na mũtumia ũrĩa wanyiitĩtwo agĩtharia, na ũhoro wa ũrĩa aariũkirie mũratawe Lazaro.</para>
  <para style="ip">Ningĩ Jesũ nĩoigire atĩ nĩwe Mũgate wa Muoyo, na nĩwe Ũtheri wa thĩ, na nĩwe Mũrĩithi ũrĩa Mwega, o na nĩwe Mũthabibũ ũrĩa wa ma.</para>
  <para style="ip">Johana nĩandĩkĩte ũhoro wa ciama mũgwanja iria Jesũ aaringire. O kĩama nĩkĩonanagia atĩ Jesũ aarĩ Mũrũ wa Ngai.</para>
  <para style="ip">Jesũ nĩeraga andũ mamwĩtĩkie, na akameerĩra muoyo wa nginya tene. Nĩonanirie ma ya ũhoro ũyũ na ũndũ wa kũriũkia Lazaro.</para>
  <para style="ip">Mũhari ũrĩa ũĩkaine mũno wa Kĩrĩkanĩro wonekaga thĩinĩ wa ibuku rĩĩrĩ (3:16) na nĩguo ũgwetagwo mũno nĩ andũ kuuma thĩinĩ wa Kĩrĩkanĩro gĩothe.</para>
  <para style="iot">Mwandĩki</para>
  <para style="im">Ibuku rĩĩrĩ rĩandĩkirwo nĩ Johana, “Mũtũmwo ũrĩa Jesũ eendete mũno” (13:23, 19:26).</para>
  <para style="iot">Ũrĩa Ibuku Rĩĩrĩ Rĩgayanĩtio</para>
  <para style="io1">· Kĩambĩrĩria gĩa gũtuonia Jesũ nĩ Ngai kũna <char style="ior"><ref loc="JHN 1:1-14">1:1-14</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">· Ũtungata mbere ya gũthiĩ Galili <char style="ior"><ref loc="JHN 1:15-4:54">1:15–4:54</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">· Ũtungata Galili, na gũthiĩ Jerusalemu <char style="ior"><ref loc="JHN 5:1-10:42">5:1–10:42</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">· Kũrĩkĩrĩria kwa ũtungata wa Jesũ <char style="ior"><ref loc="JHN 12:1-13:38">12:1–13:38</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">· Ũrutani wa mũthia wa Jesũ <char style="ior"><ref loc="JHN 14:1-17:26">14:1–17:26</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">· Gũkua na kũriũka kwa Jesũ <char style="ior"><ref loc="JHN 18:1-20:10">18:1–20:10</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">· Kuonekana kwa Jesũ aarĩkia kũriũka <char style="ior"><ref loc="JHN 20:11-21:25">20:11–21:25</ref></char>.</para>
  <para style="ie"/>
  <chapter number="1" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Ũhoro Gũtuĩka Mũndũ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1JN 1:2">1Joh 1:2</ref>; <ref loc="PHP 2:6">Afil 2:6</ref></char>
    </note>Kĩambĩrĩria-inĩ Ũhoro aarĩ o kuo, nake Ũhoro aatũũrĩte na Ngai, na Ũhoro aarĩ Ngai. <verse number="2" style="v"/>We aatũũrĩte na Ngai kuuma o kĩambĩrĩria.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:3 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="COL 1:16">Akol 1:16</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Indo ciothe ciombirwo na ũndũ wake; gũtirĩ kĩndũ kĩa iria ciombirwo kĩagĩire atarĩ ho. <verse number="4" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:4 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 5:26">Joh 5:26</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 36:9">Thab 36:9</ref></char></note>Thĩinĩ wake kwarĩ muoyo, naguo muoyo ũcio nĩguo warĩ ũtheri wa andũ. <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:5 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 3:19">Joh 3:19</ref></char></note>Ũtheri ũcio nĩũtheraga nduma-inĩ, nayo nduma ndĩigana kũũhoota.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 3:1">Math 3:1</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 3:15">Joh 3:15</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 5:33">5:33</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩguokire mũndũ watũmĩtwo nĩ Ngai; eetagwo Johana. <verse number="7" style="v"/>We okire arĩ mũira oimbũre ũhoro ũkoniĩ ũtheri ũcio, nĩgeetha andũ othe metĩkie nĩ ũndũ wake. <verse number="8" style="v"/>We mwene tiwe warĩ ũtheri ũcio, no okire arĩ o ta mũira tu nĩgeetha oimbũre ũhoro wa ũtheri ũcio. <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:9 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1JN 2:8">1Joh 2:8</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 49:6">Isa 49:6</ref></char></note>Ũtheri ũcio wa ma, ũrĩa ũtheragĩra o mũndũ o wothe, nĩwokaga thĩ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>We Ũhoro aarĩ gũkũ thĩ, no o na gũtuĩka thĩ yombirwo na ũndũ wake-rĩ, andũ a thĩ matiigana kũmũmenya. <verse number="11" style="v"/>Okire gwake mwene, no andũ ake mwene matiigana kũmwĩtĩkĩra. <verse number="12" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:12 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1JN 3:23">1Joh 3:23</ref>; <ref loc="DEU 14:1">Gũcook 14:1</ref></char></note>No andũ arĩa othe maamwĩtĩkĩrire, o acio metĩkirie rĩĩtwa rĩake, nĩamahotithirie gũtuĩka ciana cia Ngai <verse number="13" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:13 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 3:6">Joh 3:6</ref>; <ref loc="1PE 1:23">1Pet 1:23</ref></char></note>ciana itaciarĩtwo nĩ thakame, kana igaciarwo nĩ kwenda kwa mwĩrĩ kana kwenda kwa mũndũ, no iciarĩtwo nĩ kwenda kwa Ngai.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:14 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GAL 4:4">Agal 4:4</ref>; <ref loc="1TI 3:16">1Tim 3:16</ref></char>
    </note>We Kiugo agĩtuĩka mũndũ na agĩtũũrania na ithuĩ. Nĩtuonete riiri wake, riiri wa Mũrũ wake wa Mũmwe, ũrĩa woimire kũrĩ Ithe aiyũrĩtwo nĩ ũtugi na ũhoro wa ma.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:15 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 3:11">Math 3:11</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Johana nĩoimbũraga ũhoro wake. Aanagĩrĩra akoiga atĩrĩ, “Ũyũ nĩwe ũrĩa ndaaragia ũhoro wake ngiuga atĩrĩ, ‘Ũrĩa ũgũũka thuutha wakwa nĩ mũnene kũngĩra, tondũ aarĩ mbere yakwa.’ ” <verse number="16" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:16 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="COL 1:19">Akol 1:19</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 3:24">Arom 3:24</ref></char></note>Na kuuma ũiyũrĩrĩru wa ũtugi wake-rĩ, ithuothe nĩtwamũkĩrĩte irathimo nyingĩ mũno. <verse number="17" style="v"/>Tondũ watho wokire na Musa, no ũtugi na ũhoro ũrĩa wa ma ciokire na Jesũ Kristũ. <verse number="18" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:18 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EXO 33:20">Thaam 33:20</ref>; <ref loc="1JN 4:9">1Joh 4:9</ref></char></note>Gũtirĩ mũndũ o na ũrĩkũ ũrĩ ona Ngai, o tiga Mũrũ wake wa Mũmwe ũrĩa ũikarĩte hamwe na Ithe, na nĩwe ũtũmĩte amenyeke.</para>
  <para style="s1">Johana Mũbatithania kuuga tiwe Kristũ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:19 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 3:1">Math 3:1</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 2:18">Joh 2:18</ref></char>
    </note>Na rĩrĩ, ũyũ nĩguo ũira wa Johana hĩndĩ ĩrĩa Ayahudi a Jerusalemu maamũtũmĩire athĩnjĩri-Ngai na Alawii makamũũrie we aarĩ ũ. <verse number="20" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:20 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 3:15">Luk 3:15</ref>, <ref loc="LUK 3:16">16</ref></char></note>We ndaagire kuumbũra, no oimbũrire atekũhitha, akiuga atĩrĩ, “Niĩ ti niĩ Kristũ.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:21 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 11:14">Math 11:14</ref>; <ref loc="DEU 18:15">Gũcook 18:15</ref></char>
    </note>Nao makĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Wee ũkĩrĩ ũ? Wee nĩwe Elija?”</para>
  <para style="p">Nake akĩmacookeria atĩrĩ, “Aca, ti niĩ.”</para>
  <para style="p">Ningĩ makĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Nĩwe Mũnabii ũrĩa?”</para>
  <para style="p">Nake agĩcookia atĩrĩ, “Aca.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>Mũthia-inĩ makĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Wee ũkĩrĩ ũ? Tũhe macookio nĩguo tũcookerie arĩa matũtũmire. Ũkuuga atĩa ha ũhoro waku mwene?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:23 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 40:3">Isa 40:3</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Johana akĩmacookeria na ciugo iria ciarĩtio nĩ mũnabii Isaia, akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Niĩ ndĩ mũgambo wa mũndũ ũranĩrĩra werũ-inĩ akoiga atĩrĩ, ‘Rũngariai njĩra ya Mwathani.’ ”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v"/>Na rĩrĩ, Afarisai amwe arĩa maatũmĩtwo <verse number="25" style="v"/>makĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Angĩkorwo we tiwe Kristũ, na tiwe Elija, o na kana Mũnabii ũrĩa-rĩ, ũkĩbatithanagia nĩkĩ?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v"/>Nake Johana akĩmacookeria atĩrĩ, “Niĩ ndĩmũbatithagia na maaĩ. No gatagatĩ-inĩ kanyu nĩ harĩ na ũmwe mũtooĩ. <verse number="27" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:27 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MRK 1:7">Mar 1:7</ref></char></note>Ũcio nĩwe ũgũũka thuutha wakwa, o we ũrĩa itaagĩrĩire kuohora ndigi cia iraatũ ciake.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:28 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 3:26">Joh 3:26</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 10:40">10:40</ref></char>
    </note>Maũndũ maya mothe mekĩkire itũũra-inĩ rĩa Bethania, mũrĩmo wa Rũũĩ rwa Jorodani, kũrĩa Johana aabatithanagĩria.</para>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Gatũrũme ka Ngai</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:29 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 53:7">Isa 53:7</ref>; <ref loc="1PE 1:19">1Pet 1:19</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 3:17">Joh 3:17</ref></char>
    </note>Mũthenya ũyũ ũngĩ, Johana akĩona Jesũ agĩũka na kũrĩ we, akiuga atĩrĩ, “Onei! Gatũrũme ka Ngai karĩa keheragia mehia ma kĩrĩndĩ! <verse number="30" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:30 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 1:15">Joh 1:15</ref>, <ref loc="JHN 1:27">27</ref></char></note>Ũyũ nĩwe ndaaragia ũhoro wake rĩrĩa ndoigire atĩrĩ, ‘Mũndũ ũrĩa ũgũũka thuutha wakwa nĩ mũnene kũrĩ niĩ tondũ we aarĩ kuo mbere yakwa.’ <verse number="31" style="v"/>Niĩ mwene ndiamũũĩ, no ndokire ngĩbatithanagia na maaĩ nĩgeetha aguũrĩrio andũ a Isiraeli.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:32 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 3:16">Math 3:16</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Ningĩ Johana akĩheana ũira ũyũ: “Nĩndonire Roho agĩikũrũka kuuma igũrũ atariĩ ta ndutura, agĩikara igũrũ rĩake. <verse number="33" style="v"/>Niĩ ndingĩamũmenyire, tiga ũrĩa wandũmire mbatithanagie na maaĩ aanjĩĩrire atĩrĩ, ‘Mũndũ ũrĩa ũkoona Roho agĩikũrũkĩra na aikare igũrũ rĩake-rĩ, ũcio nĩwe ũkaabatithanagia na Roho Mũtheru.’ <verse number="34" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:34 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 1:49">Joh 1:49</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 4:3">Math 4:3</ref></char></note>Niĩ nĩnyonete ũguo na ngoimbũra atĩ ũyũ nĩwe Mũrũ wa Ngai.”</para>
  <para style="s1">Arutwo a Mbere a Jesũ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v"/>Ningĩ mũthenya ũyũ ũngĩ, Johana agĩkorwo arĩ kũu o rĩngĩ marĩ na arutwo ake eerĩ. <verse number="36" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:36 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 1:29">Joh 1:29</ref></char></note>Na rĩrĩa onire Jesũ akĩhĩtũka, akiuga atĩrĩ, “Onei Gatũrũme ka Ngai!”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="37" style="v"/>Hĩndĩ ĩrĩa arutwo acio eerĩ maiguire oiga ũguo, makĩrũmĩrĩra Jesũ. <verse number="38" style="v"/>Jesũ ehũgũra akĩmoona mamumĩte thuutha, akĩmooria atĩrĩ, “Nĩ atĩa mũrenda?”</para>
  <para style="p">Nao makĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Rabii” (ũguo nĩ kuuga Mũrutani), “ũikaraga kũ?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="39" style="v"/>Nake akĩmacookeria atĩrĩ, “Ũkai na nĩmũkuona.”</para>
  <para style="p">Nĩ ũndũ ũcio magĩthiĩ makĩona kũrĩa aikaraga, na magĩikara nake mũthenya ũcio. Na kwarĩ ta thaa ikũmi.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="40" style="v"/>Na rĩrĩ, ũmwe wa arutwo acio eerĩ arĩa maiguĩte ũrĩa Johana oigĩte na makĩrũmĩrĩra Jesũ aarĩ Anderea, mũrũ wa nyina na Simoni Petero. <verse number="41" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:41 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 4:25">Joh 4:25</ref></char></note>Ũndũ wa mbere ũrĩa Anderea eekire nĩgũcaria mũrũ wa nyina Simoni, na kũmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Nĩtuonete Mesia” (nĩwe Kristũ). <verse number="42" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:42 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GEN 17:5">Kĩam 17:5</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 16:18">Math 16:18</ref></char></note>Nake akĩmũtwara kũrĩ Jesũ.</para>
  <para style="p">Nake Jesũ akĩmũrora, akiuga atĩrĩ, “Wee nĩwe Simoni mũrũ wa Johana. Ũgũcooka gwĩtwo Kefa” (na rĩo rĩgĩtaũrwo nĩ kuuga Petero).</para>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ gwĩta Filipu na Nathanieli</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="43" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:43 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 10:3">Math 10:3</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 6:5-7">Joh 6:5-7</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 12:21">12:21</ref></char>
    </note>Mũthenya ũyũ ũngĩ Jesũ agĩtua itua rĩa gũthiĩ Galili. Agĩkora Filipu, akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Nũmĩrĩra.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="44" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:44 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 11:21">Math 11:21</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Filipu, o ta Petero na Anderea, aarĩ wa itũũra rĩa Bethisaida. <verse number="45" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:45 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 21:2">Luk 21:2</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 24:27">Luk 24:27</ref></char></note>Filipu agĩkora Nathanieli, akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Nĩtuonete mũndũ ũrĩa Musa aandĩkire ũhoro wake Ibuku-inĩ rĩa Watho, na nowe anabii maandĩkire ũhoro wake, nake nĩwe Jesũ wa Nazarethi, mũrũ wa Jusufu.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="46" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:46 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 7:41">Joh 7:41</ref>, <ref loc="JHN 7:42">42</ref>, <ref loc="JHN 7:52">52</ref></char>
    </note>Nake Nathanieli akĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Kũrĩ kĩndũ kĩega kĩngiuma Nazarethi?”</para>
  <para style="p">Nake Filipu akĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Ũka ũkoone.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="47" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:47 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 9:4">Arom 9:4</ref>, <ref loc="ROM 9:6">6</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 32:2">Thab 32:2</ref></char>
    </note>Hĩndĩ ĩrĩa Jesũ onire Nathanieli agĩũka kũrĩ we, akĩaria ũhoro wake, akiuga atĩrĩ, “Onei Mũisiraeli kũna ũtarĩ ũhinga.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="48" style="v"/>Nake Nathanieli akĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Ũnjũũĩ atĩa?”</para>
  <para style="p">Jesũ akĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Nĩngũkuonete o na rĩrĩa uuma rungu rwa mũkũyũ, Filipu atanagwĩta.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="49" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:49 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 12:13">Joh 12:13</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Hĩndĩ ĩyo Nathanieli akiuga atĩrĩ, “Rabii, wee nĩwe Mũrũ wa Ngai; wee nĩwe Mũthamaki wa Isiraeli.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="50" style="v"/>Nake Jesũ akiuga atĩrĩ, “Wetĩkia tondũ nĩndakwĩra atĩ nĩnguonire ũrĩ rungu rwa mũkũyũ. Nĩũkuona maũndũ manene kũrĩ macio.” <verse number="51" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:51 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GEN 28:12">Kĩam 28:12</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 8:20">Math 8:20</ref></char></note>Ningĩ akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ na ma, nĩmũkona igũrũ rĩhingũkĩte na araika a Ngai makĩambata na magĩikũrũka, harĩ Mũrũ wa Mũndũ.”</para>
  <chapter number="2" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Kũgarũra Maaĩ Magatuĩka Ndibei</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 4:46">Joh 4:46</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 21:2">21:2</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 12:46">Math 12:46</ref></char>
    </note>Na rĩrĩ, mũthenya wa gatatũ nĩ kwagĩire na kihikanio kũu Kana ya Galili. Nyina wa Jesũ aarĩ kuo, <verse number="2" style="v"/>nake Jesũ na arutwo ake o nao nĩmetĩtwo kĩhikanio-inĩ kĩu. <verse number="3" style="v"/>Rĩrĩa ndibei yathirire,<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">2:3 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Warĩ ũndũ wa thoni mũno kũrĩ andũ a mũciĩ ndibei ĩngĩathirire ũhiki-inĩ.</char></note> nyina wa Jesũ akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Matirĩ na ndibei ĩngĩ.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:4 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 19:26">Joh 19:26</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 26:18">Math 26:18</ref></char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Mũtumia ũyũ, ndĩ na ũhoro ũrĩkũ nawe? Ihinda rĩakwa rĩtirĩ rĩrakinya.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:5 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 41:55">Kĩam 41:55</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake nyina akĩĩra ndungata atĩrĩ, “Ĩkai ũrĩa wothe ekũmwĩra.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MRK 7:3">Mar 7:3</ref>, <ref loc="MRK 7:4">4</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 3:25">Joh 3:25</ref></char>
    </note>Hau hakuhĩ nao nĩ haarĩ na ndigithũ ithathatũ cia maaĩ ciathondeketwo na ihiga, mũthemba ũrĩa wahũthagĩrwo nĩ Ayahudi magongona-inĩ mao ma gwĩtheria,<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">2:6 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Ayahudi meetĩkĩtie mũndũ nĩanyiitagwo nĩ thaahu o mũthenya, na nĩkĩo meethambaga moko hĩndĩ ciothe.</char></note> na o ĩmwe yaiyũragio nĩ ngeereni kuuma mĩrongo ĩĩrĩ nginya mĩrongo ĩtatũ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>Nake Jesũ akĩĩra ndungata icio atĩrĩ, “Iyũriai ndigithũ maaĩ”; nacio ikĩiyũria riita.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>Agĩcooka agĩciĩra atĩrĩ, “Rĩu tahiai ĩmwe mũtwarĩre mũtabania wa iruga.”</para>
  <para style="p">Nacio igĩĩka o ũguo, <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:9 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 4:46">Joh 4:46</ref></char></note>nake mũtabania wa iruga agĩcama maaĩ macio maagarũrĩtwo magatuĩka ndibei. Ndaamenyaga kũrĩa yoimĩte, o na gũtuĩka ndungata iria ciatahĩte maaĩ nĩciamenyaga. Hĩndĩ ĩyo agĩĩta mũhikania keheri-inĩ <verse number="10" style="v"/>akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Mũndũ aambaga kũruta ndibei ĩrĩa njega, na ageni maarĩkia kũnyua mũno, agacooka akaruta ĩrĩa ĩtarĩ njega; no wee ũkũigĩte ĩrĩa njega nginya rĩu.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 1:14">Joh 1:14</ref>; <ref loc="EXO 14:31">Thaam 14:31</ref></char>
    </note>Kĩu nĩkĩo kĩama kĩa mbere kĩrĩa Jesũ aaringire, na aakĩringĩire kũu Kana ya Galili. Akĩonania riiri wake, nao arutwo ake makĩmwĩtĩkia.</para>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Gũtheria Hekarũ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:12 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 12:46">Math 12:46</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Thuutha ũcio agĩikũrũka Kaperinaumu, marĩ na nyina, na ariũ a nyina, o na arutwo ake. Magĩikara kuo matukũ manini.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:13 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 11:55">Joh 11:55</ref>; <ref loc="DEU 16:1-6">Gũcook 16:1-6</ref></char>
    </note>Rĩrĩa Bathaka ya Ayahudi yakuhĩrĩirie-rĩ, Jesũ akĩambata, agĩthiĩ Jerusalemu. <verse number="14" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:14 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LEV 1:14">Alaw 1:14</ref>; <ref loc="DEU 14:25">Gũcook 14:25</ref></char></note>Kũu hekarũ-inĩ nĩakorire andũ makĩendia ngʼombe, na ngʼondu, na ndutura,<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">2:14 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Nyamũ cia kũrutwo magongona ciendagĩrio Ayahudi arĩa moimaga mabũrũri mangĩ magooka gũkũngũĩra ciathĩ icio.</char></note> o na angĩ maikarĩte metha-inĩ magĩceenjia mbeeca. <verse number="15" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio agĩthondeka mũcarica wa mĩkanda, na akĩmarutũrũra othe kuuma hekarũ-inĩ, hamwe na ngʼondu, na ngʼombe; akĩhurunja mbeeca cia arĩa maacenjagia mbeeca na akĩngʼaũrania metha ciao. <verse number="16" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:16 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 2:49">Luk 2:49</ref></char></note>Nao arĩa meendagia ndutura akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Eheriai ici gũkũ! Mwahota atĩa gũtua nyũmba ya Baba ndũnyũ!”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:17 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 69:9">Thab 69:9</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nao arutwo ake makĩririkana nĩ kwandĩkĩtwo atĩrĩ, “Kĩyo kĩrĩa ndĩ nakĩo kĩa nyũmba yaku nĩkĩo gĩkaandĩa.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:18 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 12:38">Math 12:38</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Hĩndĩ ĩyo Ayahudi makĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Nĩ kĩama kĩrĩkũ ũngĩtũringĩra gĩa gũtuonia ũhoti ũrĩa ũrĩ naguo wa gwĩka maũndũ macio mothe?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:19 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 26:61">Math 26:61</ref>; <ref loc="MRK 14:58">Mar 14:58</ref>; <ref loc="MRK 15:29">15:29</ref></char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akĩmacookeria atĩrĩ, “Thariai hekarũ ĩno, na nĩngũmĩaka rĩngĩ na mĩthenya ĩtatũ.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>Nao Ayahudi magĩcookia atĩrĩ, “Hekarũ ĩno yakirwo na mĩaka mĩrongo ĩna na ĩtandatũ, nawe ũkũmĩaka na mĩthenya ĩtatũ?” <verse number="21" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:21 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 6:19">1Akor 6:19</ref></char></note>No rĩrĩ, hekarũ ĩrĩa aaragia ũhoro wayo nĩ mwĩrĩ wake. <verse number="22" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:22 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 24:5-8">Luk 24:5-8</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 24:27">Luk 24:27</ref></char></note>Na thuutha wake kũriũkio kuuma kũrĩ arĩa akuũ-rĩ, arutwo ake makĩririkana ũrĩa oigĩte. Nao magĩĩtĩkia Maandĩko, o na ciugo icio Jesũ aarĩtie.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:23 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 3:15">Joh 3:15</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Na rĩrĩ, hĩndĩ ĩrĩa aarĩ Jerusalemu hĩndĩ ya Gĩathĩ kĩa Bathaka, andũ aingĩ makĩona ciama iria aaringaga, nao magĩĩtĩkia rĩĩtwa rĩake. <verse number="24" style="v"/>No Jesũ ndaigana kũmeĩhokera, nĩgũkorwo nĩooĩ andũ othe. <verse number="25" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:25 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 6:61">Joh 6:61</ref>, <ref loc="JHN 6:64">64</ref></char></note>Ndaabataragio nĩ ũira wa mũndũ, ũkoniĩ mũndũ ũrĩa ũngĩ, nĩgũkorwo nĩamenyaga kĩrĩa kĩrĩ thĩinĩ wa mũndũ.</para>
  <chapter number="3" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ na Nikodemo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>Na rĩrĩ, kwarĩ na mũndũ wa Afarisai wetagwo Nikodemo, warĩ wa kĩama kĩrĩa gĩathanaga kĩa Ayahudi. <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 2:22">Atũm 2:22</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 10:38">10:38</ref></char></note>Nĩokire kũrĩ Jesũ ũtukũ, akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Rabii, nĩtũũĩ we ũrĩ mũrutani uumĩte kũrĩ Ngai. Nĩgũkorwo gũtirĩ mũndũ ũngĩhota kũringa ciama iria ũringaga Ngai atarĩ hamwe nake.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:3 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 1:13">Joh 1:13</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 3:2">Math 3:2</ref></char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Ngũkwĩra atĩrĩ na ma, gũtirĩ mũndũ ũngĩona ũthamaki wa Ngai atangĩciarwo rĩngĩ.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>Nake Nikodemo akĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Mũndũ angĩciarwo atĩa arĩ mũkũrũ? Ti-itherũ ndangĩhota gũtoonya nda ya nyina hĩndĩ ya keerĩ nĩguo aciarwo!”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:5 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="TIT 3:5">Tit 3:5</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Jesũ akĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Ngũkwĩra atĩrĩ na ma, gũtirĩ mũndũ ũngĩtoonya ũthamaki-inĩ wa Ngai atangĩciarwo na maaĩ na Roho. <verse number="6" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:6 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 1:13">Joh 1:13</ref></char></note>Mwĩrĩ ũciaraga mwĩrĩ, no Roho aciaraga roho. <verse number="7" style="v"/>Ndũkagegio nĩ ũguo ndoiga atĩ, ‘No nginya ũciarwo rĩngĩ.’ <verse number="8" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:8 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 2:14-16">1Akor 2:14-16</ref></char></note>Rũhuho rũhurutanaga na kũrĩa rũngĩenda. Ũiguaga rũkĩhurutana, no ndũmenyaga kũrĩa rumĩte kana kũrĩa rũrorete. Ũguo noguo gũtariĩ harĩ mũndũ ũrĩa wothe ũciarĩtwo nĩ Roho.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>Nake Nikodemo akĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Ũndũ ũcio ũngĩhoteka atĩa?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:10 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LUK 2:46">Luk 2:46</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Wee ũrĩ mũrutani wa Isiraeli na ndũrataũkĩrwo nĩ maũndũ maya? <verse number="11" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:11 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 7:16">Joh 7:16</ref>, <ref loc="JHN 7:17">17</ref></char></note>Ngũkwĩra atĩrĩ na ma, twaragia ũrĩa tũũĩ, na tũkoimbũra ũrĩa tuonete, no inyuĩ, mũtiĩtĩkagĩra ũira witũ. <verse number="12" style="v"/>Ndakwĩra maũndũ ma gũkũ thĩ, waga gwĩtĩkia; ũngĩtĩkia atĩa ingĩkwĩra maũndũ ma na igũrũ? <verse number="13" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:13 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PRO 30:4">Thim 30:4</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 2:34">Atũm 2:34</ref>; <ref loc="EPH 4:8-10">Aef 4:8-10</ref></char></note>Gũtirĩ mũndũ ũrĩ wathiĩ igũrũ tiga ũrĩa woimire igũrũ, na nĩwe Mũrũ wa Mũndũ.” <verse number="14" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:14 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="NUM 28:8-9">Ndar 28:8-9</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 12:32">Joh 12:32</ref></char></note>Na o ta ũrĩa Musa aambararirie nyoka ya gĩcango werũ-inĩ, ũguo no taguo Mũrũ wa Mũndũ akaambarario, <verse number="15" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:15 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GEN 15:6">Kĩam 15:6</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 27:42">Math 27:42</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 20:31">Joh 20:31</ref></char></note>nĩguo ũrĩa wothe ũmwĩhokete agĩe na muoyo wa tene na tene.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:16 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 5:8">Arom 5:8</ref>; <ref loc="1JN 4:9-10">1Joh 4:9-10</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 9:6">Isa 9:6</ref></char>
    </note>“Nĩgũkorwo Ngai nĩendire kĩrĩndĩ, akĩruta Mũrũ wake wa mũmwe, nĩgeetha mũndũ o wothe ũmwĩtĩkĩtie ndakoore, no agĩe na muoyo wa tene na tene. <verse number="17" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:17 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 6:29">Joh 6:29</ref>, <ref loc="JHN 6:57">57</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo Ngai ndaatũmire Mũrũwe gũkũ thĩ aciirithie kĩrĩndĩ, no nĩguo kĩrĩndĩ kĩhonoke nĩ ũndũ wake. <verse number="18" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:18 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 5:24">Joh 5:24</ref></char></note>Ũrĩa wothe ũmwĩtĩkĩtie ti wa gũciirithio, no ũrĩa wothe ũtamwĩtĩkĩtie ũcio nĩarĩkĩtie gũtuĩrwo ciira, nĩgũkorwo ndehokete rĩĩtwa rĩa Mũrũ wa Ngai wa mũmwe. <verse number="19" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:19 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 1:4">Joh 1:4</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 52:3">Thab 52:3</ref></char></note>Rĩĩrĩ nĩrĩo ituĩro: Ũtheri nĩwokire gũkũ thĩ, no andũ makĩenda nduma gũkĩra ũtheri, nĩ ũndũ ciĩko ciao ciarĩ njũru. <verse number="20" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:20 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EPH 5:11">Aef 5:11</ref>, <ref loc="EPH 5:13">13</ref></char></note>Mũndũ o wothe wĩkaga ũũru nĩathũire ũtheri, na ndangiumĩra ũtheri-inĩ nĩ gwĩtigĩra ciĩko ciake itikoimbũke. <verse number="21" style="v"/>No mũndũ ũrĩa wothe wĩkaga maũndũ ma ma nĩoimagĩra ũtheri-inĩ, nĩguo kuonekane kũna atĩ ũguo ekĩte nĩ Ngai ũmũhotithĩtie.”</para>
  <para style="s1">Ũira wa Johana Mũbatithania ũkoniĩ Jesũ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:22 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 4:2">Joh 4:2</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Thuutha wa ũguo, Jesũ na arutwo ake nĩmoimagarire magĩthiĩ bũrũri wa Judea, kũrĩa aikarangire nao, na akabatithanagia. <verse number="23" style="v"/>O nake Johana nĩabatithanagĩria Ainoni gũkuhĩ na Salimu, nĩgũkorwo kũu nĩ kwarĩ maaĩ maingĩ, nao andũ nĩmookaga kuo kaingĩ kaingĩ mabatithio. <verse number="24" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:24 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 4:12">Math 4:12</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 14:3">14:3</ref></char></note>(Hĩndĩ ĩyo Johana ndaakoretwo aikĩtio njeera.) <verse number="25" style="v"/>Nĩ kwagĩire na ngarari gatagatĩ-inĩ ka arutwo amwe a Johana na Mũyahudi ũmwe ũhoro-inĩ wa mĩtugo yao ya gwĩtheria. <verse number="26" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:26 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 1:7">Joh 1:7</ref></char></note>Magĩũka kũrĩ Johana makĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Rabii, mũndũ ũrĩa mũraarĩ nake mũrĩmo ũrĩa ũngĩ wa Jorodani, ũrĩa wee warutire ũira ũmũkoniĩ-rĩ, nĩarabatithania, nao andũ othe nĩmarathiĩ kũrĩ we.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v"/>Ũhoro-inĩ ũcio Johana agĩcookia atĩrĩ, “Mũndũ ndarĩ ũndũ angĩamũkĩra o tiga ũrĩa aheetwo kuuma igũrũ. <verse number="28" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:28 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 1:20">Joh 1:20</ref>, <ref loc="JHN 1:23">23</ref></char></note>Inyuĩ ene no mũheane ũira muuge atĩ nĩndoigire atĩrĩ, ‘Niĩ ti niĩ Kristũ, no ndũmĩtwo njũke mbere yake.’ <verse number="29" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:29 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 9:15">Math 9:15</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 16:24">Joh 16:24</ref></char></note>Mũhiki nĩ wa mũhikania. No rĩrĩ, mũrata wa mũhikania ũrĩa ũmũrũgamĩrĩire nĩamũthikagĩrĩria, na akaiyũrwo nĩ gĩkeno rĩrĩa aigua mũgambo wa mũhikania. Gĩkeno ta kĩu nĩkĩo ndĩ na kĩo, na rĩu nĩgĩkinyanĩru. <verse number="30" style="v"/>We no nginya akĩrĩrĩrie kũneneha, na niĩ ngĩrĩrĩrie kũnyiiha.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:31 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 8:23">Joh 8:23</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Ũrĩa uumĩte igũrũ nĩ mũnene kũrĩ andũ othe; nake ũrĩa uumĩte thĩ nĩ wa gũkũ thĩ, na maũndũ marĩa aragia no ma gũkũ thĩ. Ũrĩa uumĩte igũrũ arĩ igũrũ rĩa andũ arĩa angĩ othe. <verse number="32" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:32 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 3:11">Joh 3:11</ref></char></note>We oimbũraga maũndũ marĩa onete na akaigua no gũtirĩ mũndũ o na ũmwe wĩtĩkagĩra ũira wake. <verse number="33" style="v"/>Mũndũ ũrĩa wĩtĩkĩrĩte ũira ũcio nĩahũũrĩte mũhũũri atĩ Ngai nĩ wa ma. <verse number="34" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:34 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 42:1">Isa 42:1</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 4:18">Luk 4:18</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo ũrĩa Ngai atũmĩte aragia ciugo cia Ngai nĩ ũndũ Ngai aheanaga Roho hatarĩ gĩthimi. <verse number="35" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:35 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 28:18">Math 28:18</ref></char></note>Ithe nĩendete Mũriũ na nĩ aigĩte indo ciothe moko-inĩ make. <verse number="36" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:36 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 5:24">Joh 5:24</ref></char></note>Ũrĩa wothe wĩtĩkĩtie Mũriũ, arĩ na muoyo wa tene na tene, no ũrĩa wothe ũregete Mũriũ ndakona muoyo, nĩgũkorwo egũtũũra arakarĩirwo nĩ Ngai.”</para>
  <chapter number="4" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Kwaria na Mũtumia Mũsamaria</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 3:22">Joh 3:22</ref>, <ref loc="JHN 3:26">26</ref></char>
    </note>Afarisai nĩmaiguire atĩ Jesũ nĩagĩĩaga na arutwo aingĩ gũkĩra Johana na akamabatithia, <verse number="2" style="v"/>o na gũtuĩka, ti Jesũ wabatithanagia, no nĩ arutwo ake. <verse number="3" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:3 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 7:13">Luk 7:13</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 3:22">Joh 3:22</ref></char></note>Hĩndĩ ĩrĩa Mwathani aamenyire ũhoro ũcio, akiuma Judea na agĩcooka Galili o rĩngĩ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:4 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 10:5">Math 10:5</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Na rĩrĩ, no nginya angĩatuĩkanĩirie bũrũri wa Samaria. <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:5 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GEN 33:19">Kĩam 33:19</ref>; <ref loc="JOS 24:32">Josh 24:32</ref></char></note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio, agĩkinya itũũra rĩarĩ Samaria rĩetagwo Sukaru, hakuhĩ na gĩthaka kĩrĩa Jakubu aaheete mũriũ Jusufu. <verse number="6" style="v"/>Nakĩo gĩthima kĩa Jakubu nĩkuo kĩarĩ, nake Jesũ, tondũ wa kũnoga nĩ rũgendo, agĩikara thĩ hau gĩthima-inĩ. Na kwarĩ ta thaa thita.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>Na rĩrĩa mũtumia ũmwe Mũsamaria okire gũtaha maaĩ-rĩ, Jesũ akĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “No ũũhe maaĩ ma kũnyua?” <verse number="8" style="v"/>(Hĩndĩ ĩyo arutwo ake nĩmathiĩte kũgũra irio itũũra-inĩ.)</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>Nake mũtumia ũcio Mũsamaria akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Wee ũrĩ Mũyahudi na niĩ ndĩ mũtumia Mũsamaria. Ũngĩkĩĩhooya gĩa kũnyua atĩa?” (Nĩgũkorwo Ayahudi matirĩ ngwatanĩro na Asamaria.)</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:10 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 44:3">Isa 44:3</ref>; <ref loc="JER 2:13">Jer 2:13</ref>; <ref loc="REV 7:17">Kũg 7:17</ref></char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Korwo nĩũũĩ kĩheo kĩa Ngai na ũkamenya nũũ ũrakũhooya maaĩ ma kũnyua, wee nĩwe ũngĩamũhooya nake nĩangĩakũhe maaĩ ma muoyo.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>Nake mũtumia ũcio akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Mũthuuri ũyũ, ndũrĩ na kĩndũ gĩa gũtaha maaĩ nakĩo, na gĩthima gĩkĩ nĩ kĩriku. Ũngĩkĩruta kũ maaĩ macio ma muoyo? <verse number="12" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:12 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 4:6">Joh 4:6</ref></char></note>Anga ũkĩrĩ mũnene gũkĩra ithe witũ Jakubu ũrĩa watũheire gĩthima gĩkĩ, na we mwene aatũũrĩte anyuuaga maaĩ kuuma kĩo o hamwe na ariũ ake na ndũũru ciake cia mbũri na cia ngʼombe?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>Nake Jesũ akĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Mũndũ o wothe ũnyuuaga maaĩ maya nĩanyootaga rĩngĩ, <verse number="14" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:14 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 6:35">Joh 6:35</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 12:3">Isa 12:3</ref></char></note>no ũrĩa wothe ũkũnyua maaĩ marĩa ngaamũhe ndarĩ hĩndĩ akaanyoota. Ti-itherũ, maaĩ marĩa ngũmũhe megũtuĩka gĩthima kĩa maaĩ thĩinĩ wake, gĩtherũkage muoyo wa tene na tene.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:15 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 6:34">Joh 6:34</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake mũtumia ũcio akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Mũthuuri ũyũ, he maaĩ macio nĩguo ndikananyoote rĩngĩ, na ndige gũũkaga haha gũtaha maaĩ.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>Nake akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Thiĩ wĩte mũthuuriguo mũũke nake.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>Nake mũtumia ũcio akĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Niĩ ndirĩ na mũthuuri.”</para>
  <para style="p">Nake Jesũ akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Nĩ waria ma rĩrĩa woiga atĩ ndũrĩ na mũthuuri. <verse number="18" style="v"/>Ũhoro wa ma nĩ atĩ ũkoretwo ũrĩ na athuuri atano, na mũndũ mũrũme ũrĩa ũrĩ nake rĩu ti mũthuuriguo.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">4:18 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Ayahudi moigaga atĩ mũtumia nĩangĩateirwo nĩ athuuri eerĩ kana atatũ, no angĩakĩririe hau onekaga arĩ mũndũ mwĩhia biũ.</char></note> Ũguo woiga nĩ ũhoro wa ma.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:19 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 21:11">Math 21:11</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake mũtumia ũcio akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Mũthuuri ũyũ, nĩndĩrona atĩ wee ũrĩ mũnabii. <verse number="20" style="v"/>Maithe maitũ maahooyagĩra Ngai kĩrĩma-inĩ gĩkĩ, no inyuĩ Ayahudi muugaga atĩ Jerusalemu nokuo kũndũ kũrĩa twagĩrĩirwo nĩkũhooyagĩra Ngai.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:21 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAL 1:11">Mal 1:11</ref>; <ref loc="1TI 2:8">1Tim 2:8</ref></char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akiuga atĩrĩ, “Mũtumia ũyũ, njĩtĩkia, kũrĩ ihinda rĩroka rĩrĩa mũtakaahooyagĩra Baba kĩrĩma-inĩ gĩkĩ o na kana Jerusalemu. <verse number="22" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:22 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2KI 17:28-41">2Ath 17:28-41</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 2:3">Isa 2:3</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 9:4-5">Arom 9:4-5</ref></char></note>Inyuĩ Asamaria mũhooyaga kĩrĩa mũtooĩ; no ithuĩ tũhooyaga kĩrĩa tũũĩ, nĩgũkorwo ũhonokio uumĩte kũrĩ Ayahudi.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">4:22 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Asamaria maarĩ na maandĩko ma mabuku o marĩa matano ma Musa, na matiametĩkĩtie mothe. Meetĩkĩtie Mesia, we Mũhonokia, akoima kũrĩ Ayahudi.</char></note> <verse number="23" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:23 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 5:25">Joh 5:25</ref>; <ref loc="PHP 3:3">Afil 3:3</ref></char></note>No ihinda nĩrĩroka na rĩu nĩrĩkinyu, rĩrĩa arĩa mahooyaga na ma makaahooyaga Baba na roho, na mamũhooyage na ma, nĩgũkorwo nĩ andũ ta acio Baba acaragia a kũmũhooyaga. <verse number="24" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:24 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PHP 3:3">Afil 3:3</ref></char></note>Ngai nĩ roho, nao arĩa mamũhooyaga no nginya mamũhooyage na roho, na mamũhooyage na ma.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:25 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 1:16">Math 1:16</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 1:41">Joh 1:41</ref></char>
    </note>Nake mũtumia ũcio akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Nĩnjũũĩ atĩ Mesia” (ũrĩa wĩtagwo Kristũ) “nĩarooka. Hĩndĩ ĩrĩa agooka nĩagatũtaarĩria maũndũ mothe.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:26 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 8:24">Joh 8:24</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akiuga atĩrĩ, “Niĩ ndĩrakwarĩria nĩ niĩ we.”</para>
  <para style="s1">Arutwo Gũcooka harĩ Jesũ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:27 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 4:8">Joh 4:8</ref>
      </char>
    </note>O ihinda-inĩ rĩu arutwo ake magĩũka, na makĩgega maakora akĩaranĩria na mũtumia. No gũtirĩ o na ũmwe woririe atĩrĩ, “Nĩ kĩĩ ũrenda?” kana akĩũria, “Ũraaranĩria nake nĩkĩ?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v"/>O hĩndĩ ĩyo mũtumia ũcio agĩtiga ndigithũ yake ya maaĩ, agĩcooka itũũra-inĩ, akĩĩra andũ atĩrĩ, <verse number="29" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:29 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 4:17-18">Joh 4:17-18</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 7:26">Joh 7:26</ref>, <ref loc="JHN 7:31">31</ref></char></note>“Ũkai, mũkone mũndũ wanjĩĩra maũndũ marĩa mothe ndaaneka. Ũcio no akorwo nĩwe Kristũ?” <verse number="30" style="v"/>Nao makiuma kũu itũũra-inĩ, magĩthiĩ harĩa Jesũ aarĩ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v"/>Mũira wa makinye, arutwo ake makĩmũringĩrĩria makĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Rabii, rĩa irio.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v"/>Nowe akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Ndĩ na irio cia kũrĩa, iria mũtarĩ ũndũ wacio mũũĩ.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v"/>Nao arutwo ake makĩũrania atĩrĩ, “Kaĩ hihi harĩ mũndũ ũmũreheire irio?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:34 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 26:39">Math 26:39</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 19:30">Joh 19:30</ref></char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akiuga atĩrĩ, “Irio ciakwa nĩ gwĩka wendi wa ũrĩa wandũmire na kũrĩĩkia wĩra wake. <verse number="35" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:35 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 9:37">Math 9:37</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 10:2">Luk 10:2</ref></char></note>Githĩ mũtiugaga atĩ, ‘Nĩ mĩeri ĩna ĩtigarĩte magetha makinye’? Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ, hingũrai maitho manyu muone mĩgũnda! Magetha nĩmakinyu. <verse number="36" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:36 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 1:13">Arom 1:13</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 25:46">Math 25:46</ref></char></note>O na rĩu mũgethi nĩagĩĩaga na mũcaara wake, o na nĩagethaga magetha ma muoyo wa tene na tene, nĩgeetha mũhaandi na mũgethi makenanĩre hamwe. <verse number="37" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:37 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JOB 31:8">Ayub 31:8</ref></char></note>Amu nĩ ũhoro wa ma ũrĩa uugaga atĩ, ‘Ũmwe ahaandaga, nake ũngĩ akagetha.’ <verse number="38" style="v"/>Niĩ ndaamũtũmire mũkagethe kĩrĩa mũtarutĩire wĩra. Angĩ nĩo marutĩte wĩra mũritũ, na inyuĩ mũkagetha uumithio wa wĩra wao.”</para>
  <para style="s1">Asamaria Aingĩ Gwĩtĩkia</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="39" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:39 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 4:29">Joh 4:29</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nao Asamaria aingĩ kuuma itũũra rĩu makĩmwĩtĩkia nĩ ũndũ wa ũira wa mũtumia ũcio, tondũ nĩameerire atĩrĩ, “Nĩanjĩĩrire maũndũ marĩa mothe ndaneeka.” <verse number="40" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio, hĩndĩ ĩrĩa Asamaria mokire kũrĩ Jesũ, makĩmũringĩrĩria aikaranie nao, nake agĩikara mĩthenya ĩĩrĩ. <verse number="41" style="v"/>Na tondũ wa ciugo ciake, andũ angĩ aingĩ magĩĩtĩkia.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="42" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:42 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LUK 2:11">Luk 2:11</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Magĩkĩĩra mũtumia ũcio atĩrĩ, “Ithuĩ tũtiretĩkia no ũndũ wa ũrĩa ũratwĩrire; rĩu nĩtwĩiguĩrĩire ithuĩ ene na tũkamenya atĩ mũndũ ũyũ ti-itherũ nĩwe Mũhonokia wa kĩrĩndĩ.”</para>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Kũhonia Mwana wa Mũnene</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="43" style="v"/>Thuutha wa mĩthenya ĩyo ĩĩrĩ, akiumagara agĩthiĩ Galili. <verse number="44" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:44 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 13:57">Math 13:57</ref></char></note>(Amu Jesũ we mwene nĩoigĩte atĩ mũnabii ndatĩĩagwo bũrũri-inĩ wake mwene.) <verse number="45" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:45 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 2:23">Joh 2:23</ref></char></note>Rĩrĩa aakinyire Galili, andũ a Galili makĩmũnyiita ũgeni. Nĩmonete ũrĩa wothe ekĩte Jerusalemu hĩndĩ ya Gĩathĩ gĩa Bathaka, nĩgũkorwo o nao maarĩ kuo.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="46" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:46 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 2:1-11">Joh 2:1-11</ref>
      </char>
    </note>O rĩngĩ agĩceera Kana ya Galili, kũrĩa aagarũrĩte maaĩ magatuĩka ndibei. Na kũu Kaperinaumu nĩ kwarĩ na mũndũ ũmwe mũnene warĩ na mũriũ mũrũaru. <verse number="47" style="v"/>Rĩrĩa mũndũ ũcio aaiguire atĩ Jesũ nĩoimĩte Judea agooka Galili, agĩthiĩ kũrĩ we, akĩmũthaitha athiĩ akahonie mũriũ, ũrĩa warĩ hakuhĩ gũkua.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="48" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:48 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DAN 4:2-3">Dan 4:2-3</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 2:43">Atũm 2:43</ref></char>
    </note>Jesũ akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Inyuĩ mũtangĩona ciama na morirũ, mũtingĩtĩkia.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="49" style="v"/>Nake mũnene ũcio akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Mũthuuri ũyũ, nĩtũikũrũke mwana wakwa atanakua.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="50" style="v"/>Nake Jesũ akĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Inũka. Mũrũguo nĩekũhona.”</para>
  <para style="p">Mũndũ ũcio agĩĩtĩkia ũguo Jesũ aamwĩrire, na akĩinũka. <verse number="51" style="v"/>Naarĩ njĩra akĩinũka, ndungata ciake ikĩmũtũnga na ndũmĩrĩri atĩ mũrũwe arĩ o muoyo. <verse number="52" style="v"/>Rĩrĩa aamooririe nĩ ta thaa ciigana mũriũ aambĩrĩirie kũigua wega, makĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Ira thaa mũgwanja nĩguo araahonire.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="53" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:53 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 11:14">Atũm 11:14</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake ithe akĩmenya atĩ thaa icio nocio Jesũ aramwĩrĩte atĩrĩ, “Mũrũguo nĩekũhona.” Nĩ ũndũ ũcio we na nyũmba yake yothe magĩĩtĩkia.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="54" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:54 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 2:11">Joh 2:11</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Gĩkĩ nĩkĩo kĩarĩ kĩama gĩa keerĩ kĩrĩa Jesũ aaringire kũu Galili, oimĩte Judea.</para>
  <chapter number="5" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Kũhonania Karia-inĩ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>Thuutha wa maũndũ macio Jesũ nĩambatire Jerusalemu tondũ nĩ kwarĩ na gĩathĩ kĩa Ayahudi. <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="NEH 3:1">Neh 3:1</ref>; <ref loc="NEH 12:39">12:39</ref></char></note>Na rĩrĩ, kũu Jerusalemu hakuhĩ na Kĩhingo-kĩa-Ngʼondu nĩ kwarĩ na karia geetagwo na Kĩhibirania Bethesida, nako gaathiũrũrũkĩirio nĩ ithaku ithano ciarĩ ngite. <verse number="3" style="v"/>Kũu nĩkuo gwakomagwo nĩ ikundi nene cia andũ arĩa maarĩ arũaru, ta atumumu, na cionje, na arĩa maakuĩte ciĩga (meetereire maaĩ moinjugwo. <verse number="4" style="v"/>Nĩgũkorwo nĩ kũrĩ hĩndĩ mũraika wa Mwathani aikũrũkaga akoinjuga maaĩ karia-inĩ kau; na mũndũ wa mbere kũrika kuo maaĩ moinjugwo, nĩahonagio mũrimũ o wothe ũrĩa aarĩ naguo.) <verse number="5" style="v"/>Na hau nĩ haarĩ mũndũ ũmwe watũũrĩte arĩ mũrũaru mĩaka mĩrongo ĩtatũ na ĩnana. <verse number="6" style="v"/>Hĩndĩ ĩrĩa Jesũ aamuonire akomete hau, na akĩmenya atĩ atũũrĩte ũguo ihinda iraaya, akĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Nĩũkwenda kũhonio?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>Nake mũndũ ũcio warũarĩte akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Mũthuuri ũyũ, ndirĩ na mũndũ wa kũndikia thĩinĩ wa karia rĩrĩa maaĩ moinjugwo. Ngĩgeria gũtoboka thĩinĩ-rĩ, mũndũ ũngĩ agatoboka mbere yakwa.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:8 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 9:5">Math 9:5</ref>, <ref loc="MAT 9:6">6</ref></char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Ũkĩra, oya kĩbarĩ gĩaku, wĩtware!” <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:9 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 9:14">Joh 9:14</ref></char></note>Na o rĩmwe mũndũ ũcio akĩhona, akĩoya kĩbarĩ gĩake, na agĩĩtwara.</para>
  <para style="p">Na rĩrĩ, mũthenya ũcio gwekĩkire ũguo warĩ wa Thabatũ, <verse number="10" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:10 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="NEH 13:15-22">Neh 13:15-22</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 12:2">Math 12:2</ref></char></note>na nĩ ũndũ ũcio Ayahudi makĩĩra mũndũ ũcio wahonetio atĩrĩ, “Ũmũthĩ nĩ mũthenya wa Thabatũ; watho ndũgwĩtĩkĩrĩtie ũkuue kĩbarĩ gĩaku.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>Nowe akĩmacookeria atĩrĩ, “Mũndũ ũrĩa ũũhonirie anjĩĩrire atĩrĩ, ‘Oya kĩbarĩ gĩaku, wĩtware.’ ”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio makĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Mũndũ ũcio ũkwĩrire woe kĩbarĩ wĩtware nũũ?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>Mũndũ ũcio wahonetio ndaamenyaga nũũ wamũhonetie, tondũ Jesũ aakoretwo orĩire kĩrĩndĩ-inĩ kĩrĩa kĩarĩ hau.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:14 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 8:11">Joh 8:11</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Thuutha ũcio Jesũ akĩmũkora hekarũ-inĩ, akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “One, rĩu nĩũhonete. Ndũgacooke kwĩhia ndũkae gũkorwo nĩ ũndũ mũũru kũrĩ ũcio.” <verse number="15" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:15 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 1:19">Joh 1:19</ref></char></note>Nake mũndũ ũcio agĩthiĩ na akĩĩra Ayahudi atĩ Jesũ nĩwe wamũhonetie.</para>
  <para style="s1">Kũgĩa Muoyo thĩinĩ wa Mũriũ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio, Ayahudi makĩnyariira Jesũ, tondũ ekĩte maũndũ macio mũthenya wa Thabatũ. <verse number="17" style="v"/>Nake Jesũ akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Baba atũũrĩte o arĩ wĩra-inĩ wake nginya rĩu, na o na niĩ no ndĩraruta wĩra.” <verse number="18" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:18 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 10:30">Joh 10:30</ref>, <ref loc="JHN 10:33">33</ref></char></note>Nĩ ũndũ wa gĩtũmi kĩu, Ayahudi magĩkĩrĩrĩria kũgeria kũmũũraga; nĩgũkorwo to mũthenya wa Thabatũ aathũkagia, no o na nginya nĩetaga Ngai ithe wake mwene, na ũguo akeiganania na Ngai.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>Nake Jesũ akĩmacookeria atĩrĩ, “Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ na ma, Mũriũ ndarĩ ũndũ angĩĩka we mwene, tiga o ũrĩa onaga Ithe agĩĩka, nĩgũkorwo maũndũ marĩa Ithe ekaga no mo Mũriũ o nake ekaga. <verse number="20" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:20 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 3:35">Joh 3:35</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo Ithe nĩendete Mũriũ, na nĩamuonagia maũndũ mothe marĩa ekaga, Ĩĩ, na nĩakamuonia maũndũ manene o na gũkĩra maya, nĩgeetha o na inyuĩ mũgege. <verse number="21" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:21 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 4:17">Arom 4:17</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 11:25">Joh 11:25</ref></char></note>O ta ũrĩa Ithe ariũkagia andũ arĩa akuũ akamahe muoyo, noguo o nake Mũriũ aheaga muoyo o ũrĩa angĩenda kũhe. <verse number="22" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:22 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GEN 18:25">Kĩam 18:25</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 10:42">Atũm 10:42</ref></char></note>Na ningĩ-rĩ, ithe ndarĩ mũndũ atuagĩra ciira, no ehokeire Mũriũ ũtuanĩri wothe wa ciira,<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">5:22 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Ayahudi meetĩkĩtie atĩ Ngai Ithe nĩwe warĩ mũciirithia wa andũ othe. Nĩ ũndũ ũcio ũrutani ũyũ nĩmawonire ta ũtaarĩ wa ma.</char></note> <verse number="23" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:23 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 10:16">Luk 10:16</ref>; <ref loc="1JN 2:23">1Joh 2:23</ref></char></note>nĩgeetha andũ othe matĩĩage Mũriũ o ta ũrĩa matĩĩaga Ithe. Ũrĩa ũtatĩĩaga Mũriũ ndatĩĩaga Ithe ũrĩa wamũtũmire.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:24 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 3:18">Joh 3:18</ref>; <ref loc="1JN 3:14">1Joh 3:14</ref></char>
    </note>“Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ na ma, ũrĩa wothe ũiguaga kiugo gĩakwa na agetĩkia ũrĩa wandũmire, arĩ na muoyo wa tene na tene; na ti wa gũciirithio nĩarĩkĩtie kuuma gĩkuũ-inĩ agatoonya muoyo-inĩ. <verse number="25" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:25 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 4:23">Joh 4:23</ref></char></note>Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ na ma, kũrĩ ihinda rĩrooka, na rĩu nĩikinyu rĩrĩa akuũ makaigua mũgambo wa Mũrũ wa Ngai, nao arĩa makaũigua nĩ magaatũũra muoyo. <verse number="26" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:26 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="DEU 30:20">Gũcook 30:20</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 10:12">Ayub 10:12</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 36:9">Thab 36:9</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo o ta ũrĩa Ithe arĩ na muoyo thĩinĩ wake mwene, no taguo ahotithĩtie Mũriũ kũgĩa na muoyo thĩinĩ wake mwene. <verse number="27" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:27 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 5:22">Joh 5:22</ref></char></note>Na nĩamũheete ũhoti wa gũtuanĩra ciira nĩ tondũ nĩ Mũrũ wa Mũndũ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:28 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 4:21">Joh 4:21</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Mũtikagegio nĩ ũhoro ũcio, nĩgũkorwo ihinda nĩrĩroka rĩrĩa andũ arĩa othe marĩ mbĩrĩra-inĩ makaigua mũgambo wake <verse number="29" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:29 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 25:46">Math 25:46</ref></char></note>na moime kuo, arĩa mekĩte wega mariũke nĩguo matũũre muoyo, nao arĩa mekĩte ũũru mariũke nĩguo matuĩrwo ciira. <verse number="30" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:30 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 28:6">Isa 28:6</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 26:39">Math 26:39</ref></char></note>Ndirĩ ũndũ ingĩhota gwĩka niĩ mwene; nduanagĩra ciira kũringana na ũrĩa njiguaga, na itua rĩakwa nĩ rĩa kĩhooto, nĩgũkorwo ndicaragia gwĩkenia niĩ mwene, tiga gũkenia ũrĩa wandũmire.</para>
  <para style="s1">Ũira Ũkoniĩ Jesũ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:31 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 8:14">Joh 8:14</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Ingĩheana ũira ũngoniĩ niĩ mwene-rĩ, ũira ũcio wakwa ndũngĩtuĩka wa ma. <verse number="32" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:32 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 8:18">Joh 8:18</ref></char></note>Nĩ kũrĩ na ũngĩ ũrĩa uumbũraga ũhoro wakwa, na nĩnjũũĩ atĩ ũira wake igũrũ rĩakwa nĩ wa ma.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v"/>“Inyuĩ nĩmwatũmanire kũrĩ Johana, nake nĩaheanire ũira wa ma. <verse number="34" style="v"/>Ti atĩ nĩnjĩtĩkagĩra ũira wa mũndũ; no nĩndĩũgwetaga nĩgeetha mũhonokio. <verse number="35" style="v"/>Johana aarĩ tawa ũrĩa wakanire na ũkĩmũrĩka, na inyuĩ mũgĩthuura gũkenera ũtheri wake kwa ihinda.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="36" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:36 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 3:17">Joh 3:17</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Niĩ ndĩ na ũira mũnene gũkĩra ũcio wa Johana. Nĩgũkorwo wĩra ũrĩa Baba aaheete ndĩĩkie, na noguo ndĩraruta, nĩguo uumbũraga atĩ Baba nĩwe ũndũmĩte. <verse number="37" style="v"/>Nake Baba ũrĩa wandũmire nĩaheanĩte ũira ũngoniĩ we mwene. Inyuĩ mũtirĩ mwaigua mũgambo wake kana mũkona ũrĩa atariĩ, <verse number="38" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:38 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 26:10">Isa 26:10</ref></char></note>o na kiugo gĩake gĩtitũũraga thĩinĩ wanyu, tondũ mũtiĩtĩkĩtie ũrĩa aatũmire. <verse number="39" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:39 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 24:27">Luk 24:27</ref>, <ref loc="LUK 24:44">44</ref></char></note>Inyuĩ mũtuĩragia Maandĩko tondũ mwĩciiragia atĩ na ũndũ wamo nĩmwĩgwatĩire muoyo wa tene na tene. Maandĩko macio nĩmo moimbũraga ũhoro ũrĩa ũngoniĩ, <verse number="40" style="v"/>no nĩmũregaga gũũka kũrĩ niĩ mũgĩe na muoyo.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="41" style="v"/>“Niĩ ndiĩtĩkagĩra ũgooci kuuma kũrĩ andũ, <verse number="42" style="v"/>no inyuĩ nĩndĩmũũĩ. Ngamenya atĩ inyuĩ mũtirĩ na wendo wa Ngai ngoro-inĩ cianyu. <verse number="43" style="v"/>Njũkĩte thĩinĩ wa rĩĩtwa rĩa Baba na mũtinjĩtĩkagĩra; no mũndũ ũngĩ angĩũka na rĩĩtwa rĩake mwene, nĩmũkũmwĩtĩkĩra. <verse number="44" style="v"/>Mũngĩtĩkia atĩa angĩkorwo mwĩtĩkagĩra ũgooci kuuma kũrĩ andũ arĩa angĩ, no mũticaragia ũgooci ũrĩa uumaga kũrĩ Ngai o ũcio ũmwe?</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="45" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:45 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 9:28">Joh 9:28</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 2:17">Arom 2:17</ref></char>
    </note>“No mũtigeciirie atĩ nĩngamũthitanga mbere ya Baba. Musa ũrĩa inyuĩ mwĩhokeete nĩwe mũmũthitangi. <verse number="46" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:46 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 24:27">Luk 24:27</ref>, <ref loc="LUK 24:44">44</ref></char></note>Korwo nĩmwĩtĩkĩtie Musa-rĩ, no mũnjĩtĩkie, nĩgũkorwo nĩ ũhoro wakwa aandĩkire. <verse number="47" style="v"/>No kuona atĩ mũtiĩtĩkĩtie ũrĩa aandĩkire-rĩ, mũngĩgĩtĩkia atĩa ũrĩa njugaga?”</para>
  <chapter number="6" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Kũhũũnia Andũ Ngiri Ithano</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>Thuutha wa maũndũ macio, Jesũ akĩringa mũrĩmo ũrĩa ũngĩ wa Iria rĩa Galili (na norĩo rĩĩtagwo Iria rĩa Tiberia), <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 2:11">Joh 2:11</ref></char></note>nakĩo kĩrĩndĩ kĩnene kĩa andũ gĩkĩmũrũmĩrĩra tondũ nĩkĩoneete ciama iria aaringĩire andũ arĩa maarĩ arũaru. <verse number="3" style="v"/>Nake Jesũ akĩambata kĩrĩma-inĩ, agĩikara thĩ marĩ hamwe na arutwo ake. <verse number="4" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:4 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 11:55">Joh 11:55</ref></char></note>Nakĩo Gĩathĩ gĩa Bathaka ya Ayahudi nĩgĩakuhĩrĩirie.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:5 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 1:43">Joh 1:43</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Rĩrĩa Jesũ aarorire akĩona kĩrĩndĩ kĩnene gĩgĩũka kũrĩ we, akĩũria Filipu atĩrĩ, “Tũkũgũra mĩgate kũ andũ aya marĩe?” <verse number="6" style="v"/>Oririe ũguo nĩguo amũgerie, nĩgũkorwo we nĩooĩ ũrĩa egwĩka.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>Nake Filipu akĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Mũcara wa mĩeri ĩnana ndũngĩgũra mĩgate ya kũigana nĩguo o mũndũ arũme kenyũ!”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:8 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 1:40">Joh 1:40</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake mũrutwo ũngĩ wake wetagwo Anderea, mũrũ wa nyina na Simoni Petero, akiuga atĩrĩ, <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:9 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2KI 4:43">2Ath 4:43</ref></char></note>“Haha harĩ kahĩĩ karĩ na mĩgate ĩtano ya mũtu wa cairi na thamaki igĩrĩ nini, no ingĩkĩigana atĩa andũ marĩ aingĩ ũũ?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>Nake Jesũ akiuga atĩrĩ, “Ĩraai andũ maikare thĩ.” Hau maarĩ haarĩ na nyeki nyingĩ, nao arũme magĩikara thĩ, na maarĩ ta arũme ngiri ithano. <verse number="11" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:11 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 14:19">Math 14:19</ref></char></note>Jesũ agĩcooka akĩoya mĩgate ĩyo, agĩcookia ngaatho na akĩgaĩra arĩa maikarĩte thĩ kũringana na mũigana ũrĩa o mũndũ angĩendire. Agĩcooka agĩĩka o ũguo na thamaki.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>Rĩrĩa othe maarĩire na makĩhũũna, akĩĩra arutwo ake atĩrĩ, “Ũnganiai cienyũ iria ciatigara. Mũtikareke kĩndũ o na kĩrĩkũ kĩũrĩre.” <verse number="13" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio magĩciũngania, makĩiyũria ikabũ ikũmi na igĩrĩ na icunjĩ cia mĩgate ĩrĩa ĩtano ya cairi, iria ciatigirio nĩ andũ acio maarĩkia kũrĩa.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:14 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DEU 18:15">Gũcook 18:15</ref>, <ref loc="DEU 18:18">18</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 11:3">Math 11:3</ref></char>
    </note>Thuutha wa andũ kuona ciama iria Jesũ aaringĩte, makĩambĩrĩria kuuga atĩrĩ, “Ti-itherũ ũyũ nĩwe mũnabii ũrĩa ũgooka gũkũ thĩ.” <verse number="15" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:15 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 18:36">Joh 18:36</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 14:23">Math 14:23</ref></char></note>Nake Jesũ akĩmenya atĩ nĩmendaga mamũtue mũthamaki wao na hinya, nĩ ũndũ ũcio akĩmeherera o rĩngĩ, akĩambata kĩrĩma-inĩ arĩ wiki.</para>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Kũgerera Maaĩ Igũrũ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>Rĩrĩa gwakinyire hwaĩ-inĩ arutwo ake magĩikũrũka nginya iria-inĩ, <verse number="17" style="v"/>magĩtoonya marikabu, makĩringa iria marorete Kaperinaumu. Hĩndĩ ĩyo kwarĩ nduma, na Jesũ ndaathiĩte kũrĩ o. <verse number="18" style="v"/>Nĩ kwarĩ na makũmbĩ ma maaĩ tondũ wa rũhuho rũnene rũrĩa rwahurutanaga. <verse number="19" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:19 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JOB 9:8">Ayub 9:8</ref></char></note>Na hĩndĩ ĩrĩa maatwarithĩtie marikabu ta kilomita ithano kana ithathatũ, makĩona Jesũ agĩũka kũrĩ marikabu-inĩ agereire maaĩ igũrũ; nao makĩmaka. <verse number="20" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:20 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 14:27">Math 14:27</ref></char></note>Nowe akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Nĩ niĩ; tigai gwĩtigĩra.” <verse number="21" style="v"/>Magĩtĩkĩra atoonye thĩinĩ wa marikabu, na kahinda o kau marikabu ĩgĩkinya hũgũrũrũ-inĩ cia kũrĩa maathiiaga.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:22 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 6:15-21">Joh 6:15-21</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Mũthenya ũcio ũngĩ, kĩrĩndĩ kĩrĩa kĩarĩ mũrĩmo ũũrĩa ũngĩ wa iria gĩkĩmenya atĩ no marikabu ĩmwe yarĩ ho, na atĩ Jesũ ndaamĩingĩrĩte hamwe na arutwo ake no maathiĩte marĩ oiki. <verse number="23" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:23 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 6:11">Joh 6:11</ref></char></note>No ningĩ gũgĩũka marikabu ingĩ ciumĩte Tiberia ikĩrũgama hakuhĩ na harĩa andũ maarĩĩrĩire mĩgate thuutha wa Mwathani gũcookeria Ngai ngaatho. <verse number="24" style="v"/>Na rĩrĩa kĩrĩndĩ kĩamenyire atĩ Jesũ kana arutwo ake gũtirĩ warĩ ho, gĩkĩingĩra marikabu icio, gĩgĩthiĩ Kaperinaumu gũcaria Jesũ.</para>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ nĩwe Mũgate wa Muoyo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:25 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 23:7">Math 23:7</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Rĩrĩa maamũkorire mũrĩmo ũũrĩa ũngĩ wa iria makĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Rabii, ũkinyire gũkũ rĩ?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:26 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 2:11">Joh 2:11</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akĩmacookeria atĩrĩ, “Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ na ma, inyuĩ mũtiranjaria nĩ ũndũ wa ciama iria mũronire, no nĩ ũndũ nĩmũrarĩire mĩgate mũrahũũna. <verse number="27" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:27 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 55:2">Isa 55:2</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 25:46">Math 25:46</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 4:11">Arom 4:11</ref></char></note>Tigagai gũtangĩkĩra irio iria ithũkaga, no mwĩtangagei nĩ ũndũ wa irio iria cia gũtũũra nginya muoyo-inĩ wa tene na tene, iria Mũrũ wa Mũndũ akaamũhe. Ũcio nĩwe Ngai Ithe ahũũrĩte mũhũũri wa gwĩtĩkĩrĩka.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v"/>Magĩcooka makĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Twagĩrĩirwo nĩ gwĩka atĩa nĩgeetha tũrutage mawĩra marĩa Ngai endaga?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:29 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1JN 3:23">1Joh 3:23</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akĩmacookeria atĩrĩ, “Wĩra wa Ngai nĩ ũyũ: nĩ mwĩtĩkie ũrĩa we atũmĩte.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:30 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 12:38">Math 12:38</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio makĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Nĩ ciama irĩkũ ũgũtũringĩra tuone nĩguo tũgwĩtĩkie? Ũgwĩka atĩa? <verse number="31" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:31 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="NUM 11:7-9">Ndar 11:7-9</ref>; <ref loc="EXO 16:4">Thaam 16:4</ref>, <ref loc="EXO 16:15">15</ref></char></note>Maithe maitũ ma tene maarĩĩaga mana kũu werũ-inĩ; o ta ũrĩa kwandĩkĩtwo atĩrĩ: ‘Aamaheire mĩgate kuuma igũrũ marĩe.’ ”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">6:31 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Ayahudi meciiragia atĩ Mesia oka nĩangĩamaheire irio iria cietagwo mana, iria maithe mao maarĩĩaga marĩ werũ-inĩ.</char></note></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v"/>Nake Jesũ akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ na ma, ti Musa wamũheire mũgate kuuma igũrũ, no nĩ Baba ũmũheaga mũgate ũrĩa wa ma kuuma igũrũ. <verse number="33" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:33 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 3:13">Joh 3:13</ref>, <ref loc="JHN 3:31">31</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo mũgate wa Ngai nĩ ũrĩa ũikũrũkaga kuuma igũrũ akahe kĩrĩndĩ gĩa thĩ muoyo wa tene na tene.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:34 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 4:15">Joh 4:15</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nao makĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Mũthuuri ũyũ, kuuma rĩu tũheage mũgate ũcio.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:35 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EXO 3:14">Thaam 3:14</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 6:48">Joh 6:48</ref>, <ref loc="JHN 6:51">51</ref></char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akiuga atĩrĩ, “Niĩ nĩ niĩ mũgate wa muoyo. Mũndũ ũrĩa ũũkaga kũrĩ niĩ ndakahũũta o na rĩ, na ũrĩa ũnjĩtĩkĩtie ndakanyoota o na rĩ. <verse number="36" style="v"/>No rĩrĩ, o ta ũrĩa ndĩmwĩrĩte, nĩmũnyonete, no mũtirĩ mũretĩkia. <verse number="37" style="v"/>Arĩa othe Baba ahee nĩmarĩũkaga kũrĩ niĩ, na ũrĩa wothe ũgooka kũrĩ niĩ ndikamũingata o na rĩ. <verse number="38" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:38 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 26:39">Math 26:39</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo ndiikũrũkĩte kuuma igũrũ njũke gwĩka wendi wakwa niĩ mwene, no njũkĩte gwĩka wendi wa ũrĩa wandũmire. <verse number="39" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:39 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 27:3">Isa 27:3</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 10:28">Joh 10:28</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 17:12">17:12</ref></char></note>Naguo ũyũ nĩguo wendi wa ũrĩa wandũmire, atĩ ndigaate o na ũmwe wa arĩa othe aaheete, no ngaamariũkia mũthenya wa kũrigĩrĩria. <verse number="40" style="v"/>Nĩgũkorwo wendi wa Baba nĩ atĩ ũrĩa wothe wonete Mũriũ na akamwĩtĩkia nĩakagĩa na muoyo wa tene na tene, na nĩngamũriũkia mũthenya wa kũrigĩrĩria.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="41" style="v"/>Ayahudi maigua ũguo makĩambĩrĩria kũngʼongʼora nĩ ũndũ wake tondũ nĩoigĩte atĩrĩ, “Niĩ nĩ niĩ mũgate ũrĩa waikũrũkire kuuma igũrũ.” <verse number="42" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:42 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 7:27-28">Joh 7:27-28</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 4:22">Luk 4:22</ref></char></note>Makiuga atĩrĩ, “Githĩ ũyũ ti Jesũ mũrũ wa Jusufu, ũrĩa ithe na nyina tũũĩ? Rĩu angĩhota atĩa kuuga atĩ, ‘Niĩ ndaikũrũkire kuuma igũrũ’?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="43" style="v"/>Nake Jesũ akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Tigai kũngʼongʼora gatagatĩ-inĩ kanyu. <verse number="44" style="v"/>Gũtirĩ mũndũ ũngĩũka kũrĩ niĩ ataguucĩrĩirio nĩ Baba ũrĩa wandũmire, na niĩ nĩngamũriũkia mũthenya wa kũrigĩrĩria. <verse number="45" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:45 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 54:13">Isa 54:13</ref></char></note>Nĩ kwandĩkĩtwo maandĩko-inĩ ma Anabii atĩrĩ, ‘Nao othe makaarutwo ũhoro nĩ Ngai.’ Nake ũrĩa wothe ũthikagĩrĩria Baba na akeeruta ũhoro kuuma kũrĩ we, nĩokaga kũrĩ niĩ. <verse number="46" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:46 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 1:18">Joh 1:18</ref></char></note>Gũtirĩ mũndũ ũrĩ ona Baba, tiga o ũrĩa uumĩte kũrĩ Ngai; we wiki nowe wonete Baba. <verse number="47" style="v"/>Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ na ma, mũndũ ũrĩa wĩtĩkĩtie arĩ na muoyo wa tene na tene. <verse number="48" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:48 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 6:35">Joh 6:35</ref>, <ref loc="JHN 6:51">51</ref></char></note>Niĩ nĩ niĩ mũgate wa muoyo. <verse number="49" style="v"/>Maithe manyu ma tene maarĩĩaga mana marĩ werũ-inĩ, na no maakuire. <verse number="50" style="v"/>No ũyũ nĩguo mũgate ũrĩa ũikũrũkĩte kuuma igũrũ, ũrĩa mũndũ angĩrĩa na ndakue. <verse number="51" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:51 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="HEB 10:10">Ahib 10:10</ref></char></note>Niĩ nĩ niĩ mũgate ũrĩa ũrĩ muoyo ũrĩa waikũrũkire kuuma igũrũ. Mũndũ o wothe ũngĩrĩa mũgate ũyũ, nĩagatũũra tene na tene. Mũgate ũyũ nĩ mwĩrĩ wakwa ũrĩa ngũheana nĩ ũndũ wa muoyo wa andũ a gũkũ thĩ.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="52" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:52 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 9:16">Joh 9:16</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 10:19">10:19</ref></char>
    </note>Hĩndĩ ĩyo nao Ayahudi makĩambĩrĩria gũkararania mũno o ene, makoorania atĩrĩ, “Mũndũ ũyũ angĩhota atĩa gũtũhe mwĩrĩ wake tũrĩe?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="53" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:53 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 26:26">Math 26:26</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Jesũ akĩmacookeria atĩrĩ, “Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ na ma, mũtangĩrĩa mwĩrĩ wa Mũrũ wa Mũndũ na mũnyue thakame yake, mũtirĩ na muoyo thĩinĩ wanyu. <verse number="54" style="v"/>Ũrĩa wothe ũrĩĩaga mwĩrĩ wakwa na akanyua thakame yakwa arĩ na muoyo wa tene na tene, na nĩngamũriũkia mũthenya wa kũrigĩrĩria. <verse number="55" style="v"/>Nĩgũkorwo mwĩrĩ wakwa nĩ irio kũna, nayo thakame yakwa nĩ kĩndũ gĩa kũnyua kũna. <verse number="56" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:56 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 15:4-7">Joh 15:4-7</ref></char></note>Ũrĩa wothe ũrĩĩaga mwĩrĩ wakwa na akanyua thakame yakwa aikaraga thĩinĩ wakwa na niĩ ngaikara thĩinĩ wake. <verse number="57" style="v"/>O ta ũrĩa Baba mũtũũra muoyo aandũmire na o ta ũrĩa na niĩ ndũũraga muoyo nĩ ũndũ wa Baba, noguo mũndũ ũrĩa ũndĩĩaga agaatũũra muoyo nĩ ũndũ wakwa. <verse number="58" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:58 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 6:49-51">Joh 6:49-51</ref></char></note>Ũyũ nĩguo mũgate ũrĩa waikũrũkire kuuma igũrũ. Maithe manyu maarĩire mana na nĩmakuire, no ũrĩa ũrĩĩaga mũgate ũyũ egũtũũra tene na tene.” <verse number="59" style="v"/>Maũndũ macio aamaaririe rĩrĩa aarutanaga thunagogi-inĩ kũu Kaperinaumu.</para>
  <para style="s1">Arutwo Aingĩ Gũtiganĩria Jesũ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="60" style="v"/>Arutwo ake aingĩ maigua ũguo makiuga atĩrĩ, “Ũyũ nĩ ũrutani mũritũ mũno, nũũ ũngĩhota kũwĩtĩkĩra?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="61" style="v"/>Jesũ amenya atĩ arutwo ake nĩmangʼongʼoraga nĩ ũndũ wa ũhoro ũcio akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Kaĩ ũhoro ũcio wamũrakaria? <verse number="62" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:62 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 3:13">Joh 3:13</ref></char></note>Ĩ mũngĩkĩona Mũrũ wa Mũndũ akĩambata igũrũ kũrĩa aarĩ mbere! <verse number="63" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:63 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2CO 3:6">2Akor 3:6</ref></char></note>Roho aheanaga muoyo; mwĩrĩ ndũrĩ kĩene. Ciugo iria ndamwarĩria nĩ roho na nĩcio muoyo. <verse number="64" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:64 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 2:25">Joh 2:25</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 10:4">Math 10:4</ref></char></note>No nĩ kũrĩ amwe anyu matarĩ maretĩkia.” Nĩgũkorwo kuuma o kĩambĩrĩria Jesũ nĩooĩ arĩa matetĩkĩtie, na ũrĩa ũkaamũkunyanĩra. <verse number="65" style="v"/>Agĩthiĩ na mbere, akiuga atĩrĩ, “Nĩkĩo ndamwĩrire atĩ gũtirĩ mũndũ ũngĩhota gũũka kũrĩ niĩ atahotithĩtio nĩ Baba.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="66" style="v"/>Kuuma hĩndĩ ĩyo, arutwo ake aingĩ makĩhũndũka, na matiacookire kũmũrũmĩrĩra.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="67" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:67 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 10:2">Math 10:2</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Jesũ akĩũria arĩa ikũmi na eerĩ atĩrĩ, “O na inyuĩ kaĩ mũrenda gũthiĩ?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="68" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:68 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 16:16">Math 16:16</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake Simoni Petero akĩmũcookeria, atĩrĩ, “Mwathani, tũngĩthiĩ kũrĩ ũ? Wee nĩwe ũrĩ na ciugo cia muoyo wa tene na tene. <verse number="69" style="v"/>Nĩtwĩtĩkĩtie na tũkamenya atĩ wee nĩwe ũrĩa Mũtheru wa Ngai.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="70" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:70 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 13:27">Joh 13:27</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Hĩndĩ ĩyo Jesũ akĩmacookeria akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Githĩ ti niĩ ndĩmũthuurĩte mũrĩ ikũmi na eerĩ? No ũmwe wanyu nĩ ndaimono!” <verse number="71" style="v"/>(Aaragia ũhoro wa Judasi mũrũ wa Simoni Isikariota, tondũ o na aakorwo aarĩ ũmwe wa acio ikũmi na eerĩ, nĩwe warĩ amũkunyanĩre thuutha ũcio.)</para>
  <chapter number="7" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Gũthiĩ Gĩathĩ gĩa Ithũnũ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>Thuutha ũcio, Jesũ nĩaceerangire Galili, nĩ ũndũ ndendaga gũthiĩ Judea tondũ Ayahudi akuo nĩmamũcaragia mamũũrage. <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LEV 23:34">Alaw 23:34</ref></char></note>No hĩndĩ ĩrĩa Gĩathĩ gĩa Ithũnũ<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">7:2 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Gĩathĩ gĩa Ithũnũ kĩamaririkanagia ũrĩa maatũũrĩte morũũraga werũ-inĩ, o hamwe na wega wa Ngai wa kũmakinyia Kaanani.</char></note> kĩa Ayahudi gĩakuhĩrĩirie-rĩ, <verse number="3" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:3 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 12:46">Math 12:46</ref></char></note>ariũ a nyina na Jesũ makĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Nĩwagĩrĩirwo uume gũkũ ũthiĩ Judea, nĩguo arutwo aku mone ciama iria ũringaga. <verse number="4" style="v"/>Gũtirĩ mũndũ wendaga kũmenyeka nĩ andũ ũhithaga ũrĩa areeka. Na tondũ nĩũreeka maũndũ maya-rĩ, wĩonanie kũrĩ kĩrĩndĩ.” <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:5 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MRK 3:21">Mar 3:21</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo o na ariũ a nyina matiamwĩtĩkĩtie.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio, Jesũ akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Ihinda rĩakwa rĩrĩa rĩagĩrĩire rĩtirĩ rĩrakinya; no harĩ inyuĩ ihinda o rĩothe nĩrĩagĩrĩire. <verse number="7" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:7 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 15:18-19">Joh 15:18-19</ref></char></note>Andũ a gũkũ thĩ matingĩmũthũũra, no niĩ nĩmathũire tondũ nĩnyumbũraga atĩ ũrĩa mekaga nĩ ũũru. <verse number="8" style="v"/>Inyuĩ thiĩi Gĩathĩ-inĩ. Niĩ ndikwamba kwambata Gĩathĩ-inĩ kĩu, nĩgũkorwo ihinda rĩakwa rĩrĩa rĩagĩrĩru rĩtirĩ rĩrakinya.” <verse number="9" style="v"/>Na aarĩkia kuuga ũguo, agĩikara kũu Galili.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>No rĩrĩ, thuutha wa ariũ a nyina gũthiĩ Gĩathĩ-inĩ kĩu, o nake agĩcooka agĩthiĩ, no ndaathiire akĩmenyekaga, no aathiire na hitho. <verse number="11" style="v"/>Na rĩrĩ, kũu Gĩathĩ-inĩ-rĩ, Ayahudi nĩmamũcaragia, makĩũranagia atĩrĩ, “Mũndũ ũcio arĩ ha?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">7:12 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 7:40-43">Joh 7:40-43</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Kũu mũingĩ-inĩ guothe andũ nĩmaragia na mĩheehũ ũhoro wake. Amwe makoiga atĩrĩ, “Mũndũ ũcio nĩ mũndũ mwega.”</para>
  <para style="p">Nao arĩa angĩ makoiga atĩrĩ, “Aca, mũndũ ũcio nĩaheenagia andũ.” <verse number="13" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:13 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 9:22">Joh 9:22</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 12:42">12:42</ref></char></note>No gũtirĩ mũndũ ũngĩaririe ũhoro wake akĩiguagwo nĩ ũndũ wa gwĩtigĩra Ayahudi.</para>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Kũrutana Gĩathĩ-inĩ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>Gĩathĩ gĩakinya gatagatĩ-rĩ, Jesũ akĩambata agĩthiĩ nja-inĩ cia hekarũ, akĩambĩrĩria kũrutana. <verse number="15" style="v"/>Nao Ayahudi makĩgega, makĩũrania atĩrĩ, “Mũndũ ũyũ aamenyeire maũndũ maya kũ, na ndathomete?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">7:16 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 14:24">Joh 14:24</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akĩmacookeria atĩrĩ, “Ũrutani ũrĩa ndutanaga ti wakwa niĩ mwene. Uumaga kũrĩ ũrĩa wandũmire. <verse number="17" style="v"/>Mũndũ o wothe angĩenda gwĩka wendi wa Ngai, ũcio nĩarĩĩmenyaga kana ũrutani wakwa uumaga kũrĩ Ngai, kana njaragia ũhoro wakwa mwene. <verse number="18" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:18 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 5:41">Joh 5:41</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 8:50">8:50</ref>, <ref loc="JHN 8:54">54</ref></char></note>Mũndũ ũrĩa waragia ũhoro wake we mwene eekaga ũguo nĩgeetha egoocithie we mwene, no ũrĩa ũrutaga wĩra nĩgeetha agoocithie ũrĩa ũmũtũmĩte nĩ mũndũ wa ma; gũtirĩ ũndũ wa maheeni ũmũkoniĩ. <verse number="19" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:19 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 1:17">Joh 1:17</ref></char></note>Githĩ Musa ndaamũheire watho? No gũtirĩ o na ũmwe wanyu ũmenyagĩrĩra watho. Mũrageria kũnjũraga nĩkĩ?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>Naguo mũingĩ wa andũ ũkĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Wee ũrĩ na ndaimono. Nũũ ũrageria gũkũũraga?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>Nake Jesũ akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Ndaaringire kĩama kĩmwe, na inyuĩ inyuothe mũkĩgega. <verse number="22" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:22 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GEN 17:10-14">Kĩam 17:10-14</ref></char></note>No rĩrĩ, tondũ Musa nĩamũheire ũhoro wa kũrua (o na gũtuĩka ũhoro ũcio ndwoimire kũrĩ Musa, no woimĩte kũrĩ maithe manyu ma tene-rĩ), inyuĩ nĩ mũruithagia mwana mũthenya wa Thabatũ. <verse number="23" style="v"/>Rĩu angĩkorwo mwana no aruithio mũthenya wa Thabatũ nĩgeetha watho wa Musa ndũgathaahio-rĩ, mũrakĩndakarĩra nĩkĩ nĩkũhonia mũndũ mũthenya wa Thabatũ? <verse number="24" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:24 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 8:15">Joh 8:15</ref></char></note>Tigai gũtuanagĩra ciira na ũrĩa mũndũ atariĩ, tuanagĩrai ciira na kĩhooto.”</para>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ nĩwe Kristũ?</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v"/>Tondũ ũcio andũ amwe a kũu Jerusalemu makĩambĩrĩria kũũrania atĩrĩ, “Githĩ ũyũ tiwe mũndũ ũrĩa marageria kũũraga? <verse number="26" style="v"/>Na rĩu araaria atekwĩhitha, na matirĩ ũndũ maramwĩra. Kaĩ anene mamenyete kũna atĩ ũyũ nĩwe Kristũ? <verse number="27" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:27 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 13:55">Math 13:55</ref></char></note>No ithuĩ nĩtũũĩ kũrĩa mũndũ ũyũ oimĩte; rĩrĩa Kristũ agooka, gũtirĩ mũndũ ũkaamenya kũrĩa agaakorwo oimĩte.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v"/>Tondũ ũcio Jesũ, o akĩrutanaga kũu hekarũ-inĩ, akĩanĩrĩra, akiuga atĩrĩ; “Ĩĩ nĩguo, nĩmũnjũũĩ, na mũkamenya kũrĩa nyumĩte. Ndiũkĩte gũkũ nĩ ũndũ wakwa niĩ mwene, no ũrĩa wandũmire nĩ wa ma. Inyuĩ mũtimũũĩ, <verse number="29" style="v"/>no niĩ nĩndĩmũũĩ, tondũ nyumĩte kũrĩ we, na nĩwe wandũmire.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">7:30 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 10:39">Joh 10:39</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 26:18">Math 26:18</ref></char>
    </note>Maigua ũguo makĩgeria kũmũnyiita, no gũtirĩ o na ũmwe wamũhutirie, tondũ ihinda rĩake rĩtiarĩ ikinyu. <verse number="31" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:31 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 8:30">Joh 8:30</ref></char></note>O na kũrĩ o ũguo, andũ aingĩ makĩmwĩtĩkia. Makiuga atĩrĩ, “Hĩndĩ ĩrĩa Kristũ agooka-rĩ, nĩakaringa ciama nyingĩ gũkĩra mũndũ ũyũ?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v"/>Afarisai makĩigua andũ makĩheehana maũndũ ta macio mamũkoniĩ. Nao athĩnjĩri-Ngai arĩa anene na Afarisai magĩtũma thigari cia hekarũ ikamũnyiite.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">7:33 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 13:33">Joh 13:33</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 16:16">16:16</ref></char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akiuga atĩrĩ, “Niĩ ngũkorwo na inyuĩ o ihinda inini, njooke thiĩ kũrĩ ũrĩa wandũmire. <verse number="34" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:34 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 8:21">Joh 8:21</ref></char></note>Inyuĩ mũkaanjaria, no mũtikanyona; na kũrĩa ngaakorwo, mũtikahota gũkinya.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">7:35 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JAS 1:1">Jak 1:1</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 12:20">Joh 12:20</ref></char>
    </note>Ayahudi makĩĩrana atĩrĩ, “Mũndũ ũyũ nĩ kũ arenda gũthiĩ, kũu tũtangĩhota kũmuona? Hihi egũthiĩ kũrĩa andũ aitũ matũũraga mahurunjũkĩte gatagatĩ ka Ayunani, akarute Ayunani ũhoro? <verse number="36" style="v"/>Nĩ atĩa ekwendaga kuuga, rĩrĩa oigire atĩ, ‘Mũkaanjaria no mũtikanyona’ na ‘kũrĩa ngaakorwo mũtikahota gũkinya’?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="37" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">7:37 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LEV 23:36">Alaw 23:36</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 55:1">Isa 55:1</ref></char>
    </note>Mũthenya wa mũthia, na ũrĩa warĩ mũnene wa Gĩathĩ kĩu-rĩ, Jesũ akĩrũgama, akĩanĩrĩra na mũgambo mũnene, akiuga atĩrĩ, “Mũndũ ũrĩa ũnyootiĩ-rĩ, nĩoke harĩ niĩ anyue. <verse number="38" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:38 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 3:15">Joh 3:15</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 58:11">Isa 58:11</ref></char></note>Ũrĩa wothe ũnjĩtĩkĩtie, thĩinĩ wake nĩkũriumaga njũũĩ cia maaĩ marĩ muoyo, o ta ũrĩa Maandĩko moigĩte.” <verse number="39" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:39 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JOL 2:28">Joel 2:28</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 12:23">Joh 12:23</ref></char></note>Akĩaria ũguo aaragia ũhoro wa Roho, ũrĩa arĩa maamwĩtĩkĩtie makaheo thuutha-inĩ. Amu hĩndĩ ĩyo Roho ndaaheanĩtwo, nĩgũkorwo Jesũ ndaagoocithĩtio.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="40" style="v"/>Hĩndĩ ĩrĩa andũ maiguire ciugo ciake, amwe makiuga atĩrĩ, “Ti-itherũ mũndũ ũyũ nĩ we Mũnabii ũrĩa.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="41" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">7:41 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 1:46">Joh 1:46</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Arĩa angĩ makiuga atĩrĩ, “Ũyũ nĩwe Kristũ.”</para>
  <para style="p">Nao angĩ makĩũria atĩrĩ, “Kwahoteka atĩa Kristũ oime Galili? <verse number="42" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:42 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MIC 5:2">Mik 5:2</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 2:5-6">Math 2:5-6</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 2:4">Luk 2:4</ref></char></note>Githĩ Maandĩko matiugĩte atĩ Kristũ akoima rũciaro-inĩ rwa Daudi, na oime Bethilehemu itũũra rĩrĩa Daudi aatũũraga?” <verse number="43" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio gũkĩgĩa na nyamũkano gatagatĩ-inĩ ka andũ acio nĩ ũndũ wa Jesũ. <verse number="44" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:44 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 7:30">Joh 7:30</ref></char></note>Amwe nĩmendaga kũmũnyiita, no gũtirĩ o na ũmwe wamũhutirie.</para>
  <para style="s1">Atongoria a Ayahudi Kwaga Gwĩtĩkia</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="45" style="v"/>Marigĩrĩrio-inĩ arangĩri a hekarũ magĩcooka kũrĩ athĩnjĩri-Ngai arĩa anene na Afarisai, nao makĩmooria atĩrĩ, “Mwaga kũmũrehe nĩkĩ?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="46" style="v"/>Arangĩri acio magĩcookia atĩrĩ, “Gũtirĩ mũndũ o na ũmwe ũrĩ waria ta ũrĩa mũndũ ũcio aragia.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="47" style="v"/>Nao Afarisai makĩmooria atĩrĩ, “Mũroiga atĩ o na inyuĩ nĩamũheenetie? <verse number="48" style="v"/>Nĩ kũrĩ mũnene o na ũmwe kana Mũfarisai ũmwĩtĩkĩtie? <verse number="49" style="v"/>Aca! No gĩkundi gĩkĩ kĩa andũ matooĩ watho-rĩ, nĩkĩnyiite nĩ kĩrumi.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="50" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">7:50 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 3:1">Joh 3:1</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 19:39">19:39</ref></char>
    </note>Nikodemo, ũrĩa wathiĩte kũrĩ Jesũ mbere ĩyo na aarĩ ũmwe wa gĩkundi kĩao, akĩũria atĩrĩ, <verse number="51" style="v"/>“Watho witũ nĩũtuagĩra mũndũ ciira ataambĩte gũthikĩrĩrio nĩguo akamenyeka ũrĩa ekĩte?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="52" style="v"/>Nao makĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “O nawe kaĩ uumĩte Galili? Tuĩria ũhoro, na nĩũkũmenya atĩ mũnabii ndangiuma Galili.”</para>
  <para style="s2">(Maandĩko mamwe ma tene matirĩ gacunjĩ gaka kuuma Johana 7:53–8:11)</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="53" style="v"/>(O mũndũ akĩinũka gwake mũciĩ.</para>
  <chapter number="8" style="c"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>No rĩrĩ, Jesũ agĩthiĩ Kĩrĩma-inĩ kĩa Mĩtamaiyũ. <verse number="2" style="v"/>Na rũciinĩ tene akĩroka o rĩngĩ kũu nja cia hekarũ, kũrĩa andũ othe maamũrigiicĩirie. Nake agĩikara thĩ kũmaruta. <verse number="3" style="v"/>Arutani a watho hamwe na Afarisai makĩrehe mũtumia wanyiitĩtwo agĩtharia. Makĩmũrũgamia hau mbere ya gĩkundi, <verse number="4" style="v"/>na makĩĩra Jesũ atĩrĩ, “Mũrutani, mũtumia ũyũ aanyiitwo agĩtharia. <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">8:5 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LEV 20:10">Alaw 20:10</ref>; <ref loc="DEU 22:22">Gũcook 22:22</ref></char></note>Thĩinĩ wa watho-rĩ, Musa aatwathire tũhũũrage atumia ta aya na mahiga nyuguto. Rĩu we ũkuuga atĩa?” <verse number="6" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">8:6 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 22:5">Math 22:5</ref>, <ref loc="MAT 22:18">18</ref></char></note>Maahũthagĩra kĩũria gĩkĩ kĩrĩ ta mũtego, nĩgeetha magĩe na ũndũ wa kũmũthitangĩra.</para>
  <para style="p">No Jesũ akĩinamĩrĩra, na akĩambĩrĩria kwandĩka thĩ na kĩara gĩake. <verse number="7" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">8:7 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="DEU 17:7">Gũcook 17:7</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 2:1">Arom 2:1</ref>, <ref loc="ROM 2:22">22</ref></char></note>Na rĩrĩa maathiire na mbere kũmũũria ũhoro ũcio, akĩinamũka, akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Angĩkorwo harĩ na ũmwe wanyu ũtarĩ ehia-rĩ, nĩatuĩke wa mbere kũmũikĩria ihiga.” <verse number="8" style="v"/>Agĩcooka akĩinamĩrĩra rĩngĩ, akĩandĩka thĩ na kĩara.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>Rĩrĩa maiguire ũguo, makĩambĩrĩria kwehera hau ũmwe kwa ũmwe, maambĩrĩirie na arĩa akũrũ, nginya hagĩtigara o Jesũ na mũtumia ũcio arũngiĩ o hau. <verse number="10" style="v"/>Jesũ akĩinamũka, akĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Mũtumia ũyũ, agũthitangi marĩ ha? Hatirĩ o na ũmwe wao wagũtuĩra?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">8:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 3:17">Joh 3:17</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 5:14">Joh 5:14</ref></char>
    </note>Nake akĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Mũthuuri ũyũ, gũtirĩ o na ũmwe.”</para>
  <para style="p">Nake Jesũ akiuga atĩrĩ, “O na niĩ ndigũgũtuĩra. Thiĩ, na ndũkanacooke kwĩhia.”)</para>
  <para style="s1">Ũira wa Jesũ nĩ wa Ma</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">8:12 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 6:35">Joh 6:35</ref>; <ref loc="PRO 4:18">Thim 4:18</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 5:14">Math 5:14</ref></char>
    </note>Rĩrĩa Jesũ aarĩirie andũ rĩngĩ, akiuga atĩrĩ, “Niĩ nĩ niĩ ũtheri wa thĩ. Ũrĩa wothe ũnũmagĩrĩra ndarĩ hĩndĩ arĩthiiaga na nduma, no arĩgĩaga na ũtheri wa muoyo.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">8:13 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 5:31">Joh 5:31</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nao Afarisai makĩmũkararia, makĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “We ũraheana ũira waku wee mwene; ũira waku ti wa ma.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">8:14 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 13:13">Joh 13:13</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ agĩcookia atĩrĩ, “O na ingĩruta ũira wakwa niĩ mwene-rĩ, ũira wakwa nĩ wa ma, nĩgũkorwo nĩnjũũĩ kũrĩa ndoimire o na kũrĩa ndĩrathiĩ. No inyuĩ mũtiũĩ kũrĩa nyumĩte kana kũrĩa ndĩrathiĩ. <verse number="15" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">8:15 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 7:24">Joh 7:24</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 3:17">Joh 3:17</ref></char></note>Inyuĩ mũtuanagĩra ciira na ũmũndũ; niĩ ndirĩ mũndũ nduagĩra ciira. <verse number="16" style="v"/>No o na ingĩtuanĩra ciira-rĩ, itua rĩakwa nĩrĩagĩrĩire, nĩgũkorwo ndituanagĩra ndĩ nyiki. No niĩ ndĩ na Baba, ũrĩa wandũmire. <verse number="17" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">8:17 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 18:16">Math 18:16</ref></char></note>Thĩinĩ wa watho wanyu nĩ kwandĩkĩtwo atĩ ũira wa andũ eerĩ nĩ wa ma. <verse number="18" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">8:18 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 5:37">Joh 5:37</ref></char></note>Niĩ ndĩraruta ũira wakwa mwene; nake mũira wakwa ũcio ũngĩ nĩ Baba ũrĩa wandũmire.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">8:19 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 16:3">Joh 16:3</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Ningĩ makĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Thoguo arĩ kũ?”</para>
  <para style="p">Nake Jesũ akĩmacookeria atĩrĩ, “Inyuĩ mũtinjũũĩ, o na Baba mũtimũũĩ. Korwo nĩmũnjũũĩ, o na Baba nĩmũngĩmũũĩ.” <verse number="20" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">8:20 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MRK 12:41">Mar 12:41</ref>; <ref loc="MRK 12:41">Mar 12:41</ref></char></note>Nake aaragia ciugo icio akĩrutana hekarũ-inĩ hakuhĩ na harĩa mũhothi warutagĩrwo. No gũtirĩ mũndũ wamũnyiitire nĩ tondũ ihinda rĩake rĩtiarĩ ikinyu.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">8:21 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EZK 3:18">Ezek 3:18</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 7:34">Joh 7:34</ref></char>
    </note>O rĩngĩ Jesũ akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Nĩngwĩthiĩra, na inyuĩ nĩmũkanjaria no mũgaakua mũrĩ o mehia-inĩ manyu. Kũrĩa ngũthiĩ inyuĩ mũtingĩhota gũũka.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>Ũhoro ũcio ũgĩtũma Ayahudi morie atĩrĩ, “Kaĩ ekwĩyũraga? Hihi nĩkĩo aroiga atĩ, ‘Kũrĩa ngũthiĩ mũtingĩhota gũũka’?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">8:23 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 3:31">Joh 3:31</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nowe akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Inyuĩ mũrĩ a gũkũ thĩ, niĩ nyumĩte Igũrũ. <verse number="24" style="v"/>Inyuĩ mũrĩ a thĩ-ĩno; no niĩ ndirĩ wa thĩ-ĩno. Ndamwĩrire atĩ mũgaakua mũrĩ o mehia-inĩ manyu; mũngĩrega gwĩtĩkia ũrĩa njugaga atĩ niĩ nĩ niĩ we, ti-itherũ mũgaakua mũrĩ o mehia-inĩ manyu.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v"/>Nao makĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Wee nĩwe ũ.”</para>
  <para style="p">Nake Jesũ akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Niĩ nĩ niĩ o ũrĩa ndũũrĩte ndĩmwĩraga kuuma o kĩambĩrĩria. <verse number="26" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">8:26 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 7:28">Joh 7:28</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 3:32">Joh 3:32</ref></char></note>Ndĩ na maũndũ maingĩ ingiuga ma kũmũciirithia namo. No ũrĩa wandũmire nĩ mwĩhokeku, naguo ũrĩa njiguĩte kuuma kũrĩ we nĩguo njĩĩraga kĩrĩndĩ.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v"/>Nao matiigana kũmenya atĩ aameeraga ũhoro wa Ithe. <verse number="28" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">8:28 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 12:32">Joh 12:32</ref></char></note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio Jesũ akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Mwarĩkia kwambararia Mũrũ wa Mũndũ-rĩ, nĩguo mũkamenya ũrĩa njugaga atĩ niĩ nĩ niĩ we, na atĩ gũtirĩ ũndũ njĩkaga ndĩĩrĩte, no njaragia o ũrĩa Baba andutĩte. <verse number="29" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">8:29 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 4:34">Joh 4:34</ref></char></note>Nake ũrĩa wandũmire arĩ hamwe na niĩ; ndandigĩte ndĩ nyiki, nĩgũkorwo hĩndĩ ciothe njĩkaga maũndũ o marĩa mamũkenagia.” <verse number="30" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">8:30 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 7:31">Joh 7:31</ref></char></note>O akĩaragia-rĩ, andũ aingĩ makĩmwĩtĩkia.</para>
  <para style="s1">Ciana cia Iburahĩmu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v"/>Nake Jesũ akĩĩra Ayahudi arĩa maamwĩtĩkĩtie atĩrĩ, “Mũngĩrũmia ũrutani wakwa-rĩ, mũrĩ arutwo akwa kũna. <verse number="32" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">8:32 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2CO 3:17">2Akor 3:17</ref></char></note>Nĩ mũkaamenya ũhoro wa ma, naguo ũhoro ũcio wa ma nĩ ũkaamũkũũra.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v"/>Nao makĩmũcookeria makĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Ithuĩ tũrĩ a rũciaro rwa Iburahĩmu, na tũtirĩ twatuĩka ngombo cia mũndũ o na ũ. Ũngĩkiuga atĩa atĩ nĩtũgakũũrwo?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">8:34 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 6:16">Arom 6:16</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akĩmacookeria atĩrĩ, “Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ o ma, mũndũ o wothe wĩhagia nĩ ngombo ya mehia. <verse number="35" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">8:35 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GAL 4:30">Agal 4:30</ref></char></note>No rĩrĩ, ngombo ti ya gũtũũra mũciĩ nginya tene no mũriũ wa mwene mũciĩ nĩ wa gũtũũra mũciĩ nginya tene. <verse number="36" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio Mũrũ wa Ngai angĩkamũkũũra-rĩ, nĩmũgakũũrwo kũna. <verse number="37" style="v"/>Nĩnjũũĩ mũrĩ a rũciaro rwa Iburahĩmu, no nĩmwĩharĩirie kũnjũraga, tondũ ũhoro wakwa ndũrĩ na ũikaro thĩinĩ wanyu. <verse number="38" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">8:38 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 5:19">Joh 5:19</ref>, <ref loc="JHN 5:30">30</ref></char></note>Niĩ ndĩramwĩra maũndũ marĩa nyonete harĩ Baba, na inyuĩ mwĩkaga maũndũ marĩa mũiguĩte kuuma kũrĩ ithe wanyu.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="39" style="v"/>Nao makĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Iburahĩmu nĩwe ithe witũ.” Nake Jesũ akĩmeera atĩrĩ,</para>
  <para style="p">“Mũngĩrĩ ciana cia Iburahĩmu-rĩ, nĩ mũngĩĩkaga maũndũ marĩa Iburahĩmu eekaga. <verse number="40" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">8:40 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 8:26">Joh 8:26</ref></char></note>Ũrĩa kũrĩ nĩ atĩ, inyuĩ nĩmũtuĩte itua rĩa kũnjũraga, o niĩ mũndũ ũrĩa ũmũheete ũhoro ũrĩa wa ma, o ũrĩa ndaiguire kuuma kũrĩ Ngai. Ũguo tiguo Iburahĩmu eekaga. <verse number="41" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">8:41 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 63:16">Isa 63:16</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 64:8">64:8</ref></char></note>Inyuĩ mũreka maũndũ marĩa ithe wanyu ekaga.”</para>
  <para style="p">Nao makĩmũkararia makĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Ithuĩ tũtirĩ ciana ciumanĩte na ũtharia. Ithuĩ tũrĩ na Baba ũmwe tu, na nĩwe Ngai.”</para>
  <para style="s1">Ciana cia Mũcukani</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="42" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">8:42 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1JN 5:1">1Joh 5:1</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 7:28">Joh 7:28</ref></char>
    </note>Jesũ akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Ngai angĩrĩ Ithe wanyu-rĩ, no mũnyende, nĩgũkorwo ndoimire kũrĩ Ngai, na rĩu ndĩ gũkũ. Ti niĩ mwene ndĩĩtũmĩte, no nĩwe wandũmire. <verse number="43" style="v"/>Mũraga gũtaũkĩrwo nĩ ũrĩa ndĩroiga nĩkĩ? Tondũ mũtirahota kũmenya ũhoro ũrĩa ndĩraria. <verse number="44" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">8:44 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1JN 3:8">1Joh 3:8</ref>; <ref loc="2CH 18:21">2Maũ 18:21</ref></char></note>Inyuĩ mũrĩ ciana cia ithe wanyu, Mũcukani, na mwendaga kũhingia merirĩria ma ithe wanyu. We aarĩ mũũragani kuuma o kĩambĩrĩria. Ndathingataga ũhoro wa ma, nĩgũkorwo gũtirĩ ũhoro wa ma thĩinĩ wake. Rĩrĩa ekũheenania, aaragia rũthiomi rwake, tondũ we nĩ mũheenania, na nĩwe ithe wa maheeni. <verse number="45" style="v"/>No tondũ njaragia ũhoro wa ma-rĩ, mũtinjĩtĩkagia. <verse number="46" style="v"/>Nĩ kũrĩ mũndũ ũmwe wanyu ũngĩonania atĩ ndĩ mwĩhia? Angĩkorwo ndĩraria ũhoro wa ma-rĩ, mũregaga kũnjĩtĩkia nĩkĩ? <verse number="47" style="v"/>Ũrĩa ũrĩ wa Ngai nĩaiguaga ũrĩa Ngai oigaga. Kĩrĩa kĩgiragia mũmũigue nĩ tondũ mũtirĩ a Ngai.”</para>
  <para style="s1">Uuge wa Jesũ Igũrũ Rĩake we Mwene</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="48" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">8:48 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 10:5">Math 10:5</ref>; <ref loc="MRK 3:22">Mar 3:22</ref></char>
    </note>Nao Ayahudi makĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Githĩ tũtirĩ na kĩhooto gĩa kuuga atĩ wee ũrĩ Mũsamaria na ũrĩ na ndaimono?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="49" style="v"/>Nake Jesũ akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Niĩ ndirĩ na ndaimono, no nĩndĩĩte Baba, no inyuĩ mũtindĩĩte. <verse number="50" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">8:50 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 5:41">Joh 5:41</ref></char></note>Ndirecarĩria ũgooci wakwa niĩ mwene, no nĩ harĩ na ũmwe ũrĩa ũũcaragia, na nĩwe mũtuanĩri ciira. <verse number="51" style="v"/>Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ na ma, mũndũ o wothe angĩrũmia kiugo gĩakwa, ndarĩ hĩndĩ akona gĩkuũ.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="52" style="v"/>Ayahudi maigua ũguo, makĩgũthũka makĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Rĩu nĩtwamenya atĩ ũrĩ na ndaimono. Iburahĩmu nĩakuire o na anabii magĩkua, no wee ũroiga atĩ mũndũ o wothe angĩrũmia kiugo gĩaku, ndagacama gĩkuũ. <verse number="53" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">8:53 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 8:39">Joh 8:39</ref></char></note>Wee ũkĩrĩ mũnene gũkĩra ithe witũ Iburahĩmu? We nĩakuire o na anabii magĩkua. Kaĩ ũreciiria we ũrĩ ũ?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="54" style="v"/>Nake Jesũ akĩmacookeria atĩrĩ, “Ingĩĩgooca-rĩ, kwĩgooca gwakwa nĩ gwa tũhũ. Baba, ũrĩa muugaga atĩ nĩwe Ngai wanyu nĩwe ũngoocithagia. <verse number="55" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">8:55 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 7:28">Joh 7:28</ref>, <ref loc="JHN 7:29">29</ref></char></note>O na gũtuĩka mũtimũũĩ, niĩ nĩndĩmũũĩ. Ingiuga atĩ ndimũũĩ, ingĩtuĩka wa maheeni ta inyuĩ, no nĩndĩmũũĩ na nĩnũmĩtie kiugo gĩake. <verse number="56" style="v"/>Ithe wanyu Iburahĩmu nĩakenaga atĩ nĩakona mũthenya wakwa; na nĩawonire na agĩcanjamũka.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="57" style="v"/>Nao Ayahudi makĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Wee o na ndũkinyĩtie mĩaka mĩrongo ĩtano, na ũkoiga atĩ nĩwonete Iburahĩmu!”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="58" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">8:58 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 1:2">Joh 1:2</ref>; <ref loc="EXO 3:14">Thaam 3:14</ref></char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akĩmacookeria atĩrĩ, “Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ na ma, Iburahĩmu atanaciarwo, Niĩ ndũire!” <verse number="59" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">8:59 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EXO 17:4">Thaam 17:4</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 10:31">Joh 10:31</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 11:8">11:8</ref></char></note>Maigua ũguo makĩoya mahiga mamũhũũre namo nyuguto, no Jesũ akĩĩhitha, akiuma kũu hekarũ-inĩ.</para>
  <chapter number="9" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Kũhingũra Maitho ma Mũndũ Waciarĩtwo arĩ Mũtumumu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>Na rĩrĩa aathiiaga na njĩra-rĩ, akĩona mũndũ waciarĩtwo arĩ mũtumumu. <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">9:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 9:34">Joh 9:34</ref>; <ref loc="EZK 18:20">Ezek 18:20</ref>; <ref loc="EXO 20:5">Thaam 20:5</ref></char></note>Nao arutwo ake makĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Rabii, nũũ wehirie, nĩ mũndũ ũyũ kana nĩ aciari ake, nĩgeetha aciarwo arĩ mũtumumu?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:3 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 11:4">Joh 11:4</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akiuga atĩrĩ, “Ti mũndũ ũyũ kana aciari ake mehirie. No ũndũ ũyũ wekĩkire nĩgeetha wĩra wa Ngai wonanio mũtũũrĩre-inĩ wake. <verse number="4" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">9:4 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 11:9">Joh 11:9</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 12:35">12:35</ref></char></note>Rĩrĩa rĩothe arĩ mũthenya-rĩ, no nginya tũrute wĩra wa ũrĩa wandũmire. Ũtukũ nĩũrooka rĩrĩa gũtarĩ mũndũ ũngĩhota kũruta wĩra. <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">9:5 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 1:4">Joh 1:4</ref></char></note>Rĩrĩa ndĩ gũkũ thĩ, nĩ niĩ ũtheri wa thĩ.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MRK 7:33">Mar 7:33</ref>; <ref loc="MRK 8:23">8:23</ref></char>
    </note>Na aarĩkia kuuga ũguo, agĩtua mata thĩ, akĩringia ndoro na mata macio, na akĩmĩhaka mũndũ ũcio maitho. <verse number="7" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">9:7 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2KI 5:10">2Ath 5:10</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 35:5">Isa 35:5</ref></char></note>Akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Thiĩ ũgethambe Karia-inĩ ga Siloamu” (narĩo rĩĩtwa Siloamu nĩ kuuga Gũtũmwo.)<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">9:7 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Karia gaka kaarĩ kamwe ka mĩako ya kũrehe maaĩ Jerusalemu, na gaakĩtwo nĩ Hezekia.</char></note> Nĩ ũndũ ũcio mũndũ ũcio agĩthiĩ na agĩĩthamba, na agĩũka mũciĩ akĩonaga.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>Nao andũ a itũũra rĩake na arĩa maamuonete mbere ĩyo akĩhooya ũteithio makĩũrania atĩrĩ, “Githĩ mũndũ ũyũ ti ũrĩa ũraikaraga thĩ ahooyage ũteithio?” <verse number="9" style="v"/>Andũ amwe makiuga atĩ aarĩ we.</para>
  <para style="p">Nao arĩa angĩ makiuga atĩrĩ, “Aca, no kũhaana amũhaana.”</para>
  <para style="p">Nowe agĩkĩrĩrĩria kuuga atĩrĩ, “Nĩ niĩ mũndũ ũcio.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>Nao makĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Maitho maku makĩhingũkire atĩa?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 9:7">Joh 9:7</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake akĩmacookeria atĩrĩ, “Mũndũ ũrĩa metaga Jesũ nĩwe ũringirie ndoro aahaka maitho, anjĩĩra thiĩ ngeethambe Karia-inĩ ga Siloamu. Nĩ ũndũ ũcio ndathiĩ na ndeethamba, na ndahota kuona.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>Nao makĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Mũndũ ũcio arĩ ha?”</para>
  <para style="p">Nake akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Niĩ ndiũũĩ.”</para>
  <para style="s1">Afarisai Gũtuĩria Ũhoro wa Kũhonio kwa Mũtumumu Ũcio</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>Nao magĩtwara mũndũ ũcio warĩ mũtumumu kũrĩ Afarisai. <verse number="14" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">9:14 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 5:9">Joh 5:9</ref></char></note>Na rĩrĩ, mũthenya ũcio Jesũ aaringirie ndoro na akĩhingũra maitho ma mũndũ ũcio warĩ wa Thabatũ. <verse number="15" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio Afarisai o nao makĩmũũria ũrĩa aahotete kuona. Nake mũndũ ũcio akĩmacookeria atĩrĩ, “Aahakire ndoro maitho, na niĩ ndeethamba na rĩu nĩndĩrona.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:16 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 6:52">Joh 6:52</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nao Afarisai amwe makiuga atĩrĩ, “Mũndũ ũyũ ndoimĩte kũrĩ Ngai, nĩgũkorwo ndamenyagĩrĩra Thabatũ.”</para>
  <para style="p">No arĩa angĩ makĩũria atĩrĩ, “Mũndũ mwĩhia ahota atĩa kũringa ciama ta ici?” Nĩ ũndũ ũcio makĩamũkana.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:17 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 21:11">Math 21:11</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Mũthia-inĩ Afarisai acio makĩhũgũkĩra mũndũ ũcio warĩ mũtumumu, makĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Wee ũkuuga atĩa ha ũhoro wake? Nĩwe araahingũrire maitho.”</para>
  <para style="p">Nake mũndũ ũcio agĩcookia atĩrĩ, “Nĩ mũnabii.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>O na kũrĩ ũguo Ayahudi matiigana gwĩtĩkia ũhoro wa mũndũ ũcio atĩ aarĩ mũtumumu na atĩ nĩacookete kuona, nginya rĩrĩa maatũmanĩire aciari ake. <verse number="19" style="v"/>Makĩmooria atĩrĩ, “Ũyũ nĩ mwana wanyu? Ũyũ nĩwe mũroiga aaciarirwo arĩ mũtumumu? Rĩu ahotete atĩa kuona?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>Nao aciari ake magĩcookia atĩrĩ, “Ithuĩ tũũĩ nĩ mwana witũ na tũũĩ aaciarirwo arĩ mũtumumu. <verse number="21" style="v"/>No ũrĩa ahotete kuona, kana ũrĩa ũmũhingũrire maitho make, ithuĩ tũtiũĩ. Mũũriei nĩ mũgima, nĩekwĩyarĩrĩria.” <verse number="22" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">9:22 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 7:13">Joh 7:13</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 12:42">Joh 12:42</ref></char></note>Aciari ake moigire ũguo nĩ ũndũ wa gwĩtigĩra Ayahudi, nĩgũkorwo Ayahudi nĩmarĩkĩtie gũtua atĩ mũndũ o wothe ũngiuga atĩ Jesũ nĩwe Kristũ nĩegũikio nja ya thunagogi. <verse number="23" style="v"/>Nĩkĩo aciari ake moigire atĩrĩ, “Nĩ mũgima; mũũriei.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:24 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOS 7:19">Josh 7:19</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 9:16">Joh 9:16</ref></char>
    </note>Magĩĩta mũndũ ũcio warĩ mũtumumu hĩndĩ ya keerĩ. Makĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Goocithia Ngai. Nĩtũũĩ mũndũ ũyũ nĩ mwĩhia.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v"/>Nake agĩcookia atĩrĩ, “Niĩ ndiũĩ kana nĩ mwĩhia kana ti mwĩhia. No njũũĩ ũndũ ũyũ ũmwe; ndĩraarĩ mũtumumu na rĩu nĩndĩrona!”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v"/>Ningĩ makĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Agwĩkire atĩa? Akũhingũrire maitho atĩa?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v"/>Nake akĩmacookeria atĩrĩ, “Nĩndamwĩra ũhoro o rĩu na inyuĩ mũtinathikĩrĩria. Mũrenda kũigua rĩngĩ nĩkĩ? O na inyuĩ nĩmũkwenda gũtuĩka arutwo ake?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:28 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 5:45">Joh 5:45</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nao makĩmũruma, makĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Wee ũrĩ mũrutwo wa mũndũ ũyũ! Ithuĩ tũrĩ arutwo a Musa! <verse number="29" style="v"/>Ithuĩ nĩtũũĩ atĩ Ngai nĩarĩirie Musa, no ha ũhoro wa mũndũ ũyũ-rĩ, tũtiũĩ o na kũrĩa oimĩte.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v"/>Nake mũndũ ũcio akĩmacookeria atĩrĩ, “Kaĩ ũcio nĩ ũrirũ-ĩ! Inyuĩ mũtiũĩ kũrĩa oimĩte, na nĩwe ũũhingũrire maitho. <verse number="31" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">9:31 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 34:15">Thab 34:15</ref>, <ref loc="PSA 34:16">16</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 1:15">Isa 1:15</ref></char></note>Nĩtũũĩ atĩ Ngai ndathikagĩrĩria andũ ehia. Athikagĩrĩria mũndũ ũrĩa ũrĩ na ũngai na ũrĩa wĩkaga wendi wake. <verse number="32" style="v"/>Gũtirĩ mũndũ ũrĩ waigua ũhoro wa mũndũ ũhingũrĩtwo maitho aciarĩtwo arĩ mũtumumu. <verse number="33" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">9:33 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 9:16">Joh 9:16</ref></char></note>Korwo mũndũ ũyũ ndoimĩte kũrĩ Ngai ndarĩ ũndũ angĩhota gwĩka.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:34 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 9:2">Joh 9:2</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Igũrũ rĩa ũhoro ũcio magĩcookia atĩrĩ, “Wee waciarirwo ũrĩ na mehia. Ũngĩkĩgeria atĩa gũtũruta!” Nao makĩmũikania na kũu nja.</para>
  <para style="s1">Ũtumumu wa Kĩĩroho</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v"/>Jesũ nĩaiguire atĩ nĩmaikĩtie mũndũ ũcio nja, na rĩrĩa aamuonire akĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Wee nĩwĩtĩkĩtie Mũrũ wa Mũndũ?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="36" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:36 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 10:14">Arom 10:14</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake mũndũ ũcio akĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Mũthuuri ũyũ, ũcio nĩwe ũ? Njĩĩra, nĩgeetha ndĩmwĩtĩkie.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="37" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:37 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 4:26">Joh 4:26</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akiuga atĩrĩ, “Rĩu nĩũmuonete; nĩwe ũyũ ũraaria nawe.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="38" style="v"/>Nake mũndũ ũcio akiuga atĩrĩ, “Mwathani, nĩndetĩkia,” na akĩmũthathaiya.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="39" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:39 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 5:22">Joh 5:22</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 13:13">Math 13:13</ref></char>
    </note>Ningĩ Jesũ akiuga atĩrĩ, “Njũkĩte gũkũ thĩ nĩ ũndũ wa gũtuanĩra ciira, nĩgeetha arĩa atumumu mahote kuona, nao arĩa monaga matuĩke atumumu.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="40" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:40 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 2:19">Arom 2:19</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Afarisai amwe arĩa maarĩ nake makĩigua akiuga ũguo, nao makĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Atĩ atĩa? O na ithuĩ tũrĩ atumumu?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="41" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:41 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 15:22">Joh 15:22</ref>, <ref loc="JHN 15:24">24</ref></char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akĩmacookeria atĩrĩ, “Mũngĩrĩ atumumu-rĩ, mũtingĩrĩ na mehia; no rĩu tondũ muugaga atĩ nĩmuonaga-rĩ, mũgũikara o na wĩhia wanyu.”</para>
  <chapter number="10" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Mũrĩithi na Rũũru Rwake</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>“Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ na ma, mũndũ ũrĩa ũtatoonyaga gĩcegũ kĩa ngʼondu agereire kĩhingo-inĩ, no akahaicĩra handũ hangĩ-rĩ, ũcio nĩ mũici na nĩ mũtunyani. <verse number="2" style="v"/>Mũndũ ũrĩa ũtoonyaga na kĩhingo nĩwe mũrĩithi wa ngʼondu ciake. <verse number="3" style="v"/>Mũrangĩri nĩamũhingũragĩra kĩhingo, nacio ngʼondu nĩithikagĩrĩria mũgambo wake. Eetaga ngʼondu ciake na marĩĩtwa, na agaciumagaria. <verse number="4" style="v"/>Aarĩkia kuumia iria irĩ ciake ciothe-rĩ, acitongoragia, nacio ngʼondu ciake ikamũrũmĩrĩra, tondũ nĩciũĩ mũgambo wake. <verse number="5" style="v"/>No itirĩ hĩndĩ ingĩrũmĩrĩra mũgeni; ũrĩa kũrĩ nĩ atĩ nĩikũmũũrĩra, tondũ itiũĩ mũgambo wa mũgeni.” <verse number="6" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:6 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MRK 9:32">Mar 9:32</ref></char></note>Jesũ aahũthĩrire ngerekano ĩyo, no matiigana gũtaũkĩrwo nĩ ũrĩa aameeraga.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio Jesũ akiuga o rĩngĩ atĩrĩ, “Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ na ma, Niĩ nĩ niĩ kĩhingo kĩa ngʼondu. <verse number="8" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:8 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JER 23:1">Jer 23:1</ref>, <ref loc="JER 23:2">2</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 10:1">Joh 10:1</ref></char></note>Arĩa othe mookire mbere yakwa maarĩ aici na atunyani, no ngʼondu itiigana kũmathikĩrĩria. <verse number="9" style="v"/>Niĩ nĩ niĩ kĩhingo; ũrĩa wothe ũtoonyagĩra harĩ niĩ nĩakahonoka. Agaatoonyaga na akoima, na onage gĩa kũrĩa. <verse number="10" style="v"/>Mũici okaga tu nĩgeetha aiye, na orage, na anange; niĩ njũkĩte nĩguo magĩe na muoyo, na magĩe naguo kũna.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 40:11">Isa 40:11</ref>; <ref loc="HEB 13:20">Ahib 13:20</ref></char>
    </note>“Niĩ nĩ niĩ mũrĩithi ũrĩa mwega. Mũrĩithi ũrĩa mwega arutaga muoyo wake nĩ ũndũ wa ngʼondu. <verse number="12" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:12 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EZK 11:16-17">Ezek 11:16-17</ref></char></note>Mũrĩithi wa mũcaara tiwe mũrĩithi ũrĩa mwene ngʼondu. Nĩ ũndũ ũcio rĩrĩa ona njũũi ĩgĩũka, atiganagĩria ngʼondu, akoora. Hĩndĩ ĩyo nayo njũũi ĩgatharĩkĩra rũũru, ĩkarũhurunja. <verse number="13" style="v"/>Mũndũ ũcio oraga tondũ we nĩ wa kwandĩkwo, na ndarũmbũyanagia na ũhoro wa ngʼondu.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>“Niĩ nĩ niĩ mũrĩithi ũrĩa mwega; nĩnjũũĩ ngʼondu ciakwa, nacio ngʼondu ciakwa nĩcinjũũĩ, <verse number="15" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:15 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 11:27">Math 11:27</ref></char></note>o ta ũrĩa Baba anjũũĩ, na niĩ ngamenya Baba, na nĩndutĩte muoyo wakwa nĩ ũndũ wa ngʼondu. <verse number="16" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:16 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 56:8">Isa 56:8</ref>; <ref loc="EPH 2:11-19">Aef 2:11-19</ref></char></note>Ndĩ na ngʼondu ingĩ iria itarĩ cia gĩcegũ gĩkĩ. No nginya o nacio ndĩcirehe. O nacio nĩigathikĩrĩria mũgambo wakwa, na gũgaakorwo na rũũru rũmwe, na mũrĩithi ũmwe. <verse number="17" style="v"/>Gĩtũmi kĩa Baba kũnyenda nĩ ũndũ nĩndutĩte muoyo wakwa nĩgeetha njooke ndĩwoe rĩngĩ. <verse number="18" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:18 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 15:10">Joh 15:10</ref></char></note>Gũtirĩ mũndũ ũngĩndunya guo, no niĩ ngũũruta na kwĩyendera. Ndĩ na ũhoti wa kũũruta, o na ũhoti wa kũwoya rĩngĩ. Watho ũyũ ndaamũkĩrire kuuma kũrĩ Baba.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>Maigua ciugo icio, Ayahudi makĩamũkana o rĩngĩ. <verse number="20" style="v"/>Aingĩ ao makiuga atĩrĩ, “Mũndũ ũyũ arĩ na ndaimono na akagũrũka. Mũkũmũthikĩrĩria nĩkĩ?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:21 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EXO 4:11">Thaam 4:11</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 9:32">Joh 9:32</ref>, <ref loc="JHN 9:33">33</ref></char>
    </note>No angĩ makiuga atĩrĩ, “Ĩno ti mĩario ya mũndũ ũrĩ na ndaimono. Ndaimono no ĩhingũre maitho ma mũtumumu?”</para>
  <para style="s1">Kwaga gwĩtĩkia kwa Ayahudi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>Ningĩ gũkĩgĩa na Gĩathĩ gĩa Kwamũrwo kũu Jerusalemu. Kwarĩ kĩmera kĩa heho, <verse number="23" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:23 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 3:11">Atũm 3:11</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 5:12">5:12</ref></char></note>nake Jesũ aarĩ hekarũ-inĩ agĩceraceera gĩthaku-inĩ gĩa Solomoni. <verse number="24" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:24 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 1:19">Joh 1:19</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 22:67">Luk 22:67</ref></char></note>Nao Ayahudi makĩmũrigiicĩria makĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Ũgũtũũra ũtũigĩte na nganja nginya rĩ? Angĩkorwo nĩwe Kristũ-rĩ, twĩre ũtekũhitha.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:25 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 5:36">Joh 5:36</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akĩmacookeria atĩrĩ, “Nĩndĩmwĩrĩte, no mũtiĩtĩkagia. Ciama iria ningaga na rĩĩtwa rĩa Baba nĩcinjaragĩrĩria, <verse number="26" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:26 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 8:47">Joh 8:47</ref></char></note>no inyuĩ mũtiĩtĩkagia tondũ mũtirĩ ngʼondu ciakwa. <verse number="27" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:27 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 10:14">Joh 10:14</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 10:4">Joh 10:4</ref></char></note>Ngʼondu ciakwa nĩithikagĩrĩria mũgambo wakwa; nĩndĩciũĩ, nacio nĩcinũmagĩrĩra. <verse number="28" style="v"/>Nĩndĩciheaga muoyo wa tene na tene, na gũtirĩ hĩndĩ ikoora; gũtirĩ mũndũ o na ũmwe ũngĩcigutha kuuma moko-inĩ makwa. <verse number="29" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:29 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 17:26">Joh 17:26</ref></char></note>Baba ũrĩa waheire cio, nĩ mũnene kũrĩ othe; gũtirĩ mũndũ ũngĩcigutha kuuma moko-inĩ ma Baba. <verse number="30" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:30 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 17:21-23">Joh 17:21-23</ref></char></note>Niĩ na Baba tũrĩ ũmwe.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:31 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 8:59">Joh 8:59</ref>
      </char>
    </note>O rĩngĩ Ayahudi makĩoya mahiga nĩguo mamũhũũre namo nyuguto, <verse number="32" style="v"/>nake Jesũ akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Nĩndĩmuonetie ciama nyingĩ nene kuuma kũrĩ Baba. Nĩ kĩama kĩrĩkũ gĩacio mũrenda kũũhũrĩra na mahiga nyuguto?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:33 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 5:18">Joh 5:18</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nao Ayahudi makĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Tũtirakũhũũra na mahiga nyuguto nĩ ũndũ wa o na kĩmwe gĩacio, no nĩ ũndũ wa kũruma Ngai, tondũ wĩtuĩte Ngai na wee ũrĩ o mũndũ.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:34 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 82:6">Thab 82:6</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akĩmacookeria atĩrĩ, “Githĩ gũtiandĩkĩtwo Watho-inĩ wanyu atĩrĩ, ‘Ndoigire inyuĩ mũrĩ ngai’? <verse number="35" style="v"/>Angĩkorwo aametire ‘ngai’, o acio kiugo kĩa Ngai gĩokire kũrĩ o, (na Maandĩko matheru matingĩaga kũhingio) <verse number="36" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:36 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 3:17">Joh 3:17</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 5:17">Joh 5:17</ref>, <ref loc="JHN 5:18">18</ref></char></note>ĩ mũndũ ũrĩa Baba aamũrire arĩ wake kũna na akĩmũtũma gũkũ thĩ, ũhoro wake nĩ atĩa? Mũragĩĩthitanga nĩkĩ atĩ nĩndaruma Ngai tondũ nĩndoiga, ‘Ndĩ Mũrũ wa Ngai’? <verse number="37" style="v"/>Ingĩaga gwĩka ũrĩa Baba ekaga mũtikanjĩtĩkie. <verse number="38" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:38 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 14:10">Joh 14:10</ref>, <ref loc="JHN 14:11">11</ref></char></note>No o na ingĩĩka ũrĩa ekaga-rĩ, o na gũtuĩka mũtinjĩtĩkĩtie, ĩtĩkiai ciama icio, nĩguo mũmenye na mũtaũkĩrwo atĩ Baba arĩ thĩinĩ wakwa, na niĩ ndĩ thĩinĩ wa Baba.” <verse number="39" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:39 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 7:30">Joh 7:30</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 8:59">Joh 8:59</ref></char></note>Na o rĩngĩ makĩgeria kũmũnyiita, nowe akĩĩhonokia kuuma moko-inĩ mao.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="40" style="v"/>Ningĩ Jesũ agĩcooka mũrĩmo ũũrĩa ũngĩ wa Jorodani, harĩa Johana aabatithanagĩria matukũ-inĩ ma mbere. Agiĩkara kũu, <verse number="41" style="v"/>nao andũ aingĩ magĩũka kũrĩ we. Nao makiuga atĩrĩ, “O na gũtuĩka Johana ndarĩ kĩama aaringire, ũhoro ũrĩa wothe Johana oigire ũkoniĩ mũndũ ũyũ warĩ wa ma.” <verse number="42" style="v"/>Na andũ aingĩ a kũu magĩĩtĩkia Jesũ.</para>
  <chapter number="11" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Gĩkuũ kĩa Lazaro</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LUK 10:38">Luk 10:38</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Na rĩrĩ, kwarĩ na mũndũ wetagwo Lazaro, nake aarĩ mũrũaru. Aarĩ wa Bethania, itũũra rĩa Mariamu na mwarĩ wa nyina Maritha. <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 12:3">Joh 12:3</ref></char></note>Mariamu ũyũ nowe waitĩrĩirie Mwathani maguta manungi wega na akĩmũgiria nyarĩrĩ na njuĩrĩ yake, na aarĩ mwarĩ wa nyina na Lazaro ũcio warĩ mũrũaru. <verse number="3" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio aarĩ acio a nyina magĩtũmanĩra Jesũ akeerwo atĩrĩ, “Mwathani, ũrĩa wendete nĩmũrũaru.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:4 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 11:40">Joh 11:40</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Rĩrĩa Jesũ aiguire ũhoro ũcio, akiuga atĩrĩ, “Ndwari ĩno ndĩkũrĩĩkĩrĩra na gĩkuũ. Aca, nĩ ya kũgoocithia Ngai, nĩgeetha Mũrũ wa Ngai agoocithio nĩyo.” <verse number="5" style="v"/>Jesũ nĩendete Maritha na mwarĩ wa nyina, o na Lazaro. <verse number="6" style="v"/>No o na thuutha wa kũigua atĩ Lazaro aarĩ mũrũaru-rĩ, aikarire kũu aarĩ mĩthenya ĩngĩ ĩĩrĩ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>Agĩcooka akĩĩra arutwo ake atĩrĩ, “Nĩtũcookei Judea.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:8 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 10:31">Joh 10:31</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nao makĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “No rĩrĩ Rabii, o rĩu ica ikuhĩ Ayahudi marageragia gũkũhũũra na mahiga nyuguto, na rĩu ũrenda gũcooka kuo?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:9 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 9:4">Joh 9:4</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akĩmacookeria atĩrĩ, “Githĩ mũthenya ti wa mathaa ikũmi na meerĩ? Mũndũ ũrĩa ũthiiaga mũthenya ndangĩhĩngwo, nĩgũkorwo onaga na ũtheri wa gũkũ thĩ. <verse number="10" style="v"/>Ahĩngagwo rĩrĩa egũthiĩ ũtukũ, nĩ ũndũ ndarĩ na ũtheri.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>Aarĩkia kuuga ũguo, agĩcooka akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Mũrata witũ Lazaro nĩakomete; no nĩngũthiĩ kũu ngamũũkĩrie.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>Arutwo ake makĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Mwathani, akorwo nĩ gũkoma akomete-rĩ, nĩekũhona.” <verse number="13" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11:13 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 9:24">Math 9:24</ref></char></note>Jesũ aaragia ũhoro wa gĩkuũ gĩake, no arutwo ake meciiragia aaragia ũhoro wa toro wa ndũire.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio akĩmeera na njĩra ĩgũtaũka, atĩrĩ, “Lazaro nĩmũkuũ, <verse number="15" style="v"/>no nĩ ũndũ wanyu nĩngenete nĩgũkorwo ndiraarĩ kuo, nĩgeetha mwĩtĩkie. No rĩrĩ, nĩtũthiĩi kũrĩ we.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:16 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 10:3">Math 10:3</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake Toma (ũrĩa wetagwo Wa-mahatha) akĩĩra arutwo arĩa angĩ atĩrĩ, “Nĩtũthiĩi o na ithuĩ, tũgakuanĩre nake.”</para>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Kũũmĩrĩria Aarĩ a Nyina na Lazaro</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>Jesũ aakinya-rĩ, agĩkora Lazaro nĩaniinĩte mĩthenya ĩna thĩinĩ wa mbĩrĩra. <verse number="18" style="v"/>Na rĩrĩ, itũũra rĩa Bethania rĩtiakinyĩtie kilomita ithatũ kuuma Jerusalemu, <verse number="19" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11:19 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JOB 2:11">Ayub 2:11</ref></char></note>nao Ayahudi aingĩ nĩmokĩte kũu kwa Maritha na Mariamu kũmomĩrĩria nĩ ũndũ wa gũkuĩrwo nĩ mũrũ wa nyina wao. <verse number="20" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11:20 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 10:38-42">Luk 10:38-42</ref></char></note>Rĩrĩa Maritha aiguire atĩ Jesũ nĩarooka, akiuma, agĩthiĩ kũmũtũnga, no Mariamu agĩikara kũu mũciĩ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>Maritha akĩĩra Jesũ atĩrĩ, “Mwathani ũngĩraarĩ gũkũ-rĩ, mũrũ wa maitũ ndangĩrakuire. <verse number="22" style="v"/>No rĩrĩ, nĩnjũũĩ atĩ o na rĩu Ngai nĩegũkũhe o kĩrĩa gĩothe ũngĩhooya.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>Nake Jesũ akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Mũrũ wa maitũguo nĩekũriũka.” Nake Maritha akĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ,</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:24 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 5:28">Joh 5:28</ref>, <ref loc="JHN 5:29">29</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 6:39">Joh 6:39</ref>, <ref loc="JHN 6:40">40</ref></char>
    </note>“Nĩnjũũĩ nĩakariũka hĩndĩ ya iriũkĩro mũthenya wa mũthia.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:25 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 1:4">Joh 1:4</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Niĩ nĩ niĩ kũriũka na nĩ niĩ muoyo. Nake ũrĩa wothe ũnjĩtĩkĩtie, o na aakua, nĩagatũũra muoyo; <verse number="26" style="v"/>nake ũrĩa wothe ũtũũraga muoyo na nĩanjĩtĩkĩtie, ndarĩ hĩndĩ agaakua. Wee nĩwĩtĩkĩtie ũguo?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:27 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LUK 2:11">Luk 2:11</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 6:14">Joh 6:14</ref></char>
    </note>Nake Maritha akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Ĩĩ Mwathani, nĩnjĩtĩkĩtie atĩ wee nĩwe Kristũ, Mũrũ wa Ngai, ũrĩa wĩrĩtwo nĩagooka gũkũ thĩ.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:28 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 26:18">Math 26:18</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 13:13">Joh 13:13</ref></char>
    </note>Nake aarĩkia kuuga ũguo, agĩcooka agĩthiĩ agĩĩta mwarĩ wa nyina Mariamu keeheri-inĩ, akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Mũrutani arĩ gũkũ na nĩarakũũria.” <verse number="29" style="v"/>Rĩrĩa Mariamu aiguire ũguo, akĩrũgama na ihenya agĩthiĩ kũrĩ we. <verse number="30" style="v"/>Na hĩndĩ ĩyo Jesũ ndaakoretwo atoonyete itũũra, no aarĩ o harĩa Maritha aamũtũngĩte. <verse number="31" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11:31 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 11:19">Joh 11:19</ref></char></note>Rĩrĩa Ayahudi acio maarĩ na Mariamu kũu nyũmba makĩmũũmĩrĩria monire ũrĩa okĩra na ihenya oimĩte nja, makĩmũrũmĩrĩra, magĩĩciiria atĩ aathiiaga mbĩrĩra-inĩ akarĩrĩre ho.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:32 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 11:21">Joh 11:21</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Hĩndĩ ĩrĩa Mariamu aakinyire harĩa Jesũ aarĩ na akĩmuona, akĩgũa thĩ magũrũ-inĩ make, akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Mwathani, ũngĩraarĩ gũkũ, mũrũ wa maitũ ndangĩrakuire.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:33 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 12:27">Joh 12:27</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Hĩndĩ ĩrĩa Jesũ aamuonire akĩrĩra, na Ayahudi arĩa mokĩte hamwe nake o nao makĩrĩra-rĩ, agĩcaaya mũno roho-inĩ thĩinĩ na agĩtangĩka ngoro. <verse number="34" style="v"/>Akĩmooria atĩrĩ, “Mũmũigĩte ha?”</para>
  <para style="p">Nao makĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Mwathani, ũka wone.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:35 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LUK 19:41">Luk 19:41</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Jesũ akĩrĩra.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="36" style="v"/>Nao Ayahudi makiuga atĩrĩ, “Onei ũrĩa aramwendete!”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="37" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:37 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 9:6">Joh 9:6</ref>, <ref loc="JHN 9:7">7</ref></char>
    </note>No amwe ao makĩũrania atĩrĩ, “Mũndũ ũyũ ũrahingũrire mũtumumu maitho-rĩ, ndangĩrahotire kũgiria akue?”</para>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Kũriũkia Lazaro</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="38" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:38 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 27:60">Math 27:60</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ, o rĩngĩ acaaĩte mũno, agĩthiĩ mbĩrĩra-inĩ. Mbĩrĩra ĩyo yarĩ ngurunga na yahingĩtwo na ihiga. <verse number="39" style="v"/>Nake Jesũ akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Eheriai ihiga.”</para>
  <para style="p">No Maritha, mwarĩ wa nyina na mũndũ ũcio wakuĩte, akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Mwathani, rĩu nĩmũnungu nĩ ũndũ nĩaniinĩte mĩthenya ĩna ho.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="40" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:40 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 11:23-25">Joh 11:23-25</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 11:4">Joh 11:4</ref></char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Githĩ ndikwĩrire atĩ wetĩkia nĩũkuona riiri wa Ngai?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="41" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:41 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 17:1">Joh 17:1</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 11:25">Math 11:25</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio makĩeheria ihiga. Jesũ agĩcooka agĩtiira maitho, akiuga atĩrĩ, “Baba, nĩndagũcookeria ngaatho nĩ ũndũ nĩũnjiguaga. <verse number="42" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11:42 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 12:30">Joh 12:30</ref></char></note>Nĩnjũũĩ atĩ nĩũnjiguaga hĩndĩ ciothe, no ndoiga ũguo nĩ ũndũ wa andũ aya marũgamĩte haha, nĩguo metĩkie atĩ nĩwe wandũmire.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="43" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:43 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LUK 7:14">Luk 7:14</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Jesũ aarĩkia kuuga ũguo, akĩanĩrĩra na mũgambo mũnene, akiuga atĩrĩ, “Lazaro, uma!” <verse number="44" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11:44 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 19:40">Joh 19:40</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 20:7">Joh 20:7</ref></char></note>Nake mũndũ ũcio warĩ mũkuũ akiuma, ohetwo na ndaamĩ cia gatani moko na magũrũ, na akarigiicĩrio taama ũthiũ.</para>
  <para style="p">Jesũ akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Muohorei mataama macio ma mbĩrĩra, mũreke athiĩ.”</para>
  <para style="s1">Gũciirĩra Kũũraga Jesũ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="45" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:45 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 2:23">Joh 2:23</ref>; <ref loc="EXO 14:31">Thaam 14:31</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio Ayahudi aingĩ arĩa mokĩte gũceerera Mariamu, moona ũrĩa Jesũ eekire, makĩmwĩtĩkia. <verse number="46" style="v"/>No amwe ao magĩthiĩ kũrĩ Afarisai, makĩmeera ũrĩa Jesũ ekĩte. <verse number="47" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11:47 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 26:3">Math 26:3</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 2:11">Joh 2:11</ref></char></note>Hĩndĩ ĩyo athĩnjĩri-Ngai arĩa anene hamwe na Afarisai magĩĩta Kĩama.</para>
  <para style="p">Makĩũrania atĩrĩ, “Nĩ kĩĩ tũreka? Onei ũrĩa mũndũ ũyũ araringa ciama nyingĩ. <verse number="48" style="v"/>Twareka athiĩ na mbere ũguo, andũ othe nĩmekũmwĩtĩkia, nao Aroma moke meyoere hekarũ iitũ, o na rũrĩrĩ rwitũ.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="49" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:49 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 26:3">Math 26:3</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 18:13">Joh 18:13</ref>, <ref loc="JHN 18:14">14</ref></char>
    </note>Hĩndĩ ĩyo ũmwe wao wetagwo Kaiafa, ũrĩa warĩ mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai mũnene mwaka ũcio, akiuga atĩrĩ, “Inyuĩ mũtirĩ ũndũ mũũĩ o na atĩa! <verse number="50" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11:50 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 18:14">Joh 18:14</ref></char></note>Inyuĩ mũtiũĩ atĩ nĩ kaba mũndũ ũmwe akue nĩ ũndũ wa kĩrĩndĩ, handũ ha rũrĩrĩ ruothe rũthire.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="51" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:51 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 49:6">Isa 49:6</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Ũndũ ũcio ndaaririe etaarĩte we mwene, no aarathire ũguo arĩ ta mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai mũnene wa mwaka ũcio, atĩ Jesũ nĩagakuĩra rũrĩrĩ rwa Ayahudi, <verse number="52" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11:52 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 49:6">Isa 49:6</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 10:16">Joh 10:16</ref></char></note>na to rũrĩrĩ rũu rwiki, no o na ningĩ akue nĩ ũndũ wa ciana cia Ngai iria ciahurunjũkĩte, nĩgeetha acicookanĩrĩrie atũme ituĩke kĩndũ kĩmwe. <verse number="53" style="v"/>nĩ ũndũ ũcio kuuma mũthenya ũcio magĩciirĩra kũmũũraga.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="54" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:54 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 7:1">Joh 7:1</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio Jesũ ndaacookire gũthiĩ akĩĩonithanagia kũrĩ Ayahudi. Handũ ha ũguo, akĩehera agĩthiĩ kũndũ kwarĩ hakuhĩ na werũ, gatũũra geetagwo Efiraimu, agĩikara kuo na arutwo ake.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="55" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:55 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MRK 14:1">Mar 14:1</ref>; <ref loc="2CH 30:17">2Maũ 30:17</ref>, <ref loc="2CH 30:18">18</ref></char>
    </note>Na rĩrĩa Bathaka ya Ayahudi yakuhĩrĩirie, andũ aingĩ makĩambata kuuma matũũra-inĩ, magĩthiĩ Jerusalemu nĩ ũndũ wa igongona rĩa gwĩtheria Bathaka ĩtanakinya. <verse number="56" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11:56 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 7:11">Joh 7:11</ref></char></note>Andũ acio magĩikara magĩcaragia Jesũ, na rĩrĩa maarũngiĩ nja ya hekarũ, makĩũrania atĩrĩ, “Mũgwĩciiria atĩa? Kaĩ hihi ategũũka Gĩathĩ-inĩ?” <verse number="57" style="v"/>No athĩnjĩri-Ngai arĩa anene na Afarisai nĩmarutĩte watho atĩ mũndũ o wothe ũngĩamenyire harĩa Jesũ aarĩ, amarehere ũhoro nĩgeetha mamũnyiite.</para>
  <chapter number="12" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Kũhakwo Maguta arĩ Bethania</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 11:55">Joh 11:55</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 21:17">Math 21:17</ref></char>
    </note>Mĩthenya ĩtandatũ mbere ya Gĩathĩ kĩa Bathaka gũkinya, Jesũ agĩthiĩ Bethania, kũrĩa Lazaro ũrĩa aariũkĩtie aatũũraga. <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 10:38-42">Luk 10:38-42</ref></char></note>Nĩ kwarugirwo irio cia hwaĩ-inĩ nĩ ũndũ wa Jesũ. Maritha nĩwe watungataga, nake Lazaro aarĩ ũmwe wa arĩa maikarĩte metha-inĩ na Jesũ. <verse number="3" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:3 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 11:2">Joh 11:2</ref></char></note>Nake Mariamu akĩoya cuba ya maguta manungi wega na ma goro mũno, akĩhaka Jesũ magũrũ, agĩcooka akĩmũgiria na njuĩrĩ yake.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">12:3 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Mariamu nĩonanirie wendo mũnene nĩ ũndũ wa gũitĩrĩria Jesũ maguta macio nyarĩrĩ, na kũmũhuura na njuĩrĩ ciake.</char></note> Nayo nyũmba ĩkĩiyũra mũtararĩko mwega wa maguta macio.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>No mũrutwo ũmwe wa Jesũ wetagwo Judasi Isikariota, ũrĩa wacookire kũmũkunyanĩra, akĩregana na ũndũ ũcio, akiuga atĩrĩ, <verse number="5" style="v"/>“Nĩkĩ kĩragiririe maguta macio mendio na mbeeca icio iheo athĩĩni? Nĩmaraiganĩte mũcaara wa mwaka mũgima.” <verse number="6" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:6 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 13:29">Joh 13:29</ref></char></note>Ndoigire ũguo nĩ ũndũ wa gũcaĩra athĩĩni, no oigire ũguo nĩ ũndũ aarĩ mũici, tondũ nĩwe wakuuaga mũhuko wa mbeeca, na nĩaiyaga imwe akahũthĩra we mwene.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 19:40">Joh 19:40</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ agĩcookia atĩrĩ, “Tiganai nake, araigĩte maguta macio nĩ ũndũ wa mũthenya ũrĩa ngaathikwo. <verse number="8" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:8 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="DEU 15:11">Gũcook 15:11</ref></char></note>Athĩĩni mũrĩ nao hĩndĩ ciothe, no niĩ mũtirĩkoragwo na niĩ hĩndĩ ciothe.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:9 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 11:43">Joh 11:43</ref>, <ref loc="JHN 11:44">44</ref></char>
    </note>Ihinda-inĩ o rĩu gĩkundi kĩnene kĩa Ayahudi gĩkĩmenya atĩ Jesũ aarĩ kũu na gĩgĩũka, na gĩtiokire nĩ ũndũ wa Jesũ tu, no ningĩ nĩgeetha kĩone o na Lazaro ũcio aariũkĩtie kuuma kũrĩ arĩa akuũ. <verse number="10" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio athĩnjĩri-Ngai arĩa anene magĩthugunda kũũraga Lazaro o nake, <verse number="11" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:11 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 12:17">Joh 12:17</ref>, <ref loc="JHN 12:18">18</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 11:45">Joh 11:45</ref>; <ref loc="LEV 23:40">Alaw 23:40</ref></char></note>nĩgũkorwo nĩ ũndũ wake Ayahudi aingĩ nĩmathiiaga kũrĩ Jesũ na makamwĩtĩkia.</para>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Gũtoonya Jerusalemu na Ũhootani</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>Mũthenya ũcio ũngĩ andũ aingĩ arĩa mokĩte nĩ ũndũ wa Gĩathĩ kĩu<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">12:12 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Andũ aingĩ mũno nĩmookaga gũkũngũĩra Gĩathĩ kĩa Bathaka.</char></note> makĩigua atĩ Jesũ aarĩ njĩra-inĩ agĩthiĩ Jerusalemu. <verse number="13" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:13 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LEV 23:40">Alaw 23:40</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 118:25">Thab 118:25</ref>, <ref loc="PSA 118:26">26</ref></char></note>Magĩkuua mĩkĩndũ,<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">12:13 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Mĩkĩndũ yatũmagĩrwo gũkũngũĩra ũhootani.</char></note> magĩthiĩ namo kũmũtũnga, makĩanagĩrĩra atĩrĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">“Hosana!”</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">“Kũrathimwo-rĩ, nĩ mũndũ ũrĩa ũgũũka na rĩĩtwa rĩa Mwathani!”</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">“Kũrathimwo-rĩ, nĩ Mũthamaki wa Isiraeli!”</para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>Nake Jesũ akĩona njaũ ya ndigiri, akĩmĩikarĩra, o ta ũrĩa kwandĩkĩtwo atĩrĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:15 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ZEC 9:9">Zek 9:9</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Tiga gwĩtigĩra, wee Mwarĩ wa Zayuni;</para>
  <para style="q2">ta rora, mũthamaki waku nĩarooka,</para>
  <para style="q2">aikarĩire njaũ ya ndigiri.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:16 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MRK 9:32">Mar 9:32</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 2:22">Joh 2:22</ref></char>
    </note>Arutwo ake matiambĩte gũtaũkĩrwo nĩ gĩtũmi kĩa maũndũ macio. No Jesũ aarĩkia kũgoocithio nĩguo maataũkĩirwo atĩ maũndũ macio maandĩkĩtwo nĩ ũndũ wake, na atĩ ũguo noguo maamwĩkĩte.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>Nakĩo gĩkundi kĩa andũ kĩrĩa kĩarĩ nake rĩrĩa eetire Lazaro oime mbĩrĩra-inĩ na akĩmũriũkia kuuma kũrĩ arĩa akuũ gĩgĩthiĩ na mbere kũmemerekia ũhoro ũcio. <verse number="18" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:18 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 12:11">Joh 12:11</ref></char></note>Andũ aingĩ magĩũka gũtũnga Jesũ nĩ ũndũ nĩmaiguĩte atĩ nĩaringĩte kĩama kĩu. <verse number="19" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio Afarisai makĩĩrana atĩrĩ, “Ta kĩonei tũtirĩ ũndũ tũreeka. Onei ũrĩa andũ othe mamũrũmĩrĩire!”</para>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Kũratha Ũhoro wa Gĩkuũ Gĩake</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:20 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 7:35">Joh 7:35</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Na rĩrĩ, nĩ kwarĩ na Ayunani gatagatĩ-inĩ ka arĩa maathiĩte gũthathaiya Ngai Gĩathĩ-inĩ kĩu. <verse number="21" style="v"/>Nao magĩũka kũrĩ Filipu, ũrĩa woimĩte itũũra rĩa Bethisaida kũu Galili, marĩ na ihooya, makĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Mũthuuri ũyũ, no twende kuona Jesũ.” <verse number="22" style="v"/>Nake Filipu agĩthiĩ akĩĩra Anderea ũhoro ũcio, nao eerĩ magĩthiĩ makĩĩra Jesũ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:23 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 26:18">Math 26:18</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 13:32">Joh 13:32</ref></char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akĩmacookeria atĩrĩ, “Ihinda nĩrĩkinyu Mũrũ wa Mũndũ agoocithio. <verse number="24" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:24 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 15:36">1Akor 15:36</ref></char></note>Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ na ma, tiga hĩndĩ ya ngano yambire kũgũa tĩĩri-inĩ ĩkue-rĩ, ĩtũũraga ĩrĩ iiki. No ĩngĩkua, nĩĩciaraga maciaro maingĩ. <verse number="25" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:25 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 10:39">Math 10:39</ref></char></note>Mũndũ ũrĩa wendete muoyo wake nĩakoorwo nĩguo, na mũndũ ũrĩa ũthũire muoyo wake arĩ gũkũ thĩ, nĩakaũtũũria nginya muoyo wa tene na tene. <verse number="26" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:26 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 14:3">Joh 14:3</ref></char></note>Ũrĩa wothe ũndungatagĩra no nginya anũmĩrĩre, nĩgeetha harĩa ndĩ o nayo ndungata yakwa ĩgaakorwo ho. Ũrĩa ũndungatagĩra-rĩ, nake Baba nĩarĩmũtĩĩaga.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:27 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 26:38">Math 26:38</ref>, <ref loc="MAT 26:39">39</ref></char>
    </note>“Rĩu ngoro yakwa nĩĩratangĩka, na niĩ ngũkiuga atĩa? Njuge, ‘Baba honokia harĩ ihinda rĩĩrĩ’? Aca, gĩtũmi gĩkĩ nĩkĩo gĩtũmĩte nginyie ihinda rĩĩrĩ. <verse number="28" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:28 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 3:17">Math 3:17</ref></char></note>Baba, goocithia rĩĩtwa rĩaku!”</para>
  <para style="p">Hĩndĩ ĩyo mũgambo ũkiuma igũrũ ũkiuga atĩrĩ, “Nĩndĩrĩgoocithĩtie na no ngũrĩgoocithia o rĩngĩ.” <verse number="29" style="v"/>Nakĩo gĩkundi kĩa andũ kĩrĩa kĩarĩ ho na gĩkĩigua ũguo, gĩkiuga atĩ mũgambo ũcio nĩwarurumaga; nao arĩa angĩ makiuga atĩ nĩ mũraika wamwarĩria.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:30 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 3:17">Math 3:17</ref>; <ref loc="EXO 19:9">Thaam 19:9</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 11:42">Joh 11:42</ref></char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Mũgambo ũcio ndũnaaria nĩ ũndũ wakwa, no waria nĩ ũndũ wanyu. <verse number="31" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:31 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 16:11">Joh 16:11</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 14:30">Joh 14:30</ref>; <ref loc="EPH 2:2">Aef 2:2</ref></char></note>Hĩndĩ nĩ nginyu thĩ ĩno ĩtuĩrwo ciira; nake mũnene wa thĩ ĩno nĩekũingatwo. <verse number="32" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:32 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 3:14">Joh 3:14</ref></char></note>No niĩ ndaarĩkia kũhaicio igũrũ kuuma thĩ, nĩngaguucĩrĩria andũ othe harĩ niĩ.” <verse number="33" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:33 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 18:32">Joh 18:32</ref></char></note>Oigire ũguo nĩgeetha onanie gĩkuũ kĩrĩa agaakua.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:34 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 110:4">Thab 110:4</ref>; <ref loc="EZK 37:25">Ezek 37:25</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 8:24">Math 8:24</ref></char>
    </note>Gĩkundi kĩu gĩkiuga atĩrĩ, “Nĩtũiguĩte kuuma Watho-inĩ atĩ Kristũ egũtũũra tene na tene, nĩ ũndũ ũcio-rĩ, nĩ atĩa ũguo woiga atĩ ‘Mũrũ wa Mũndũ no nginya ahaicio igũrũ’? Ũcio ‘Mũrũ wa Mũndũ’ nũũ?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:35 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EPH 5:8">Aef 5:8</ref>; <ref loc="1JN 1:6">1Joh 1:6</ref>; <ref loc="1JN 2:11">2:11</ref></char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Nĩmũgũkorwo na ũtheri ihinda rĩngĩ inini. Thiiagai rĩrĩa mũrĩ na ũtheri, nduma ĩtanamũtumanĩra. Mũndũ ũrĩa ũthiiaga na nduma ndamenyaga kũrĩa arathiĩ. <verse number="36" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:36 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 16:8">Luk 16:8</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 8:59">Joh 8:59</ref></char></note>Mwĩhokagei ũtheri hĩndĩ ĩrĩa mũrĩ naguo, nĩgeetha mũtuĩke ciana cia ũtheri.” Nake Jesũ aarĩkia kwaria, akĩmehitha, agĩĩthiĩra.</para>
  <para style="s1">Ayahudi gũthiĩ na Mbere na kwaga Gwĩtĩkia</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="37" style="v"/>O na thuutha wa Jesũ kũringa ciama icio ciothe makĩonaga-rĩ, matiigana kũmwĩtĩkia. <verse number="38" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:38 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 53:1">Isa 53:1</ref></char></note>Ũndũ ũcio warĩ wa kũhingia kiugo kĩa Isaia ũrĩa mũnabii kĩrĩa kĩũragia atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">“Mwathani, nũũ wĩtĩkĩtie ũhoro witũ,</para>
  <para style="q2">nakuo guoko kwa Mwathani kũguũrĩirio ũ?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="39" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio matingĩetĩkirie, nĩ tondũ Isaia nĩoigĩte handũ hangĩ atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="40" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:40 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 6:10">Isa 6:10</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 13:13">Math 13:13</ref>, <ref loc="MAT 13:15">15</ref></char>
    </note>“Nĩamatuĩte atumumu,</para>
  <para style="q2">na akoomia ngoro ciao,</para>
  <para style="q1">nĩgeetha matikoone na maitho mao,</para>
  <para style="q2">kana mataũkĩrwo ngoro-inĩ ciao,</para>
  <para style="q2">o na kana magarũrũke, na niĩ ndĩmahonie.”</para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="41" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:41 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 6:1-4">Isa 6:1-4</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Isaia oigire ũguo nĩ ũndũ nĩooneete riiri wa Jesũ, na akĩaria ũhoro wake.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="42" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:42 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 7:13">Joh 7:13</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 9:22">Joh 9:22</ref></char>
    </note>No o na gũtariĩ o ũguo, aingĩ o na gatagatĩ ka atongoria a Ayahudi nĩmamwĩtĩkirie. No nĩ ũndũ wa Afarisai, matingĩoimbũrire wĩtĩkio wao nĩ gwĩtigĩra matikaingatwo thunagogi; <verse number="43" style="v"/>nĩgũkorwo nĩmendete kũgoocwo nĩ andũ gũkĩra kũgoocwo nĩ Ngai.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="44" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:44 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 10:40">Math 10:40</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Jesũ agĩcooka akĩanĩrĩra na mũgambo mũnene, akiuga atĩrĩ, “Mũndũ ũrĩa ũnjĩtĩkĩtie, to niĩ nyiki etĩkĩtie, no etĩkĩtie o na ũrĩa wandũmire. <verse number="45" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:45 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 14:9">Joh 14:9</ref></char></note>Hĩndĩ ĩrĩa mũndũ ũcio andora, onaga ũrĩa wandũmire. <verse number="46" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:46 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 1:4">Joh 1:4</ref></char></note>Niĩ njũkĩte gũkũ thĩ ndĩ ũtheri, nĩgeetha gũtikagĩe o na ũmwe ũnjĩtĩkĩtie ũngĩikara nduma-inĩ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="47" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:47 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 3:17">Joh 3:17</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Ha ũhoro wa mũndũ ũrĩa ũiguaga ũhoro wakwa no akaaga kũũhingia, ndikũmũtuĩra ciira; nĩgũkorwo ndiokire gũtuĩra andũ a thĩ ciira, no ndokire kũmahonokia. <verse number="48" style="v"/>Mũtuanĩri ciira arĩ ho, harĩ mũndũ ũrĩa ũndegaga na akaaga gwĩtĩkĩra ciugo ciakwa; kiugo kĩu ndaaririe nĩkĩo gĩkaamũtuĩra ciira mũthenya wa mũthia. <verse number="49" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:49 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 14:31">Joh 14:31</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo ndiaririe ndĩĩrĩte niĩ mwene, no Baba ũrĩa wandũmire nĩwe wanjathire ũrĩa ingiuga, na ũrĩa ingĩaria. <verse number="50" style="v"/>Nĩnjũũĩ atĩ rĩathani rĩake rĩkinyagia mũndũ muoyo-inĩ wa tene na tene. Nĩ ũndũ ũcio ũhoro ũrĩa wothe njaragia no ũrĩa Baba anjĩĩrĩte njarie.”</para>
  <chapter number="13" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Gũthambia Arutwo ake Nyarĩrĩ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 11:55">Joh 11:55</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 16:28">Joh 16:28</ref></char>
    </note>Na rĩrĩ, gwatigĩtie o hanini Gĩathĩ kĩa Bathaka gĩkinye. Jesũ nĩamenyete atĩ ihinda rĩake rĩa kuuma gũkũ thĩ athiĩ kũrĩ Ithe nĩrĩakinyĩte. Na tondũ nĩendete arĩa maarĩ ake gũkũ thĩ, akĩmoonia ũrĩa aamendete nginya kĩrĩkĩrĩro.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>Na rĩrĩa maarĩĩaga irio cia hwaĩ-inĩ, Mũcukani nĩarĩkĩtie gwĩkĩra ngoro-inĩ ya Judasi Isikariota, mũrũ wa Simoni, meciiria ma gũkunyanĩra Jesũ, <verse number="3" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">13:3 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 8:42">Joh 8:42</ref></char></note>Jesũ nĩamenyete atĩ Ithe nĩamũheete ũhoti wa maũndũ mothe, na atĩ oimĩte kũrĩ Ngai, na acookaga kũrĩ o Ngai; <verse number="4" style="v"/>nĩ ũndũ ũcio Jesũ agĩũkĩra, akiuma hau maarĩĩagĩra, akĩruta nguo yake ya igũrũ, akĩoya taurũ, akĩĩoha njohero. <verse number="5" style="v"/>Thuutha wa ũguo, agĩitĩrĩra maaĩ kĩraĩ-inĩ na akĩambĩrĩria gũthambia arutwo ake nyarĩrĩ, akĩmagiragia na taurũ ĩyo eyohete njohero.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>Na aakinya harĩ Simoni Petero, Petero akĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Hĩ, Mwathani, wee nĩwe ũgũũthambia nyarĩrĩ?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>Jesũ akĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Ndũngĩmenya ũrĩa ndĩreka rĩu, no thuutha-inĩ nĩũrĩmenya.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>Petero akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Aca, wee ndũrĩ hĩndĩ ũngĩthambia nyarĩrĩ ciakwa.”</para>
  <para style="p">Jesũ akĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Itangĩgũthambia, ndũngĩgĩa ngwatanĩro na niĩ.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>Simoni Petero akĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Mwathani, ndũgaathambie o nyarĩrĩ ciiki, no gĩĩthambie moko o na mũtwe!”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13:10 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 15:3">Joh 15:3</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Jesũ akĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Mũndũ wĩthambĩte mwĩrĩ abatairio nĩ gwĩthamba o nyarĩrĩ ciiki; mwĩrĩ wake wothe nĩ mũtheru. Na inyuĩ mũrĩ atheru, o na gũtuĩka ti inyuothe.” <verse number="11" style="v"/>Nĩgũkorwo nĩamenyete ũrĩa ũkaamũkunyanĩra, na nĩkĩo oigire atĩ ti othe maarĩ atheru.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>Aarĩkia kũmathambia nyarĩrĩ, akĩĩhumba nguo yake ya igũrũ, na agĩcooka harĩa aikarĩte. Akĩmooria atĩrĩ, “Nĩmwataũkĩrwo nĩ ũguo ndamwĩka? <verse number="13" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">13:13 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PHP 2:11">Afil 2:11</ref></char></note>Mũnjĩtaga ‘Mũrutani’ na ‘Mwathani’, na ũguo nĩguo kũrĩ, nĩgũkorwo ũguo nĩguo ndĩ. <verse number="14" style="v"/>Na rĩrĩ, kuona atĩ Niĩ, Mwathani na Mũrutani wanyu, nĩndamũthambia nyarĩrĩ-rĩ, o na inyuĩ nĩmwagĩrĩirwo mũthambanagie nyarĩrĩ mũndũ na ũrĩa ũngĩ. <verse number="15" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">13:15 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 11:29">Math 11:29</ref>; <ref loc="1TI 4:12">1Tim 4:12</ref></char></note>Nĩndamuonia kĩonereria nĩguo mwĩkage o ta ũguo ndamwĩka. <verse number="16" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">13:16 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 10:24">Math 10:24</ref></char></note>Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ na ma, gũtirĩ ndungata nene gũkĩra mwathi wayo, kana mũtũmwo agakĩra ũrĩa ũmũtũmĩte. <verse number="17" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">13:17 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JAS 1:25">Jak 1:25</ref></char></note>Kuona atĩ rĩu nĩmũmenyete maũndũ maya, nĩmũrĩrathimagwo mwameka.</para>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Kũratha Ũhoro wa Gũkunyanĩrwo Gwake</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13:18 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 13:10">Joh 13:10</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 41:9">Thab 41:9</ref></char>
    </note>“Ndiraaria ũhoro wanyu inyuothe; nĩnjũũĩ arĩa thuurĩte. No ũhoro ũyũ nĩ wa kũhingia maandĩko marĩa moigĩte atĩrĩ, ‘O ũrĩa tũrĩĩanagĩra irio nake nĩangarũrũkĩte.’</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13:19 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 14:29">Joh 14:29</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 16:4">16:4</ref></char>
    </note>“Ndĩramwĩra maũndũ maya rĩu matanekĩka, nĩgeetha hĩndĩ ĩrĩa marĩĩkĩka mũrĩnjĩtĩkia atĩ niĩ nĩ niĩ we. <verse number="20" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">13:20 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 10:40">Math 10:40</ref></char></note>Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ na ma, ũrĩa wothe wamũkagĩra mũndũ ũrĩa ndũmĩte nĩ niĩ mwene aamũkagĩra; na ũrĩa wothe ũnyamũkagĩra, aamũkagĩra ũrĩa wandũmire.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>Jesũ aarĩkia kuuga ũguo, agĩtangĩka ngoro na akiumbũra atĩrĩ, “Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ na ma, ũmwe wanyu nĩekũngunyanĩra.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>Nao arutwo ake makĩambĩrĩria kũrorana marigĩtwo nũũ gatagatĩ-inĩ kao aaragia ũhoro wake. <verse number="23" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">13:23 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 19:26">Joh 19:26</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 20:2">20:2</ref></char></note>Ũmwe wao, mũrutwo ũrĩa Jesũ endete, aikarĩte thĩ etiiranĩtie na Jesũ. <verse number="24" style="v"/>Nake Simoni Petero akĩheneria mũrutwo ũcio, akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Ta mũũrie araaria ũhoro wa ũ.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13:25 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 26:22">Math 26:22</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake mũrutwo ũcio, agĩĩtiirania na Jesũ na akĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Mwathani, ũcio nũũ ũraaria ũhoro wake?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v"/>Jesũ agĩcookia atĩrĩ, “Nĩ ũrĩa ngũhe kĩenyũ gĩkĩ kĩa mũgate ndaarĩkia gũgĩtobokia thubu-inĩ.” Na aarĩkia gũtobokia kĩenyũ kĩa mũgate thubu-inĩ, agĩkĩhe Judasi Isikariota mũrũ wa Simoni. <verse number="27" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">13:27 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 22:3">Luk 22:3</ref></char></note>Judasi aarĩkia kũrĩa mũgate ũcio, Mũcukani akĩmũingĩra.</para>
  <para style="p">Nake Jesũ akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Ũrĩa ũkiriĩ gwĩka-rĩ, ĩka narua.” <verse number="28" style="v"/>No gũtirĩ o na ũmwe warĩ metha-inĩ wataũkĩirwo nĩ gĩtũmi kĩa Jesũ kũmwĩra ũguo. <verse number="29" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">13:29 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 12:6">Joh 12:6</ref></char></note>Na tondũ Judasi nĩwe waigaga mbeeca-rĩ, amwe magĩĩciiria Jesũ aamwĩraga agũre kĩrĩa kĩabataranĩtie nĩ ũndũ wa Gĩathĩ, kana aheane kĩndũ nĩ ũndũ wa arĩa athĩĩni. <verse number="30" style="v"/>Nake Judasi aarĩkia kwamũkĩra mũgate ũcio, akiuma nja. Na kwarĩ ũtukũ.</para>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Kũratha atĩ Petero Nĩekũmũkaana</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13:31 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 14:13">Joh 14:13</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Na Judasi aarĩkia gũthiĩ, Jesũ akiuga atĩrĩ, “Rĩu Mũrũ wa Mũndũ nĩagoocithĩtio, nake Ngai nĩagoocithĩtio arĩ thĩinĩ wake. <verse number="32" style="v"/>Angĩkorwo Ngai nĩagoocithĩtio thĩinĩ wake, Ngai nĩekũgoocithia Mũriũ arĩ thĩinĩ wake mwene, na amũgoocithie o narua.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v"/>“Ciana ciakwa, ngũkorwo na inyuĩ o gwa kahinda kanini. Nĩmũkanjaria, na o ta ũrĩa ndeerire Ayahudi, no taguo ngũmwĩra: Kũrĩa ndĩrathiĩ, inyuĩ mũtingĩhota gũũka.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13:34 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1JN 2:7-11">1Joh 2:7-11</ref>; <ref loc="LEV 19:18">Alaw 19:18</ref></char>
    </note>“Ngũmũhe rĩathani rĩerũ: Endanagai mũndũ na ũrĩa ũngĩ. O ta ũrĩa ndĩmwendete, o na inyuĩ no nginya mwendanage mũndũ na ũrĩa ũngĩ. <verse number="35" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">13:35 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1JN 4:20">1Joh 4:20</ref></char></note>Ũndũ ũyũ nĩguo ũrĩmenyithagia andũ othe atĩ mũrĩ arutwo akwa, mũngĩendana mũndũ na ũrĩa ũngĩ.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="36" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13:36 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 21:18">Joh 21:18</ref>, <ref loc="JHN 21:19">19</ref>; <ref loc="2PE 1:14">2Pet 1:14</ref></char>
    </note>Simoni Petero akĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Mwathani nĩ kũ ũgũthiĩ?”</para>
  <para style="p">Nake Jesũ akĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Kũrĩa ngũthiĩ, mũtingĩhota kũnũmĩrĩra rĩu, no nĩmũrĩnũmĩrĩra thuutha-inĩ.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="37" style="v"/>Petero akĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Mwathani nĩ kĩĩ kĩngĩgiria ngũrũmĩrĩre rĩu? Niĩ nĩngũruta muoyo wakwa nĩ ũndũ waku.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="38" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13:38 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 18:27">Joh 18:27</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Atĩ no ũrute muoyo waku nĩ ũndũ wakwa? Ngũkwĩra atĩrĩ na ma, ngũkũ ĩtanakũga, nĩũrĩngaana maita matatũ!</para>
  <chapter number="14" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Kũũmĩrĩria Arutwo Ake</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">14:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 14:27">Joh 14:27</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 4:5">Thab 4:5</ref></char>
    </note>“Mũtigatangĩke ngoro, mwĩhokei Ngai; o na niĩ mũnjĩhoke. <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">14:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 13:33">Joh 13:33</ref>, <ref loc="JHN 13:36">36</ref></char></note>Thĩinĩ wa nyũmba ya Baba kũrĩ na ciikaro nyingĩ; gũtangĩrĩ ũguo ingĩrĩ kũmwĩra. Nĩngũthiĩ kuo kũmũthondekera handũ. <verse number="3" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">14:3 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 12:26">Joh 12:26</ref></char></note>Na ndathiĩ na ndamũthondekera handũ-rĩ, nĩngacooka ndĩmũgĩĩre nĩgeetha o na inyuĩ mũkoragwo harĩa ndĩ. <verse number="4" style="v"/>Njĩra ya kũrĩa ndĩrathiĩ inyuĩ nĩmũmĩũĩ.”</para>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Nĩwe Njĩra ya Gũthiĩ kũrĩ Baba</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>Nake Toma akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Mwathani, ithuĩ tũtiũĩ kũrĩa ũgũthiĩ, nĩ ũndũ ũcio-rĩ, njĩra tũngĩkĩmĩmenya atĩa?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">14:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 10:9">Joh 10:9</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 4:12">Atũm 4:12</ref></char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Niĩ nĩ niĩ njĩra, na nĩ niĩ ũhoro ũrĩa wa ma, na nĩ niĩ muoyo. Gũtirĩ mũndũ ũkinyaga kũrĩ Baba atagereire harĩ niĩ. <verse number="7" style="v"/>Korwo nĩmũũmenyete kũna, no mũmenye Baba o nake. Kuuma rĩu, nĩmũmũĩ na nĩ mũmuonete!”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>Filipu akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Mwathani, tuonie Baba na ithuĩ nĩtũkũiganĩra.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">14:9 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 9:6">Isa 9:6</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 1:14">Joh 1:14</ref></char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Filipu, ndũrĩ wamenya o na thuutha wa gũkorwo na inyuĩ ihinda iraihu ũguo? Mũndũ ũrĩa wothe ũnyonete nĩonete Baba. Ũngĩkiuga atĩa atĩ, ‘Tuonie Baba’? <verse number="10" style="v"/>Kaĩ ũtetĩkĩtie atĩ niĩ ndĩ thĩinĩ wa Baba, na atĩ Baba arĩ thĩinĩ wakwa? Ciugo iria ndĩmwĩraga ti ciakwa niĩ mwene; no Baba ũrĩa ũtũũraga thĩinĩ wakwa, nĩwe ũraruta wĩra wake. <verse number="11" style="v"/>Njĩtĩkiai rĩrĩa nguuga atĩ ndĩ thĩinĩ wa Baba, nake Baba arĩ thĩinĩ wakwa; kana mũgĩĩtĩkie nĩ ũndũ wa ũira wa ciama iria ningaga. <verse number="12" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">14:12 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 10:17">Luk 10:17</ref></char></note>Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ na ma, mũndũ ũrĩa wothe ũnjĩtĩkĩtie, nĩarĩĩkaga maũndũ marĩa njĩkaga. Na nĩageeka o na maũndũ manene kũrĩ macio, tondũ ndĩrathiĩ kũrĩ Baba. <verse number="13" style="v"/>Na ũrĩa wothe mũkahooya, nĩngawĩka thĩinĩ wa rĩĩtwa rĩakwa, nĩgeetha Mũriũ arehere Baba riiri. <verse number="14" style="v"/>Mwahooya ũndũ o wothe thĩinĩ wa rĩĩtwa rĩakwa, nĩndĩrĩwĩkaga.</para>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Kwĩranĩra Roho Mũtheru</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">14:15 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 15:10">Joh 15:10</ref>; <ref loc="1JN 5:3">1Joh 5:3</ref></char>
    </note>“Angĩkorwo nĩmũnyendete, nĩmũrĩathĩkagĩra ũrĩa ndĩmwathĩte. <verse number="16" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">14:16 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 15:26">Joh 15:26</ref></char></note>Na niĩ nĩngahooya Baba, nake nĩakamũhe Mũteithia ũngĩ aikarage na inyuĩ nginya tene, <verse number="17" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">14:17 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 16:13">Joh 16:13</ref>; <ref loc="1CO 2:14">1Akor 2:14</ref></char></note>nake nĩwe Roho ũrĩa wa ma. Nao andũ a gũkũ thĩ matingĩmwĩtĩkĩra tondũ matimuonaga na matimũũĩ. No inyuĩ nĩmũmũĩ nĩgũkorwo atũũranagia na inyuĩ, na aikaraga thĩinĩ wanyu. <verse number="18" style="v"/>Ndikũmũtiga ta ciana cia ngoriai, nĩngũũka kũrĩ inyuĩ. <verse number="19" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">14:19 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 7:33">Joh 7:33</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 6:57">Joh 6:57</ref></char></note>Thuutha wa ihinda inyinyi, thĩ ndĩgũcooka kũnyona, no inyuĩ nĩmũrĩnyonaga. Tondũ nĩndũũraga muoyo, o na inyuĩ nĩmũgũtũũra muoyo. <verse number="20" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">14:20 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 16:23">Joh 16:23</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 8:10">Arom 8:10</ref></char></note>Mũthenya ũcio nĩmũkamenya atĩ niĩ ndĩ thĩinĩ wa Baba, na inyuĩ mũrĩ thĩinĩ wakwa, na niĩ ndĩ thĩinĩ wanyu. <verse number="21" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">14:21 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="DEU 7:13">Gũcook 7:13</ref></char></note>Ũrĩa wothe ũiguaga maathani makwa na akamaathĩkĩra, ũcio nĩwe ũnyendete. Nake ũcio ũnyendete nĩarĩendagwo nĩ Baba, o na niĩ nĩndĩmwendaga na ndĩĩonithanagie kũrĩ we.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">14:22 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LUK 6:16">Luk 6:16</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 10:41">Atũm 10:41</ref></char>
    </note>Nake Judasi (no ti Isikariota) akiuga atĩrĩ, “No rĩrĩ Mwathani, nĩ kĩĩ gĩgũtũma wĩonithanie kũrĩ ithuĩ na ti kũrĩ andũ a gũkũ thĩ?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>Nake Jesũ agĩcookia atĩrĩ, “Mũndũ o wothe ũnyendete nĩarĩathĩkagĩra ũrutani wakwa. Baba nake nĩarĩmwendaga, na nĩtũrĩũkaga kũrĩ we tũtũũranagie nake. <verse number="24" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">14:24 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="DEU 18:18">Gũcook 18:18</ref></char></note>Ũrĩa ũtanyendete ndathĩkagĩra ũrutani wakwa. Ciugo icio mũiguaga ti ciakwa niĩ mwene; nĩ cia Baba ũrĩa wandũmire.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v"/>“Maũndũ maya mothe ndamwarĩria tũrĩ o na inyuĩ. <verse number="26" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">14:26 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 15:26">Joh 15:26</ref>; <ref loc="1JN 2:20">1Joh 2:20</ref>, <ref loc="1JN 2:27">27</ref></char></note>No rĩrĩ, we Mũteithia, na nĩwe Roho Mũtheru, ũrĩa Baba agaatũma thĩinĩ wa rĩĩtwa rĩakwa, nĩakamũruta maũndũ mothe na amũririkanie ũrĩa wothe ndĩmwĩrĩte. <verse number="27" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">14:27 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PHP 4:7">Afil 4:7</ref></char></note>Thayũ nĩguo ngũmũtigĩra; thayũ wakwa nĩguo ndaamũhe. Ndikũmũhe thayũ ta ũrĩa ũheanagwo nĩ andũ a gũkũ thĩ. Mũtigatangĩke ngoro kana mwĩtigĩre.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v"/>“Inyuĩ nĩmwaiguire ngiuga atĩrĩ, ‘Nĩngũthiĩ na nĩngacooka njũke kũrĩ inyuĩ rĩngĩ.’ Angĩkorwo nĩmũnyendete-rĩ, no mũkene tondũ ndĩrathiĩ kũrĩ Baba, nĩgũkorwo Baba nĩ mũnene kũrĩ niĩ. <verse number="29" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">14:29 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 13:19">Joh 13:19</ref></char></note>Ndamwĩra maũndũ macio o rĩu matanekĩka nĩgeetha rĩrĩa magekĩka mũgeetĩkia. <verse number="30" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">14:30 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 12:31">Joh 12:31</ref></char></note>Ndikũmwarĩria ũhoro ũyũ ihinda iraaya, nĩgũkorwo mũnene wa gũkũ thĩ nĩarooka. We ndarĩ na hinya wa kũnjatha, <verse number="31" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">14:31 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 10:18">Joh 10:18</ref></char></note>no andũ a gũkũ thĩ no nginya mamenye atĩ nĩnyendete Baba, na atĩ njĩkaga o ũrĩa Baba anjathĩte.</para>
  <para style="p">“Ũkai rĩu; nĩtũthiĩi.</para>
  <chapter number="15" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Mũthabibũ na Honge</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">15:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 6:35">Joh 6:35</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 80:8-11">Thab 80:8-11</ref></char>
    </note>“Niĩ nĩ niĩ mũthabibũ ũrĩa wa ma nake Baba nĩwe mũrĩmĩri. <verse number="2" style="v"/>Rũhonge o ruothe rũrĩ thĩinĩ wakwa rũtaciaraga nĩarũtemaga akarweheria. Naruo rũhonge o ruothe rũrĩa rũciaraga nĩarũceehaga nĩguo rũciare maciaro maingĩ makĩria. <verse number="3" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15:3 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 13:10">Joh 13:10</ref>; <ref loc="EPH 5:26">Aef 5:26</ref></char></note>Inyuĩ o na rĩu mũrĩ atheru nĩ ũndũ wa ũhoro ũrĩa ndĩmũheete. <verse number="4" style="v"/>Ikaragai thĩinĩ wakwa na niĩ nĩndĩrĩikaraga thĩinĩ wanyu. Gũtirĩ rũhonge rũngĩciara maciaro rũrĩ rwiki; no nginya rũikare thĩinĩ wa mũthabibũ. O na inyuĩ mũtingĩciara maciaro mũtangĩikara thĩinĩ wakwa.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>“Nĩ niĩ mũthabibũ, na inyuĩ mũrĩ honge. Mũndũ angĩikara thĩinĩ wakwa na niĩ njikare thĩinĩ wake, nĩarĩciaraga maciaro maingĩ; tondũ mũtarĩ hamwe na niĩ mũtirĩ ũndũ mũngĩhota gwĩka. <verse number="6" style="v"/>Mũndũ o wothe angĩaga gũikara thĩinĩ wakwa-rĩ, atariĩ o ta rũhonge rũrĩa rũteagwo rũkooma; honge icio nĩkũnganio ciũnganagio, igaikio mwaki-inĩ ikahĩa. <verse number="7" style="v"/>Mũngĩikara thĩinĩ wakwa, nacio ciugo ciakwa ciikare thĩinĩ wanyu, hooyai o kĩrĩa gĩothe mũngĩenda, na nĩmũkũheo kĩo. <verse number="8" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15:8 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 8:31">Joh 8:31</ref></char></note>Ũndũ ũrĩa ũngĩgoocithia Baba nĩ atĩ, mũciarage maciaro maingĩ nĩguo mwĩonanie mũrĩ arutwo akwa.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>“O ta ũrĩa Baba anyendete, ũguo noguo na niĩ ndĩmwendete. Rĩu-rĩ, ikaragai o wendo-inĩ wakwa. <verse number="10" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15:10 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 14:15">Joh 14:15</ref></char></note>Mũngĩathĩkĩra maathani makwa-rĩ, nĩmũrĩikaraga wendo-inĩ wakwa o ta ũrĩa niĩ njathĩkĩire maathani ma Baba na ngaikara wendo-inĩ wake. <verse number="11" style="v"/>Ndamwĩra maũndũ macio nĩguo gĩkeno gĩakwa kĩgĩe thĩinĩ wanyu, nakĩo gĩkeno kĩanyu gĩkinyanĩre. <verse number="12" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15:12 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 13:34">Joh 13:34</ref></char></note>Rĩathani rĩakwa nĩ rĩĩrĩ: Endanagai inyuĩ ene, o ta ũrĩa niĩ ndĩmwendete. <verse number="13" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15:13 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 10:11">Joh 10:11</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 5:7">Arom 5:7</ref>, <ref loc="ROM 5:8">8</ref></char></note>Gũtirĩ mũndũ ũrĩ wendo mũnene kũrĩ ũyũ, atĩ mũndũ no arute muoyo wake nĩ ũndũ wa arata ake. <verse number="14" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15:14 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JOB 16:20">Ayub 16:20</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 12:50">Math 12:50</ref></char></note>Inyuĩ mũrĩ arata akwa, mũngĩĩka ũrĩa ndĩmwathĩte. <verse number="15" style="v"/>Ndigũcooka kũmwĩta ndungata, tondũ ndungata ndĩmenyaga ũrĩa mũmĩathi areeka; no inyuĩ ndĩmwĩtĩte arata nĩgũkorwo maũndũ marĩa mothe ndĩĩrutĩte kuuma kũrĩ Baba nĩndĩmũmenyithĩtie. <verse number="16" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15:16 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 15:19">Joh 15:19</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 7:7">Math 7:7</ref></char></note>Ti inyuĩ mwathuurire, no nĩ niĩ ndamũthuurire, na ngĩmwamũra mũthiĩ mũgaciare maciaro, namo maciaro macio matũũre. Nake Baba nĩakamũhe kĩrĩa gĩothe mũkahooya thĩinĩ wa rĩĩtwa rĩakwa. <verse number="17" style="v"/>Rĩĩrĩ nĩrĩo rĩathani rĩakwa: Endanagai.</para>
  <para style="s1">Andũ a Thĩ Gũthũũra Arutwo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">15:18 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 66:5">Isa 66:5</ref>; <ref loc="1JN 3:13">1Joh 3:13</ref></char>
    </note>“Andũ a thĩ mangĩmũthũũra, menyai atĩ nĩ niĩ maambire gũthũũra. <verse number="19" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15:19 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 17:14">Joh 17:14</ref></char></note>Korwo mũrĩ a gũkũ thĩ, andũ a thĩ no mamwende ta mũrĩ ao. No rĩrĩ, inyuĩ mũtirĩ a gũkũ thĩ, no nĩndĩmũthuurĩte kuuma kũrĩ andũ a thĩ. Nĩkĩo andũ a thĩ mamũthũire. <verse number="20" style="v"/>Ririkanai ũhoro ũrĩa ndamwĩrire atĩrĩ, ‘Gũtirĩ ndungata nene gũkĩra mũmĩathi.’ Angĩkorwo niĩ nĩmanyariirire, o na inyuĩ nĩmakamũnyarira. Angĩkorwo nĩmathĩkĩire ũrutani wakwa o na wanyu nĩmakawathĩkĩra. <verse number="21" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15:21 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 66:5">Isa 66:5</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 16:3">Joh 16:3</ref></char></note>Nao makaamwĩka ũguo nĩ ũndũ wa rĩĩtwa rĩakwa, nĩgũkorwo matiũĩ ũrĩa wandũmire.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">15:22 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 9:41">Joh 9:41</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Korwo ndiokire ngĩmahe ũhoro, matingĩamenyire nĩ ehia. No rĩu matirĩ na kĩĩgwatio nĩ ũndũ wa mehia mao. <verse number="23" style="v"/>Mũndũ ũrĩa ũũthũũrĩte, nĩathũũire Baba o nake. <verse number="24" style="v"/>Korwo ndiĩkĩte gatagatĩ-inĩ kao maũndũ marĩa matarĩ mekwo nĩ mũndũ ũngĩ matingĩamenyire nĩ ehia. No rĩu nĩmonete ciama ici, no no maathũire na magathũũra Baba. <verse number="25" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15:25 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 35:19">Thab 35:19</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 69:4">69:4</ref></char></note>No nĩgeetha kũhingio ũrĩa kwandĩkĩtwo Watho-inĩ wao atĩrĩ, ‘Nĩmathũũrire hatarĩ gĩtũmi.’</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">15:26 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 14:17">Joh 14:17</ref>; <ref loc="1JN 5:7">1Joh 5:7</ref></char>
    </note>“Hĩndĩ ĩrĩa Mũteithia agooka, ũrĩa ngaamũtũmĩra kuuma kũrĩ Baba, na nĩwe Roho wa ma ũrĩa uumaga kũrĩ Baba, we nĩakaheana ũira wakwa. <verse number="27" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15:27 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 24:48">Luk 24:48</ref></char></note>Na o na inyuĩ no nginya mũkaaruta ũira, tondũ mũtũũrĩte na niĩ kuuma o kĩambĩrĩria.</para>
  <chapter number="16" style="c"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">16:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 15:18-27">Joh 15:18-27</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 11:6">Math 11:6</ref></char>
    </note>“Ndamwĩra maũndũ macio mothe nĩgeetha mũtikanae gũtiganĩria wĩtĩkio. <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">16:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 9:22">Joh 9:22</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 26:9">Atũm 26:9</ref>, <ref loc="ACT 26:10">10</ref></char></note>Nĩmakamũingata thunagogi-inĩ; na ũhoro wa ma nĩ atĩ, kũrĩ hĩndĩ ĩgũũka rĩrĩa mũndũ o wothe ũkaamũũraga ageciiragia atĩ nĩ Ngai aratungatĩra. <verse number="3" style="v"/>Mageekaga maũndũ macio nĩ ũndũ matimenyete Baba o na kana makaamenya. <verse number="4" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">16:4 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 13:19">Joh 13:19</ref></char></note>Ndamwĩra maũndũ macio nĩgeetha hĩndĩ ĩyo yakinya mũkaaririkana atĩ nĩndamwĩrĩte. Ndiamwĩrire maũndũ macio kĩambĩrĩria-inĩ tondũ ndaarĩ hamwe na inyuĩ.</para>
  <para style="s1">Wĩra wa Roho Mũtheru</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">16:5 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 7:33">Joh 7:33</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 13:36">Joh 13:36</ref></char>
    </note>“Rĩu nĩngũthiĩ kũrĩ ũrĩa wandũmire. No gũtirĩ o na ũmwe wanyu ũranjũũria atĩrĩ, ‘Ũrathiĩ kũ?’ <verse number="6" style="v"/>Mwaiyũrwo nĩ kĩeha nĩ tondũ nĩndamwĩra maũndũ macio. <verse number="7" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">16:7 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 14:16">Joh 14:16</ref>, <ref loc="JHN 14:26">26</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 7:39">7:39</ref></char></note>No ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ na ma, nĩ kwagĩrĩire niĩ thiĩ nĩ ũndũ wanyu. Tondũ ndaaga gũthiĩ, Mũteithia ndagooka kũrĩ inyuĩ. No ndaathiĩ, nĩngamũtũma oke kũrĩ inyuĩ. <verse number="8" style="v"/>Nake oka, nĩakaiguithia andũ a gũkũ thĩ ũrĩa mahĩtĩtie ũhoro-inĩ wa mehia, na ũhoro-inĩ wa ũthingu, o na ũhoro-inĩ wa ciira: <verse number="9" style="v"/>Nĩmahĩtĩtie ũhoro-inĩ wa mehia, nĩgũkorwo andũ matinjĩtĩkĩtie; <verse number="10" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">16:10 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 3:14">Atũm 3:14</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 16:5">Joh 16:5</ref></char></note>nĩmahĩtĩtie ũhoro-inĩ wa ũthingu, nĩgũkorwo ndĩrathiĩ kũrĩ Baba kũrĩa mũtangĩcooka kũnyona; <verse number="11" style="v"/>na nĩmahĩtĩtie ũhoro-inĩ wa ciira tondũ mũnene wa gũkũ thĩ nĩarĩkĩtie gũtuĩrwo ciira.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>“Ndĩ na maũndũ mangĩ maingĩ ma kũmwĩra, makĩria ya marĩa mũngĩhota kũũmĩrĩria rĩu. <verse number="13" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">16:13 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 14:17">Joh 14:17</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 14:26">Joh 14:26</ref></char></note>No rĩrĩ, Roho Mũtheru ũcio wa ma oka, nĩakamũtongoria ũhoro-inĩ ũrĩa wa ma wothe. Ndakaaragia ũhoro wake mwene; akaaragia ũhoro wa maũndũ marĩa aiguĩte, ningĩ nĩakamwĩra ũhoro wa maũndũ marĩa magooka thuutha. <verse number="14" style="v"/>Nĩakangoocithia nĩgũkorwo nĩakamũmenyithia ũhoro wakwa ũrĩa arutĩte kuuma kũrĩ niĩ. <verse number="15" style="v"/>Maũndũ mothe ma Baba nĩ makwa. Nĩkĩo ndamwĩra atĩ Roho nĩakamũmenyithia ũhoro wakwa ũrĩa arutĩte kuuma kũrĩ niĩ, mũũmenye.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">16:16 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 14:18-24">Joh 14:18-24</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Thuutha wa kahinda kanini mũtikũnyona rĩngĩ na ningĩ thuutha wa kahinda kanini nĩmũkũnyona.”</para>
  <para style="s1">Kĩeha kĩa Arutwo nĩ Gĩgũtuĩka Gĩkeno</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>Amwe a arutwo ake makĩũrania atĩrĩ, “Arenda kuuga atĩa rĩrĩa aroiga atĩ, ‘Thuutha wa kahinda kanini mũtikũnyona rĩngĩ na ningĩ atĩ thuutha wa kahinda kanini nĩmũkũnyona’, ningĩ atĩ ‘Tondũ ndĩrathiĩ kũrĩ Baba?’ ” <verse number="18" style="v"/>Magĩthiĩ na mbere kũũrania atĩrĩ, “Arenda kuuga atĩa rĩrĩa aroiga atĩ, ‘Kahinda kanini’? Ithuĩ tũtiramenya ũrĩa aroiga.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>Nake Jesũ akĩona atĩ nĩmendaga kũmũũria ũhoro ũcio, nĩ ũndũ ũcio akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Nĩ kũũrania mũrorania ũrĩa ngwendaga kuuga rĩrĩa njugire atĩ ‘Thuutha wa kahinda kanini mũtikũnyona rĩngĩ, na ningĩ thuutha wa kahinda kanini nĩmũkũnyona’? <verse number="20" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">16:20 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 20:20">Joh 20:20</ref></char></note>Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ na ma, mũkaarĩra na mũcakae rĩrĩa andũ a thĩ marakena. Inyuĩ mũkanyiitwo nĩ kĩeha, no kĩeha, kĩanyu nĩgĩkagarũrũka gĩtuĩke gĩkeno. <verse number="21" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">16:21 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 13:8">Isa 13:8</ref></char></note>Mũndũ-wa-nja agĩciara nĩakoragwo na ruo tondũ hĩndĩ yake nĩ nginyu; no aarĩkia gũciara kaana, akariganĩrwo nĩ ruo nĩ ũndũ wa gũkena nĩgũkorwo kaana nĩ gaaciarwo gũkũ thĩ. <verse number="22" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">16:22 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PRO 20">Thim 20</ref></char></note>O na inyuĩ noguo: Rĩu nĩ ihinda rĩanyu rĩa kĩeha, no nĩngamuona rĩngĩ na nĩmũgakena, na gũtirĩ mũndũ o na ũmwe ũkaamũtunya gĩkeno kĩu. <verse number="23" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">16:23 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 7:7">Math 7:7</ref></char></note>Mũthenya ũcio wakinya mũtigacooka kũnjũũria ũndũ o na ũrĩkũ. Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ na ma, Baba nĩakamũhe kĩrĩa gĩothe mũkaahooya thĩinĩ wa rĩĩtwa rĩakwa. <verse number="24" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">16:24 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 3:29">Joh 3:29</ref></char></note>Nginyagia rĩu mũtirĩ mwahooya ũndũ thĩinĩ wa rĩĩtwa rĩakwa. Hooyai na nĩmũkũheo, nĩguo gĩkeno kĩanyu gĩkinyanĩre.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">16:25 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 13:34">Math 13:34</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“O na gũtuĩka ngoretwo ngĩaria na ngerekano-rĩ, hĩndĩ nĩĩroka rĩrĩa itagacooka kũmwarĩria na njĩra ĩyo, no ngaamwĩraga ũhoro wa Baba itekũhithĩrĩra. <verse number="26" style="v"/>Mũthenya ũcio nĩmũkahooyaga thĩinĩ wa rĩĩtwa rĩakwa. Ndiroiga atĩ nĩngahooyaga Baba ithenya rĩanyu. <verse number="27" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">16:27 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 14:21">Joh 14:21</ref>, <ref loc="JHN 14:23">23</ref></char></note>No rĩrĩ, Baba we mwene nĩamwendete, nĩgũkorwo inyuĩ nĩmũnyendete, na nĩmwĩtĩkĩtie atĩ ndoimire kũrĩ Ngai. <verse number="28" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">16:28 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 13:3">Joh 13:3</ref></char></note>Niĩ ndoimire kũrĩ Baba, ngĩũka gũkũ thĩ; na rĩu nĩnguuma gũkũ thĩ, njooke kũrĩ Baba.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v"/>Hĩndĩ ĩyo arutwo a Jesũ makiuga atĩrĩ, “Rĩu nĩũratũhe ũhoro wega, ũtekwaria na ngerekano. <verse number="30" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">16:30 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1KI 17:24">1Ath 17:24</ref></char></note>Rĩu nĩtwamenya atĩ wee nĩũũĩ maũndũ mothe, na atĩ o na ndũbataire mũndũ o na ũrĩkũ akũũrie ciũria. Ũhoro ũcio nĩwatũma twĩtĩkie atĩ woimĩte kũrĩ Ngai.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v"/>Nake Jesũ akĩmacookeria atĩrĩ, “Rĩu nĩmwetĩkia! <verse number="32" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">16:32 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 26:31">Math 26:31</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 8:16">Joh 8:16</ref>, <ref loc="JHN 8:29">29</ref></char></note>No hĩndĩ nĩĩroka, na nĩnginyu, rĩrĩa mũkahurunjũka, o mũndũ athiĩ gwake mũciĩ. Mũkaandiga ndĩ nyiki, no ndirĩ nyiki, nĩgũkorwo Baba arĩ hamwe na niĩ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">16:33 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 14:27">Joh 14:27</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 8:37">Arom 8:37</ref></char>
    </note>“Ndamwĩra maũndũ macio nĩgeetha mũgĩe na thayũ thĩinĩ wakwa. Gũkũ thĩ nĩmũrĩonaga thĩĩna. No ũmĩrĩriai! Niĩ nĩndooretie thĩ.”</para>
  <chapter number="17" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Kwĩhoera</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">17:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 11:41">Joh 11:41</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 12:23">Joh 12:23</ref></char>
    </note>Jesũ aarĩkia kuuga maũndũ macio, agĩtiira maitho akĩrora na igũrũ, akĩhooya, akiuga atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="pm">“Baba hĩndĩ nĩ nginyu. Goocithia Mũrũguo, nĩguo nake Mũrũguo akũgoocithie. <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">17:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 28:18">Math 28:18</ref>; <ref loc="DAN 7:14">Dan 7:14</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo nĩũmũheete ũhoti wa gwatha andũ othe, nĩguo arĩa othe ũmũheete amahe muoyo wa tene na tene. <verse number="3" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">17:3 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PHP 3:8">Afil 3:8</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 3:17">Joh 3:17</ref></char></note>Na rĩu ũyũ nĩguo muoyo wa tene na tene: Atĩ makũmenye, o Wee Ngai ũrĩa wa ma, na mamenye Jesũ Kristũ, ũrĩa ũtũmĩte. <verse number="4" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">17:4 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 13:31">Joh 13:31</ref></char></note>Nĩngũgoocithĩtie gũkũ thĩ na ũndũ wa kũrĩĩkia wĩra ũrĩa waheire ndute. <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">17:5 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PHP 2:6">Afil 2:6</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 1:2">Joh 1:2</ref></char></note>Na rĩu Baba, ngoocithia ndĩ mbere yaku na riiri ũrĩa ndaarĩ naguo hamwe nawe o mbere thĩ ĩtaanagĩa.</para>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Kũhoera Arutwo ake</para>
  <para style="pm">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>“Nĩnguũrĩirie andũ arĩa waheire gũkũ thĩ rĩĩtwa rĩaku. Acio maarĩ aku; nawe ũkĩĩhe o, nao nĩmathĩkĩire kiugo gĩaku. <verse number="7" style="v"/>Na rĩu nĩmamenyete atĩ indo iria ciothe ũheete ciumĩte kũrĩ wee. <verse number="8" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">17:8 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 17:14">Joh 17:14</ref>, <ref loc="JHN 17:26">26</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo nĩndamaheire ciugo iria waheire, nao magĩciĩtĩkĩra. Nĩmamenyire hatarĩ nganja atĩ ndoimire kũrĩ wee, na magĩĩtĩkia atĩ wee nĩwe wandũmire. <verse number="9" style="v"/>Acio nĩo ndĩrahoera. Ndirahoera andũ a gũkũ thĩ, no ndĩrahoera arĩa ũũheete, nĩgũkorwo nĩ aku. <verse number="10" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">17:10 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 16:15">Joh 16:15</ref></char></note>Kĩrĩa gĩothe ndĩ nakĩo nĩ gĩaku, na kĩrĩa gĩothe ũrĩ nakĩo nĩ gĩakwa. Naguo ũgooci nĩũũkĩte kũrĩ niĩ nĩ ũndũ wao. <verse number="11" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">17:11 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 13:1">Joh 13:1</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 7:33">Joh 7:33</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 133:1">Thab 133:1</ref></char></note>Ndigũikara gũkũ thĩ rĩngĩ, no-o marĩ o gũkũ thĩ, na niĩ ndĩroka kũrĩ wee. Baba Mũtheru, magitĩre na ũhoti wa rĩĩtwa rĩaku, rĩĩtwa rĩrĩa waheire, nĩgeetha matuĩke ũmwe o ta ũrĩa ithuĩ tũrĩ ũmwe. <verse number="12" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">17:12 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 6:70">Joh 6:70</ref></char></note>Rĩrĩa ndĩraarĩ nao, nĩndĩramagitagĩra na ngamamenyerera na rĩĩtwa rĩu waheire. Gũtirĩ o na ũmwe ũũrĩte o tiga ũrĩa wathĩrĩirwo kwanangwo nĩguo Maandĩko mahingio.</para>
  <para style="pm">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>“Rĩu ndĩroka kũrĩ wee, no maũndũ maya ndĩroiga ndĩ o gũkũ thĩ, nĩguo maiyũrwo nĩ gĩkeno gĩakwa kĩrĩ gĩkinyanĩru kũna thĩinĩ wao. <verse number="14" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">17:14 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 8:23">Joh 8:23</ref></char></note>Nĩndĩmaheete kiugo gĩaku, nao andũ a gũkũ thĩ makamathũũra, nĩgũkorwo o ti a gũkũ thĩ rĩngĩ, o ta ũrĩa niĩ itarĩ wa gũkũ thĩ. <verse number="15" style="v"/>Ihooya rĩakwa ti ũmarute gũkũ thĩ, no nĩ atĩ ũmagitagĩre kuuma kũrĩ ũrĩa mũũru. <verse number="16" style="v"/>O ti a gũkũ thĩ, o ta ũrĩa o na niĩ itarĩ wakuo. <verse number="17" style="v"/>Maamũre, ũmatherie na ũhoro ũrĩa wa ma; ũhoro waku nĩguo ũhoro wa ma. <verse number="18" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">17:18 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 20:21">Joh 20:21</ref></char></note>O ta ũrĩa wandũmire gũkũ thĩ, na niĩ noguo ndamatũma kũrĩ andũ a gũkũ thĩ. <verse number="19" style="v"/>Ndĩĩtheretie nĩ ũndũ wao, nĩguo o nao matherio kũna nĩ ũhoro ũrĩa wa ma.</para>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Kũhoera Etĩkia othe</para>
  <para style="pm">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>“Ningĩ to aya oiki ndĩrahoera. Ndĩrahoera o na arĩa angĩ makaanjĩtĩkia nĩ ũndũ wa ndũmĩrĩri ya aya, <verse number="21" style="v"/>nĩguo othe matuĩke ũmwe Baba, o ta ũrĩa we ũrĩ thĩinĩ wakwa na niĩ ndĩ thĩinĩ waku. O nao marogĩa thĩinĩ witũ nĩgeetha andũ a gũkũ thĩ metĩkie atĩ nĩwe ũndũmĩte. <verse number="22" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">17:22 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 14:20">Joh 14:20</ref></char></note>Nĩndĩmaheete riiri ũrĩa waheire, nĩguo matuĩke ũmwe o ta ũrĩa ithuĩ tũrĩ ũmwe, <verse number="23" style="v"/>niĩ ndĩ thĩinĩ wao, nawe ũrĩ thĩinĩ wakwa. Marotuĩka ũmwe kũna, nĩgeetha andũ a gũkũ thĩ mamenye atĩ nĩwe wandũmire, na atĩ nĩũmendete o ta ũrĩa ũnyendete.</para>
  <para style="pm">
    <verse number="24" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">17:24 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 12:26">Joh 12:26</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 17:5">Joh 17:5</ref></char>
    </note>“Baba, ngwenda arĩa ũũheete makorwo na niĩ harĩa ndĩ na mone riiri wakwa, riiri ũrĩa ũũheete nĩ ũndũ nĩwanyendete thĩ ĩtanombwo.</para>
  <para style="pm">
    <verse number="25" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">17:25 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 15:21">Joh 15:21</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 16:27">Joh 16:27</ref></char>
    </note>“Baba Mũthingu, o na gũtuĩka andũ a gũkũ thĩ matikũũĩ-rĩ, niĩ nĩngũũĩ, nao nĩ moĩ atĩ nĩwe ũndũmĩte. <verse number="26" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">17:26 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 17:6">Joh 17:6</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 15:9">Joh 15:9</ref></char></note>Nĩngũmenyithanĩtie kũrĩ o, na nĩngũkĩrĩrĩria gũkũmenyithania, nĩgeetha wendani ũrĩa ũnyendete naguo ũikarage thĩinĩ wao na nĩguo o na niĩ mwene ngoragwo thĩinĩ wao.”</para>
  <chapter number="18" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Kũnyiitwo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">18:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2SA 15:23">2Sam 15:23</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Jesũ aarĩkia kũhooya, agĩthiĩ arĩ na arutwo ake, makĩringa mũkuru wa Karũũĩ ga Kidironi. Mũrĩmo ũcio ũngĩ nĩ haarĩ na mũgũnda wa mĩtamaiyũ, agĩtoonya ho na arutwo ake.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">18:2 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LUK 21:37">Luk 21:37</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 22:39">22:39</ref></char>
    </note>Na rĩrĩ, Judasi, ũrĩa wamũkunyanĩire, nĩooĩ handũ hau, nĩ ũndũ Jesũ nĩacemanagĩria ho kaingĩ na arutwo ake. <verse number="3" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">18:3 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 1:16">Atũm 1:16</ref></char></note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio Judasi agĩthiĩ hau mũgũnda-inĩ ũcio, atongoretie mbũtũ ya thigari na anene amwe kuuma kũrĩ athĩnjĩri-Ngai arĩa anene na Afarisai. Nao nĩmakuuĩte icinga, na matawa, na indo cia mbaara.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">18:4 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 6:64">Joh 6:64</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ nĩ ũndũ nĩamenyaga maũndũ marĩa mothe maakirie kũmũkora-rĩ, akiumĩra akĩmooria atĩrĩ, “Nũũ mũracaria?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>Nao makĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Nĩ Jesũ wa Nazarethi.”</para>
  <para style="p">Nake Jesũ akĩmacookeria atĩrĩ, “Niĩ nĩ niĩ we.” (Nake Judasi ũcio wamũkunyanĩire aarũngiĩ hau hamwe nao.) <verse number="6" style="v"/>Rĩrĩa Jesũ aameerire atĩrĩ, “Niĩ nĩ niĩ we,” magĩcooka na thuutha makĩgũa thĩ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>O rĩngĩ Jesũ akĩmooria atĩrĩ, “Nũũ mũracaria?”</para>
  <para style="p">Nao makĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Nĩ Jesũ wa Nazarethi.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>Jesũ akĩmacookeria atĩrĩ, “Ndamwĩra atĩ nĩ niĩ we. Akorwo nĩ niĩ mũracaria-rĩ, rekei andũ aya mathiĩ.” <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">18:9 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 6:39">Joh 6:39</ref></char></note>Gwekĩkire ũguo nĩgeetha ũhoro ũrĩa aarĩtie ũhinge, rĩrĩa oigire atĩrĩ, “Andũ arĩa waheire gũtirĩ o na ũmwe wao ndeete.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>Hĩndĩ ĩyo Simoni Petero, tondũ aarĩ na rũhiũ rwa njora, akĩrũcomora na agĩtinia gũtũ kwa ũrĩo kwa ndungata ya mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai ũrĩa mũnene. (Ndungata ĩyo yetagwo Maliku.)</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">18:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 20:22">Math 20:22</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ agĩatha Petero atĩrĩ, “Cookia rũhiũ rwaku rwa njora! Gĩkombe kĩrĩa Baba aaheete-rĩ, nĩngwaga gũkĩnyuĩra?”</para>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Gũtwarwo kwa Anasi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>Nayo mbũtũ ĩyo ya thigari na mũnene wayo, hamwe na anene acio a Ayahudi makĩnyiita Jesũ. Makĩmuoha na <verse number="13" style="v"/>makĩamba kũmũtwara kwa Anasi, ũrĩa warĩ mũthoniwe wa Kaiafa, ũrĩa warĩ mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai ũrĩa mũnene mwaka ũcio. <verse number="14" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">18:14 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 11:49-51">Joh 11:49-51</ref></char></note>Kaiafa nĩwe wataarĩte Ayahudi atĩ no gũkorwo arĩ wega mũndũ ũmwe akuĩre andũ othe.</para>
  <para style="s1">Petero Gũkaana Jesũ Ihinda rĩa Mbere</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">18:15 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 26:58">Math 26:58</ref>; <ref loc="MRK 14:54">Mar 14:54</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 22:54">Luk 22:54</ref></char>
    </note>Simoni Petero marĩ na mũrutwo ũngĩ makĩrũmĩrĩra Jesũ. Na tondũ mũrutwo ũcio nĩoĩo nĩ mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai ũrĩa mũnene, agĩtwarana na Jesũ kũu nja ya mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai ũcio mũnene. <verse number="16" style="v"/>No Petero agĩtigwo etereire hau nja ya kĩhingo. Nake mũrutwo ũcio ũngĩ, woĩo nĩ mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai ũrĩa mũnene, agĩcooka, akĩaria na mũirĩtu ũrĩa warĩ kĩhingo-inĩ agĩtoonyia Petero.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>Nake mũirĩtu ũcio warĩ kĩhingo-inĩ akĩũria Petero atĩrĩ, “Kaĩ wee ũrĩ ũmwe wa arutwo a mũndũ ũyũ?”</para>
  <para style="p">Nake agĩcookia agĩkiuga atĩrĩ, “Aca, ndirĩ ũmwe wao.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">18:18 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 21:9">Joh 21:9</ref>; <ref loc="MRK 14:54">Mar 14:54</ref>, <ref loc="MRK 14:67">67</ref></char>
    </note>Na rĩrĩ, ndungata na thigari ciarũgamĩte irigiicĩirie mwaki ũrĩa ciakĩtie ikĩwota, tondũ kwarĩ na heho. Petero o nake aarũgamĩte hamwe nao agĩota mwaki.</para>
  <para style="s1">Mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai ũrĩa Mũnene kũũria Jesũ Ciũria</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>Ihinda-inĩ o rĩu, mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai ũrĩa mũnene oragia Jesũ ũhoro wa arutwo ake na ũhoro wa ũrutani wake.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">18:20 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 26:55">Math 26:55</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 7:26">Joh 7:26</ref></char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Niĩ njarĩirie andũ othe a thĩ itarĩ ũndũ ngũhitha, na ngarutana hĩndĩ ciothe thunagogi-inĩ o na hekarũ-inĩ, kũrĩa Ayahudi othe macemanagia. Ndirĩ ũndũ njaragia na hitho. <verse number="21" style="v"/>Ũranjũria ũguo nĩkĩ? Ũria arĩa mananjigua ngĩaria. Ti-itherũ nĩmoĩ ũrĩa ndanoiga.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">18:22 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 19:3">Joh 19:3</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Rĩrĩa Jesũ oigire ũguo, ũmwe wa thigari iria ciarĩ hau akĩmũgũtha rũhĩ, akĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Ũguo nĩguo ũgũcookeria mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai ũrĩa mũnene?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">18:23 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 23:2-5">Atũm 23:2-5</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Angĩkorwo nĩndoiga ũũru-rĩ, heana ũira wa ũũru ũcio. No angĩkorwo ndaaria ũhoro wa ma-rĩ, wangũthĩra kĩ?” <verse number="24" style="v"/>Nake Anasi akĩmũneana atwarwo arĩ o muohe kũrĩ Kaiafa mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai ũrĩa mũnene.</para>
  <para style="s1">Petero Gũkaana Jesũ rĩa Keerĩ na rĩa Gatatũ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">18:25 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 18:18">Joh 18:18</ref>
      </char>
    </note>O hĩndĩ ĩyo Simoni Petero arũgamĩte agĩota mwaki, akĩũrio atĩrĩ, “Kaĩ wee ũrĩ ũmwe wa arutwo a mũndũ ũyũ?”</para>
  <para style="p">Nake agĩkaana, akiuga atĩrĩ, “Aca, ndirĩ ũmwe wao!”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v"/>Ndungata ĩmwe ya mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai ũrĩa mũnene, na yarĩ ya mbarĩ ya mũndũ ũrĩa Petero aatinĩtie gũtũ, ĩkĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Na githĩ niĩ ndirakuonire mũrĩ nake hau mũgũnda-inĩ wa mĩtamaiyũ?” <verse number="27" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">18:27 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 13:38">Joh 13:38</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 27:2">Math 27:2</ref></char></note>O rĩngĩ Petero agĩkaana, na o hĩndĩ ĩyo ngũkũ ĩgĩkũga.</para>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Mbere ya Pilato</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">18:28 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 27:2">Math 27:2</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 11:55">Joh 11:55</ref></char>
    </note>Ningĩ Ayahudi makĩruta Jesũ gwa Kaiafa makĩmũtwara gĩikaro-inĩ kĩa Barũthi wa Kĩroma. Hĩndĩ ĩyo kwarĩ rũciinĩ tene, na nĩgeetha matikagwatwo nĩ thaahu, Ayahudi matiatoonyire gĩikaro kĩu; nĩ ũndũ nĩmendaga mahote kũrĩa gĩathĩ kĩa Bathaka. <verse number="29" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio Pilato akiuma akĩmakora kũu nja akĩmooria atĩrĩ, “Mũndũ ũyũ mũramũthitangĩra kĩ?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v"/>Nao makĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Atangĩrĩ muuni watho-rĩ, tũtingĩmũrehe kũrĩ we.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v"/>Nake Pilato akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Kĩmuoei inyuĩ ene mũkamũciirithie kũringana na watho wanyu.”</para>
  <para style="p">Nao Ayahudi makĩregana na ũhoro ũcio, makiuga atĩrĩ, “Ithuĩ tũtirĩ na rũũtha rwa kũũraga mũndũ o na ũ.” <verse number="32" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">18:32 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 20:19">Math 20:19</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 12:32">Joh 12:32</ref>, <ref loc="JHN 12:33">33</ref></char></note>Maũndũ maya mekĩkire nĩgeetha ciugo iria Jesũ aarĩtie akĩonania mũthemba wa gĩkuũ kĩrĩa agaakua ihingio.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">18:33 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 19:9">Joh 19:9</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 23:3">Luk 23:3</ref></char>
    </note>Pilato agĩcooka agĩtoonya gĩikaro kĩu kĩa Barũthi, agĩĩta Jesũ akĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Wee nĩwe mũthamaki wa Ayahudi?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v"/>Nake Jesũ akĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Ũcio nĩ woni waku, kana nĩ andũ makwĩrĩte ũhoro wakwa?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v"/>Nake Pilato akĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Niĩ ndĩkĩrĩ Mũyahudi? Andũ anyu na athĩnjĩri-Ngai arĩa anene nĩo makũneanĩte kũrĩ niĩ. Nĩ atĩa wĩkĩte?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="36" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">18:36 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 26:53">Math 26:53</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 6:15">Joh 6:15</ref></char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Ũthamaki wakwa ti wa gũkũ thĩ. Korwo nĩ ũguo-rĩ, ndungata ciakwa nicingĩndũĩrĩire ndikanyiitwo nĩ Ayahudi. No ũthamaki wakwa nĩ wa kuuma kũndũ kũngĩ.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="37" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">18:37 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 8:47">Joh 8:47</ref>; <ref loc="1JN 4:6">1Joh 4:6</ref></char>
    </note>Nake Pilato akĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “nĩ ũndũ wa ũguo-rĩ, wee ũkĩrĩ Mũthamaki!”</para>
  <para style="p">Nake Jesũ akĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Nĩwaria ma kuuga atĩ niĩ ndĩ Mũthamaki. Ma nĩ atĩrĩ, gĩtũmi gĩkĩ nĩkĩo gĩatũmire njiarwo, na nĩkĩo ndokire gũkũ thĩ atĩ nyumbũrage ũhoro ũrĩa wa ma. Mũndũ o wothe ũrĩ mwena wa ũhoro wa ma nĩathikagĩrĩria.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="38" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">18:38 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LUK 23:4">Luk 23:4</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake Pilato akĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Ũhoro wa ma nĩ ũrĩkũ?” Aarĩkia kũũria ũguo akiuma nja o rĩngĩ agĩthiĩ kũrĩ Ayahudi akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Ndirona gĩtũmi gĩa kũmũthitangĩra. <verse number="39" style="v"/>No ningĩ nĩ mũtugo wanyu hĩndĩ ya Bathaka ndĩmuohorere mũndũ ũmwe. Nĩmũkwenda ndĩmuohorere ‘mũthamaki wa Ayahudi’?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="40" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">18:40 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 3:14">Atũm 3:14</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nao makĩanĩrĩra, magĩcookia atĩrĩ, “Aca, tũtikwenda ũcio! Tuohorere Baraba!” Na rĩrĩ, Baraba ũcio aarĩ mũtunyani.</para>
  <chapter number="19" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Gũtuĩrwo kwambwo Mũtĩ-Igũrũ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">19:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DEU 25:3">Gũcook 25:3</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 50:6">Isa 50:6</ref></char>
    </note>Hĩndĩ ĩyo Pilato akĩoya Jesũ, akĩmũhũũrithia iboko. <verse number="2" style="v"/>Nacio thigari igĩtuma thũmbĩ ya mĩigua, ikĩmwĩkĩra mũtwe, na ikĩmũhumba kanjũ ya rangi wa ndathi, <verse number="3" style="v"/>igathiiaga harĩ we o ihinda kwa ihinda, ikamũnyũrũragia ikiugaga atĩrĩ, “Ngeithi, mũthamaki wa Ayahudi!” Nacio ikamũgũthaga ũthiũ na hĩ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">19:4 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 18:38">Joh 18:38</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 23:4">Luk 23:4</ref></char>
    </note>O rĩngĩ Pilato akiuma nja, akĩĩra Ayahudi atĩrĩ, “Ta onei ngũmũruta nja ndĩmũrehe kũrĩ inyuĩ, nĩguo mũmenye atĩ niĩ ndionete ũndũ o na ũrĩkũ angĩthitangĩrwo.” <verse number="5" style="v"/>Rĩrĩa Jesũ oimire nja ekĩrĩte thũmbĩ ĩyo ya mĩigua na ehumbĩte kanjũ ĩyo ya rangi wa ndathi-rĩ, Pilato akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Mũndũ nĩ ũyũ!”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">19:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 3:13">Atũm 3:13</ref>; <ref loc="LEV 24:16">Alaw 24:16</ref></char>
    </note>Rĩrĩa athĩnjĩri-Ngai arĩa anene o na atongoria a Ayahudi maamuonire, makĩanĩrĩra makiuga atĩrĩ, “Mwambithie mũtĩ-igũrũ! Mwambithie mũtĩ-igũrũ!”</para>
  <para style="p">No Pilato akĩmacookeria atĩrĩ, “Muoei mũmwambe mũtĩ igũrũ arĩ inyuĩ. Ha ũhoro wakwa, ndirona ũndũ o na ũrĩkũ angĩthitangĩrwo.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">19:7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LEV 24:16">Alaw 24:16</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 26:63-66">Math 26:63-66</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 5:18">Joh 5:18</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 10:33">10:33</ref></char>
    </note>Nao Ayahudi makiuga magwatĩirie atĩrĩ, “Ithuĩ nĩtũrĩ watho; na kũringana na watho ũcio no nginya akue, tondũ nĩetuĩte Mũrũ wa Ngai.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>Rĩrĩa Pilato aiguire ũguo, agĩĩtigĩra mũno makĩria, <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">19:9 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 18:33">Joh 18:33</ref>; <ref loc="MRK 14:61">Mar 14:61</ref></char></note>agĩcooka thĩinĩ wa nyũmba ĩyo ya ũthamaki. Ningĩ akĩũria Jesũ atĩrĩ, “Wee-rĩ, uumĩte kũ?” Nowe Jesũ ndaigana kũmũcookeria. <verse number="10" style="v"/>Pilato akĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Kaĩ ũkũrega kũnjarĩria? Kaĩ ũtooĩ ndĩ na ũhoti wa gũkuohorithia, kana wa gũkwambithia mũtĩ igũrũ?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">19:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 13:1">Arom 13:1</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 18:28-30">Joh 18:28-30</ref></char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Wee ndũngĩrĩ na ũhoti igũrũ rĩakwa korwo ndũheetwo guo kuuma igũrũ. Nĩ ũndũ ũcio ũrĩa ũũneanire kũrĩwe nĩwe ũrĩ na mehia marĩa manene.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>Kuuma hĩndĩ ĩyo, Pilato akĩgeria kuohora Jesũ, no Ayahudi magĩthiĩ na mbere kwanĩrĩra atĩrĩ, “Ũngĩrekereria mũndũ ũyũ, wee ndũrĩ mũrata wa Kaisari. Mũndũ o wothe wĩtuaga mũthamaki nĩamenete Kaisari.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>Rĩrĩa Pilato aiguire ũguo-rĩ, akiumia Jesũ nja, na agĩikarĩra gĩtĩ kĩa mũtuanĩri ciira handũ hoĩkaine ta “Harĩa-haare-Mahiga” (na heetagwo na Kĩhibirania Gabatha). <verse number="14" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">19:14 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 27:62">Math 27:62</ref>; <ref loc="MRK 15:25">Mar 15:25</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 19:19">Joh 19:19</ref>, <ref loc="JHN 19:21">21</ref></char></note>Kwarĩ mũthenya wa Ihaarĩria rĩa Kiumia gĩa Gĩathĩ kĩa Bathaka; na kwarĩ ta thaa thita.</para>
  <para style="p">Nake Pilato akĩĩra Ayahudi atĩrĩ, “Ũyũ mũthamaki wanyu.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>No-o makĩanĩrĩra, makiuga atĩrĩ, “Mweherie! Mweherie! Mwambithie mũtĩ-igũrũ!”</para>
  <para style="p">Nake Pilato akĩmooria atĩrĩ, “Nyambithie Mũthamaki wanyu?”</para>
  <para style="p">Nao athĩnjĩri-Ngai arĩa anene magĩcookia atĩrĩ, “Ithuĩ tũtirĩ mũthamaki ũngĩ tiga Kaisari.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">19:16 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 27:26">Math 27:26</ref>; <ref loc="MRK 15:15">Mar 15:15</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 23:25">Luk 23:25</ref></char>
    </note>Mũthia-inĩ Pilato akĩmũneana kũrĩ o nĩguo akambwo mũtĩ-igũrũ.</para>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Kwambwo Mũtĩ-Igũrũ</para>
  <para style="p">Nacio thigari ikĩnyiita Jesũ. <verse number="17" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">19:17 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 23:26">Luk 23:26</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 23:33">Luk 23:33</ref></char></note>Na ekuuĩire mũtharaba wake agĩthiĩ nginya harĩa heetagwo “Ha Ihĩndĩ rĩa Mũtwe” (na no ho hetagwo na Kĩhibirania, Gologotha.) <verse number="18" style="v"/>Hau nĩho maamwambire, na hamwe nake makĩamba andũ angĩ eerĩ, ũmwe mwena ũmwe na ũcio ũngĩ mwena ũcio ũngĩ; nake Jesũ arĩ gatagatĩ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>Nake Pilato akĩandĩkithia kĩbaũ na gĩkĩhũũrĩrwo mũtharaba-inĩ. Nakĩo kĩandĩkĩtwo atĩrĩ, JESŨ WA NAZARETHI, MŨTHAMAKI WA AYAHUDI. <verse number="20" style="v"/>Nao Ayahudi aingĩ magĩthoma maandĩko macio, nĩgũkorwo handũ harĩa Jesũ aambĩirwo haarĩ hakuhĩ na itũũra rĩu inene, nakĩo kĩbaũ kĩu kĩandĩkĩtwo na Kĩhibirania, na Kĩlatini, na Kĩyunani.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">19:20 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Rũthiomi rwa Asuriata rwarĩ rũmwe rwa thiomi iria Ayahudi maaragia, na Kĩhibirania, na Kĩlatini, o hamwe na Kĩyunani.</char></note> <verse number="21" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">19:21 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 19:14">Joh 19:14</ref></char></note>Nao athĩnjĩri-Ngai arĩa anene a Ayahudi makĩĩra Pilato atĩrĩ, “Tiga kwandĩka ‘Mũthamaki wa Ayahudi’, no andĩka atĩ mũndũ ũyũ nĩ kuuga oigire atĩ nĩwe mũthamaki wa Ayahudi.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>Nake Pilato akĩmacookeria atĩrĩ, “Ũguo ndandĩka nĩndandĩka.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>Rĩrĩa thigari ciarĩkirie kwamba Jesũ, ikĩoya nguo ciake, igĩcigayania maita mana, o mũndũ yake, no kanjũ yatigarire. Nguo ĩyo ndĩarĩ na rũtumo, yatumĩtwo kuuma igũrũ nginya thĩ ĩrĩ o taama ũmwe.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">19:24 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 22:18">Thab 22:18</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nacio ikĩĩrana atĩrĩ, “Nĩtũtigei kũmĩtarũra; rekei tũmĩcuukĩre mĩtĩ nĩguo tũmenye ũrĩa ũgũthiĩ nayo.”</para>
  <para style="p">Gwekĩkire ũguo nĩguo Maandĩko mahinge marĩa moigĩte atĩrĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">“Maagayanire nguo ciakwa,</para>
  <para style="q2">na magĩcuukĩra kanjũ yakwa mĩtĩ.”</para>
  <para style="m">Ũguo nĩguo thigari ciekire.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">19:25 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 27:55">Math 27:55</ref>, <ref loc="MAT 27:56">56</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 24:18">Luk 24:18</ref></char>
    </note>Hakuhĩ na mũtharaba wa Jesũ nĩho nyina aarũgamĩte, na mwarĩ wa nyina na nyina, na Mariamu mũtumia wa Kiliopa, na Mariamu Mũmagidali. <verse number="26" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">19:26 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 12:46">Math 12:46</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 13:23">Joh 13:23</ref></char></note>Rĩrĩa Jesũ onire nyina na mũrutwo ũrĩa endete marũngiĩ hakuhĩ nake, akĩĩra nyina atĩrĩ, “Mũtumia ũyũ, ũcio mũrũguo,” <verse number="27" style="v"/>agĩcooka akĩĩra mũrutwo ũcio atĩrĩ, “Ũcio maitũguo.” Kuuma hĩndĩ ĩyo mũrutwo ũcio akĩoya nyina wa Jesũ, agĩthiĩ gũtũũra mũciĩ kwa mũrutwo ũcio.</para>
  <para style="s1">Gũkua kwa Jesũ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">19:28 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 13:1">Joh 13:1</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 1:22">Math 1:22</ref></char>
    </note>Thuutha ũcio, Jesũ amenya atĩ maũndũ mothe nĩmathira, na nĩguo Maandĩko mahinge, akiuga atĩrĩ, “Nĩnyootiĩ.” <verse number="29" style="v"/>Hau nĩ haarĩ na cuba yarĩ na thiki, nĩ ũndũ ũcio thigari igĩtobokia thibũnji ho, igĩcooka igĩthecerera thibũnji ĩyo rũthanju-inĩ rwa mũthobi, ikĩmĩtwarĩrĩria kanua-inĩ ka Jesũ. <verse number="30" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">19:30 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 12:50">Luk 12:50</ref></char></note>Hĩndĩ ĩrĩa Jesũ aamĩkundire, akiuga atĩrĩ, “Ũhoro nĩwathira.” Na oiga ũguo, akĩinamia mũtwe, agĩtuĩkana.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">19:31 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DEU 21:23">Gũcook 21:23</ref>; <ref loc="JOS 8:29">Josh 8:29</ref></char>
    </note>Na rĩrĩ, kwarĩ mũthenya wa Ihaarĩria wa Ayahudi, nĩguo marokere Thabatũ ya mwanya. Na tondũ Ayahudi matiendaga mĩĩrĩ ĩyo ĩtigwo mĩtharaba-inĩ hĩndĩ ya Thabatũ, makĩũria Pilato aathane atĩ andũ acio maambĩtwo moinwo magũrũ, na mĩĩrĩ yao ĩcuurũrio. <verse number="32" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio thigari igĩthiĩ ikiuna magũrũ ma mũndũ wa mbere ũrĩa mambanĩirio na Jesũ na igĩcooka ikiuna ma ũcio ũngĩ. <verse number="33" style="v"/>No rĩrĩa maakinyire harĩ Jesũ na makĩona atĩ nĩarĩkĩtie gũkua, makĩaga kuuna magũrũ make. <verse number="34" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">19:34 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ZEC 12:10">Zek 12:10</ref>; <ref loc="1JN 5:6">1Joh 5:6</ref>, <ref loc="1JN 5:8">8</ref></char></note>Handũ ha ũguo-rĩ, mũthigari ũmwe agĩtheeca Jesũ mbaru na itimũ, na o rĩmwe hakiura thakame na maaĩ. <verse number="35" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">19:35 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 24:48">Luk 24:48</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 15:27">Joh 15:27</ref></char></note>Nake mũndũ ũrĩa wonire maũndũ macio nĩarutĩte ũira, naguo ũira wake nĩ wa ma. We nĩooĩ atĩ aaragia ũhoro wa ma, na oimbũraga nĩgeetha o na inyuĩ mwĩtĩkie. <verse number="36" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">19:36 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 1:22">Math 1:22</ref>; <ref loc="EXO 12:46">Thaam 12:46</ref>; <ref loc="NUM 9:12">Ndar 9:12</ref></char></note>Namo maũndũ macio meekĩkire nĩgeetha Maandĩko mahinge marĩa moigĩte atĩrĩ, “Gũtirĩ ihĩndĩ o na rĩmwe rĩake rĩkoinwo.” <verse number="37" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">19:37 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ZEC 12:10">Zek 12:10</ref></char></note>O na ningĩ no harĩ Maandĩko mangĩ moigĩte atĩrĩ, “Makeerorera mũndũ ũrĩa maathecire.”</para>
  <para style="s1">Gũthikwo kwa Jesũ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="38" style="v"/>Thuutha ũcio, Jusufu wa Arimathea akĩhooya Pilato mwĩrĩ wa Jesũ. Na rĩrĩ, Jusufu aarĩ mũrutwo wa Jesũ, no amũrũmagĩrĩra na hitho tondũ wa gwĩtigĩra Ayahudi. Nake Pilato akĩmũhe rũtha, nake agĩthiĩ agĩkuua mwĩrĩ ũcio. <verse number="39" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">19:39 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 3:1">Joh 3:1</ref></char></note>Maathiire na Nikodemo, ũrĩa wathiĩte kũrĩ Jesũ ũtukũ. Nikodemo agĩtwara mũtukanio wa manemane na thubiri ingĩkinya o ta ratiri mĩrongo mũgwanja na ithano. <verse number="40" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">19:40 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 24:12">Luk 24:12</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 26:12">Math 26:12</ref></char></note>Nao eerĩ makĩoya mwĩrĩ wa Jesũ, makĩwoha na mataama ma gatani hamwe na mĩtukanio ĩyo mĩnungi wega, kũringana na mĩtugo ya Ayahudi ya gũthikana. <verse number="41" style="v"/>Hau Jesũ aambĩirwo nĩ haarĩ na mũgũnda, na thĩinĩ wa mũgũnda ũcio nĩ kwarĩ na mbĩrĩra njerũ, ĩrĩa ĩtakoretwo ĩigĩtwo mwĩrĩ wa mũndũ o na ũmwe. <verse number="42" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">19:42 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 19:14">Joh 19:14</ref>, <ref loc="JHN 19:31">31</ref></char></note>Tondũ kwarĩ mũthenya wa Ihaarĩria wa Ayahudi nĩguo marokere Thabatũ, na ningĩ nĩ ũndũ mbĩrĩra ĩyo yarĩ o hakuhĩ-rĩ, makĩiga Jesũ ho.</para>
  <chapter number="20" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Mbĩrĩra Theri</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">20:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 27:60">Math 27:60</ref>, <ref loc="MAT 27:66">66</ref></char>
    </note>Na rĩrĩ, mũthenya wa mbere wa kwambĩrĩria kiumia rũciinĩ tene, kũrĩ o na nduma, Mariamu Mũmagidali nĩathiire mbĩrĩra-inĩ na akĩona ihiga rĩrĩa rĩarĩ mũromo-inĩ rĩrĩ rĩeherie. <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">20:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 13:23">Joh 13:23</ref></char></note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio agĩthiĩ atengʼerete kũrĩ Simoni Petero na mũrutwo ũrĩa ũngĩ, ũrĩa Jesũ endete, akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Nĩmarutĩte Mwathani mbĩrĩra-inĩ, na tũtiũĩ harĩa mamũigĩte!”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">20:3 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LUK 24:12">Luk 24:12</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio Petero na mũrutwo ũcio ũngĩ makiumagara marorete mbĩrĩra-inĩ. <verse number="4" style="v"/>Marĩ o eerĩ magĩtengʼera, no mũrutwo ũcio ũngĩ agĩkĩria Petero ihenya, agĩkinya mbĩrĩra-inĩ mbere. <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">20:5 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 19:40">Joh 19:40</ref></char></note>Akĩinamĩrĩra, na akĩrora thĩinĩ, akĩona mataama ma gatani marĩ maige thĩ, no ndaatoonyire. <verse number="6" style="v"/>Nake Simoni Petero, ũrĩa warĩ thuutha wake, agĩkinya na agĩtoonya mbĩrĩra thĩinĩ. Akĩona mataama ma gatani maigĩtwo hau, <verse number="7" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">20:7 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 11:44">Joh 11:44</ref></char></note>o hamwe na gĩtambaya kĩrĩa Jesũ ohetwo mũtwe agĩthikwo. Nakĩo gĩakũnjĩtwo gĩkaigwo kĩrĩ giiki, gĩtarĩ hamwe na mataama macio ma gatani. <verse number="8" style="v"/>Thuutha ũcio mũrutwo ũcio ũngĩ, ũrĩa wakinyĩte mbĩrĩra-inĩ mbere, o nake agĩtoonya thĩinĩ. Akĩona na agĩĩtĩkia. <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">20:9 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 22:29">Math 22:29</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 24:26">Luk 24:26</ref>, <ref loc="LUK 24:46">46</ref></char></note>(Nĩgũkorwo nginyagia hĩndĩ ĩyo matiakoretwo mataũkĩirwo nĩ Maandĩko atĩ Jesũ nĩarĩ ariũke kuuma kũrĩ arĩa akuũ.)</para>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Kuumĩrĩra Mariamu Mũmagidali</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>Arutwo acio magĩcooka makĩinũka kwao, <verse number="11" style="v"/>no Mariamu akĩrũgama hau nja ya mbĩrĩra akĩrĩraga. O akĩrĩraga-rĩ, akĩinamĩrĩra, akĩrora mbĩrĩra thĩinĩ, <verse number="12" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">20:12 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MRK 16:5">Mar 16:5</ref></char></note>akĩona araika eerĩ marĩ na nguo njerũ, maikarĩte thĩ harĩa mwĩrĩ wa Jesũ waigĩtwo, ũmwe agaikara mũtwe-inĩ nake ũcio ũngĩ agaikara magũrũ-inĩ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>Nao makĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Mũtumia ũyũ, nĩ kĩĩ kĩrakũrĩria?”</para>
  <para style="p">Nake akĩmacookeria atĩrĩ, “Nĩ ũndũ nĩmeheretie Mwathani wakwa mbĩrĩra-inĩ, na ndiũĩ harĩa mamũigĩte.” <verse number="14" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">20:14 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MRK 16:9">Mar 16:9</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 21:4">Joh 21:4</ref></char></note>O hĩndĩ ĩyo akĩĩhũgũra, akĩona Jesũ arũgamĩte hau, no ndaigana kũmenya atĩ aarĩ Jesũ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>Nake Jesũ akĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Mũtumia ũyũ, nĩ kĩĩ kĩrakũrĩria? Nũũ ũracaria?”</para>
  <para style="p">Mariamu agĩĩciiria atĩ ũcio aarĩ mũrĩmi wa mũgũnda, akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Mũthuuri ũyũ, akorwo nĩwe ũmweheretie njĩĩra harĩa ũmũigĩte nĩguo thiĩ ngamuoe.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>Nake Jesũ akĩmwĩta, “Mariamu!”</para>
  <para style="p">Nake akĩĩhũgũra akĩmwĩtĩka na Kĩhibirania atĩrĩ, “Raboni!” (naguo nĩ kuuga Mũrutani).</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">20:17 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 28:10">Math 28:10</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 7:33">Joh 7:33</ref></char>
    </note>Jesũ akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Ndũkae kũnyiita, nĩ ũndũ ndirĩ ndĩrambata thiĩ kũrĩ Baba! No rĩrĩ, thiĩ kũrĩ arutwo akwa, ũmeere atĩrĩ, ‘Nĩndĩracooka thiĩ kũrĩ Baba, na nowe Ithe wanyu, njooke kũrĩ Ngai wakwa, na nowe Ngai wanyu.’ ”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">20:18 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LUK 24:10">Luk 24:10</ref>, <ref loc="LUK 24:22">22</ref>, <ref loc="LUK 24:23">23</ref></char>
    </note>Mariamu Mũmagidali agĩthiĩ kũrĩ arutwo, akĩmatwarĩra ũhoro, akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Nĩnyonete Mwathani!” Na akĩmeera atĩ nĩwe wamwĩrĩte maũndũ macio.</para>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Kuumĩrĩra Arutwo Ake</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>Hwaĩ-inĩ wa mũthenya o ũcio wa mbere wa kwambĩrĩria kiumia, rĩrĩa arutwo maarĩ hamwe, na mĩrango ĩrĩ mĩhinge nĩ ũndũ wa gwĩtigĩra Ayahudi, Jesũ agĩũka akĩrũgama gatagatĩ-inĩ kao, akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Gĩai na thayũ!” <verse number="20" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">20:20 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 16:20">Joh 16:20</ref>, <ref loc="JHN 16:22">22</ref></char></note>Aarĩkia kuuga ũguo akĩmoonia moko make na mbaru ciake. Nao arutwo makĩiyũrwo nĩ gĩkeno nĩ ũndũ wa kuona Mwathani.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>Na o rĩngĩ Jesũ akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Gĩai na thayũ! O ta ũrĩa Baba aandũmire, noguo o na niĩ ndamũtũma.” <verse number="22" style="v"/>Na oiga ũguo, akĩmahuhĩrĩria mĩhũmũ yake, akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Amũkĩrai Roho Mũtheru. <verse number="23" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">20:23 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 16:19">Math 16:19</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 18:18">18:18</ref></char></note>Arĩa othe mwarekera mehia mao, nĩmarĩrekagĩrwo, na arĩa othe mũtarĩrekagĩra, matirĩrekagĩrwo.”</para>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Kuumĩrĩra Toma</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">20:24 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 11:16">Joh 11:16</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Na rĩrĩ, Toma (ũrĩa wetagwo Wa-mahatha), ũmwe wa arĩa ikũmi na eerĩ, ndaarĩ hamwe na arutwo rĩrĩa Jesũ okire. <verse number="25" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">20:25 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 20:20">Joh 20:20</ref></char></note>Tondũ ũcio arutwo arĩa angĩ makĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Nĩtuonete Mwathani.”</para>
  <para style="p">Nowe akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Itoonete irema cia mĩcumarĩ moko-inĩ make, na ndoonyie kĩara gĩakwa hau irema-inĩ cia mĩcumarĩ, na njooke ndoonyie guoko mbaru-inĩ ciake, ndingĩĩtĩkia ũhoro ũcio.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v"/>Thuutha wa kiumia kĩmwe, arutwo ake maarĩ kũu nyũmba rĩngĩ, na Toma aarĩ hamwe nao. O na gũtuĩka mĩrango yarĩ mĩhinge-rĩ, Jesũ agĩũka, akĩrũgama gatagatĩ-inĩ kao, akiuga atĩrĩ, “Gĩai na thayũ!” <verse number="27" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">20:27 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 24:40">Luk 24:40</ref></char></note>Agĩcooka akĩĩra Toma atĩrĩ, “Toonyia kĩara gĩaku haha; rora moko makwa. Tambũrũkia guoko gwaku ũgũikie mbaru-inĩ ciakwa. Tiga kũgĩa na nganja, ĩtĩkia.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v"/>Nake Toma akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Mwathani wakwa na Ngai wakwa!”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">20:29 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1PE 1:8">1Pet 1:8</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Wetĩkia tondũ nĩwanyona. Kũrathimwo nĩ arĩa metĩkagia matonete.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">20:30 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 21:25">Joh 21:25</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Jesũ nĩaringire ciama ingĩ nyingĩ akĩonagwo nĩ arutwo ake, iria itaandĩkĩtwo Ibuku-inĩ rĩĩrĩ. <verse number="31" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">20:31 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 3:15">Joh 3:15</ref></char></note>No rĩrĩ, ici ciandĩkĩtwo nĩgeetha mwĩtĩkie atĩ Jesũ nĩwe Kristũ, Mũrũ wa Ngai, na atĩ na ũndũ wa gwĩtĩkia mũgĩe na muoyo thĩinĩ wa rĩĩtwa rĩake.</para>
  <chapter number="21" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Kũringa Kĩama gĩa Kũgwatia Thamaki</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">21:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 20:19">Joh 20:19</ref>, <ref loc="JHN 20:26">26</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 6:1">Joh 6:1</ref></char>
    </note>Thuutha ũcio Jesũ nĩacookire akiumĩrĩra arutwo ake iria-inĩ rĩa Tiberia. Ũũ nĩguo kwahaanire: <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">21:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 1:45">Joh 1:45</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 4:21">Math 4:21</ref></char></note>Simoni Petero, na Toma (ũrĩa wetagwo Wa-mahatha), na Nathanieli wa kuuma Kana ya Galili, na ariũ a Zebedi, o na arutwo angĩ eerĩ maarĩ hamwe. <verse number="3" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">21:3 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 5:5">Luk 5:5</ref></char></note>Simoni Petero akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Niĩ ndathiĩ gũtega thamaki.” Nao makĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Tũgũthiĩ nawe.” Nĩ ũndũ ũcio makiumagara, magĩtoonya marikabu, no ũtukũ ũcio matirĩ kĩndũ maagwatirie.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">21:4 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 20:14">Joh 20:14</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Rũciinĩ tene, Jesũ akĩrũgama hũgũrũrũ-inĩ cia iria, no arutwo matiamenyaga atĩ nĩ Jesũ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>Nake akĩmeeta akĩmooria atĩrĩ, “Arata akwa, nĩmũgwatĩtie thamaki?”</para>
  <para style="p">Nao magĩcookia makiuga atĩrĩ, “Aca.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">21:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LUK 5:4-7">Luk 5:4-7</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Ikiai wabu mwena wa ũrĩo wa marikabu na nĩmũkũgwatia.” Rĩrĩa meekire ũguo, makĩremwo nĩ kũguucia wabu ũcio nĩ ũrĩa thamaki icio ciarĩ nyingĩ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">21:7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 13:23">Joh 13:23</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake mũrutwo ũrĩa Jesũ eendete akĩĩra Petero atĩrĩ, “Nĩ Mwathani!” Na rĩrĩa Simoni Petero aiguire mũrutwo ũcio aamwĩra atĩ, “Nĩ Mwathani”, akĩĩoha nguo yake ya igũrũ (tondũ nĩamĩrutĩte), na akĩrũga maaĩ-inĩ. <verse number="8" style="v"/>Nao arutwo acio angĩ makĩmũrũmĩrĩra na marikabu maguucĩtie wabu ũiyũrĩte thamaki tondũ matiarĩ haraaya, maarĩ ta itĩĩna rĩa makinya igana rĩmwe kuuma hũgũrũrũ-inĩ. <verse number="9" style="v"/>Maarĩkia kuumĩria marikabu, makĩona mwaki wa makara wakĩtio hau, na thamaki irĩ njĩkĩre riiko, na mũgate.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>Nake Jesũ akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Rehei thamaki imwe cia iria mwagwatia.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>Nake Simoni Petero akĩhaica marikabu akĩguucia wabu ũcio nginya hũgũrũrũ-inĩ. Naguo waiyũrĩte thamaki iria nene, 153, no o na irĩ nyingĩ ũguo, wabu ũcio ndwatuĩkire. <verse number="12" style="v"/>Nake Jesũ akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Ũkai mwĩgagũre.” Hatirĩ o na ũmwe wa arutwo acio wamũũririe atĩrĩ, “Nĩwe ũ?” Nĩmamenyire atĩ nĩ Mwathani. <verse number="13" style="v"/>Nake Jesũ agĩthiĩ, akĩoya mũgate akĩmahe, agĩcooka akĩmahe thamaki o nacio. <verse number="14" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">21:14 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 20:19">Joh 20:19</ref>, <ref loc="JHN 20:26">26</ref></char></note>Rĩĩrĩ nĩrĩo rĩarĩ ihinda rĩa gatatũ rĩa Jesũ kuumĩrĩra arutwo ake thuutha wa kũriũka kuuma kũrĩ arĩa akuũ.</para>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Gũcookia Petero</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">21:15 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 26:33">Math 26:33</ref>, <ref loc="MAT 26:35">35</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 12:32">Luk 12:32</ref></char>
    </note>Nao maarĩkia kũrĩa, Jesũ akĩũria Simoni Petero atĩrĩ, “Simoni mũrũ wa Jona, na ma ti-itherũ nĩũnyendete gũkĩra aya?”</para>
  <para style="p">Nake agĩcookia atĩrĩ, “Ĩĩ Mwathani, wee nĩũũĩ atĩ nĩngwendete.”</para>
  <para style="p">Nake Jesũ akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Heaga tũgondu twakwa gĩa kũrĩa.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">21:16 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 20:28">Atũm 20:28</ref>; <ref loc="1PE 5:2">1Pet 5:2</ref>, <ref loc="1PE 5:3">3</ref></char>
    </note>Ningĩ Jesũ akĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Simoni mũrũ wa Jona, ti-itherũ nĩũnyendete?”</para>
  <para style="p">Nake akĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Ĩĩ Mwathani, wee nĩũũĩ atĩ nĩngwendete.”</para>
  <para style="p">Nake Jesũ akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Rĩithagia ngʼondu ciakwa.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">21:17 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 16:30">Joh 16:30</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Agĩcooka akĩmũũria hĩndĩ ya gatatũ atĩrĩ, “Simoni mũrũ wa Jona, nĩũnyendete?”</para>
  <para style="p">Nake Petero akĩigua ũũru ngoro nĩ ũndũ wa ũrĩa Jesũ aamũũririe hĩndĩ ya gatatũ atĩrĩ, “Nĩũnyendete?” Nake akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Mwathani, wee nĩũũĩ maũndũ mothe; wee nĩũũĩ atĩ nĩngwendete.”</para>
  <para style="p">Nake Jesũ akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Heaga ngʼondu ciakwa gĩa kũrĩa.” <verse number="18" style="v"/>“Ngũkwĩra atĩrĩ na ma, rĩrĩa warĩ mwĩthĩ nĩwehumbaga nguo, ũgathiĩ kũrĩa ũkwenda; no rĩrĩa ũgaakũra, nĩũgatambũrũkia moko, nake mũndũ ũngĩ nĩagakũhumba nguo, acooke agũtware kũrĩa ũtekwenda gũthiĩ.” <verse number="19" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">21:19 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2PE 1:14">2Pet 1:14</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 4:19">Math 4:19</ref></char></note>Jesũ oigire ũguo nĩgeetha onanie gĩkuũ kĩrĩa Petero agaakua, agoocithie Ngai. Agĩcooka akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Nũmĩrĩra!”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">21:20 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 13:23">Joh 13:23</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 13:25">Joh 13:25</ref></char>
    </note>Nake Petero eehũgũra akĩona mũrutwo ũrĩa Jesũ endete amarũmĩrĩire. (Ũcio nĩ ũrĩa wetiranĩtie na Jesũ rĩrĩa marĩĩaga irio cia hwaĩ-inĩ, na nowe wamũũrĩtie atĩrĩ, “Mwathani, nũũ ũcio ũgũgũkunyanĩra?”) <verse number="21" style="v"/>Na rĩrĩa Petero aamuonire-rĩ, akĩũria atĩrĩ, “Mwathani, nake mũndũ ũyũ ũhoro wake nĩ atĩa?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">21:22 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 16:27">Math 16:27</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nake Jesũ akĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Ingĩenda atũũre muoyo nginya rĩrĩa ngacooka-rĩ, ũcio ũkĩrĩ ũhoro waku? Wee no nginya ũnũmĩrĩre.” <verse number="23" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">21:23 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 1:16">Atũm 1:16</ref></char></note>Nĩ ũndũ wa ũguo-rĩ, mũhuhu ũkĩhunja thĩinĩ wa ariũ na aarĩ a Ithe witũ gũkĩĩrwo atĩ mũrutwo ũcio ndagakua. No Jesũ ndoigĩte atĩ ndagakua; ũrĩa oigĩte no atĩ, “Ingĩenda atũũre muoyo nginya rĩrĩa ngacooka-rĩ, ũcio ũkĩrĩ ũhoro waku?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">21:24 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 19:35">Joh 19:35</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Mũrutwo ũcio nĩwe ũrĩ na ũira wa maũndũ maya mothe, na nowe ũmaandĩkĩte. Na ithuĩ nĩtũũĩ atĩ ũira wake nĩ wa ma.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">21:25 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 20:30">Joh 20:30</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Jesũ nĩekire maũndũ mangĩ maingĩ. Korwo mothe nĩmandĩkirwo-rĩ, ngwĩgereria atĩ o na thĩ yothe ndĩngĩiganĩra mabuku marĩa mangĩandĩkwo.</para>
</usx>
